NK038(nyi)003:1: // dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i rim pa bzhugs pa'i dbu phyogs lags so //
NK038(nyi)003:3: badz+ra gu man tan tra karma man d+ha la /
NK038(nyi)003:4: sad tra ma a rbi sa da na ma /
NK038(nyi)003:6: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)003:7: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i rim pa rnam par dbye ba'i bsgrubs thabs zhes bya ba /
NK038(nyi)003:8: bcom ldan 'das dpal sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po
NK038(nyi)003:9: shin tu rnam par grol ba nyid la phyag 'tshal
NK038(nyi)003:11: khro la khros pa'i rgyal po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:13: khro bos nye bar zhi mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:14: khro bo de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK038(nyi)003:15: khro zhing che la phyag 'tshal te //
NK038(nyi)003:16: dgongs dam bca' ba pa 'dus pa'i rgyud dag las //
NK038(nyi)003:17: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i rim pa dag /
NK038(nyi)003:18: sems can ye nas yin pa ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:19: legs par bsdus te bstan par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:20: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK038(nyi)003:21: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK038(nyi)003:22: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:26: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK038(nyi)003:27: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK038(nyi)003:28: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK038(nyi)003:29: ston pa rdo rje'i rnal 'byor gyi rim pa thugs la gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:30: 'di ni man ngag gi che ba'i yon tan gsang chen nges pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:31: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK038(nyi)003:32: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK038(nyi)003:33: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK038(nyi)003:34: kun gyi phyag rgya rgyu rdzogs chen mchog zer ba 'dug yi mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:35: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la sbyin //
NK038(nyi)003:36: gzhan du nam yang sbyin mi bya //
NK038(nyi)003:37: rmongs la 'phyar bas gsal te byin //
NK038(nyi)003:38: dus min par ni srog zad nas //
NK038(nyi)003:39: srog dang bsdos par yun ring gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:40: 'das pa'i man ngag gi dgongs pa dus na sngon byung ba //
NK038(nyi)003:41: bdag nyid chen po rtags pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:42: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab las //
NK038(nyi)003:43: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK038(nyi)003:44: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK038(nyi)003:45: stong nyid ther zug 'gog pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:46: khro gtum log lta rkam zhing 'jungs //
NK038(nyi)003:47: le lo gti mug chang stsegs pas //
NK038(nyi)003:48: log lta dgu po bde myong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:49: de dag 'khrul pa de bsag sbyong gi sbyang rnams par grol ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:50: rgyal bas dkyil 'khor bdun du gsungs //
NK038(nyi)003:51: de rtsoms gang zag lngar 'dod rten gyi gang zag gi de //
NK038(nyi)003:52: 'dun pa dad pa dang ni rigs chen 'byed //
NK038(nyi)003:53: gnas gang du sbyin theg chen gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:54: dbang thob pa dbugs chen 'byin dang lung chen thob //
NK038(nyi)003:56: shes rab kyi rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)003:57: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:58: dgon pa chen po'i gnas chen ni //
NK038(nyi)003:59: ye shes snying po can rnams kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:60: theg chen gsang ba 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:61: dam pa rnams kyis basngagasa pa yin //
NK038(nyi)003:62: der gnas lta ba lhur len pa bstan /
NK038(nyi)003:64: gzhi ji bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK038(nyi)003:66: phyag rgya dngos grub dkyil 'khor dang //
NK038(nyi)003:67: byang chub sems kyi da la mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:68: bsod nam la spyod pas dor ba tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor sprin //
NK038(nyi)003:69: bka' 'jig rten pa'i bsnyen pa sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:71: gtad khram ma grub pa spangs pa mnan pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)003:72: de ni dbye ba'i ngos gnas su //
NK038(nyi)003:73: gsungs mi bskyod zhing khams mngon dga' nas //
NK038(nyi)003:74: dge slong ston pa thub dka' gzhon nu yi //
NK038(nyi)003:75: khyim 'khor bdag ke'u ka yi bu //
NK038(nyi)003:76: dge slong thar pa nag po dang //
NK038(nyi)003:77: g.yog po dan 'a phags gnyis po la //
NK038(nyi)003:78: ji bzhin gang bzhes na nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gsungs //
NK038(nyi)003:79: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK038(nyi)003:80: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:81: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)003:83: ji bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)003:84: phyag rgya dngos grub dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)003:85: mi 'khrugs pa yi zhing khams na //
NK038(nyi)003:86: khungs sgyu 'khrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud dag las //
NK038(nyi)003:87: drag po ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK038(nyi)003:88: mi 'khor 'khrugs rgyas po nyid la gsungs //
NK038(nyi)003:89: gnas chen dam pa dag tu ni //
NK038(nyi)003:90: tshul dang ldan pa'i rdzas bsog la //
NK038(nyi)003:91: dus man+dala la sogs mdzes byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:92: khrus bya snying gar yi dam nyi dkyil h'u //
NK038(nyi)003:93: 'od kyi snang bas dkon mchog rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:94: spyan drangs dkon mchog bskor la phyag 'tshal //
NK038(nyi)003:95: de nas mchod pa dbul ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:96: na mahsarbata th+aa ga ta badz+ra he ru ka badz+ra
NK038(nyi)003:97: da ri ma h+aa dz+ny+aa na man+da la la badz+ra
NK038(nyi)003:98: a ha ra badz+ra h'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)003:104: nee wi te p+au tsa badz+ra h'u +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)003:105: gtor ma zhes sogs byin gyis brlab par byas la /
NK038(nyi)003:106: rak+ta bdud rtsi'i tshogs mchod de //
NK038(nyi)003:110: go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:111: ba su ta tsit+ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:113: thugs byung lha mos mchod rjes la /
NK038(nyi)003:115: bdag 'dra log pa'i stobs ldan pas //
NK038(nyi)003:116: thog ma med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK038(nyi)003:118: skye ba mang po lus blangs pas //
NK038(nyi)003:119: sus kyang ma byas rang gi las //
NK038(nyi)003:120: de tsam cha gcig don spyad na //
NK038(nyi)003:121: da tsam don gyi sangs rgyas zin //
NK038(nyi)003:122: rang lus gtong bar ma phod cing //
NK038(nyi)003:123: chags pa'i mtha' la mngon zhen pas //
NK038(nyi)003:124: zug rngu nad kyis zin pa yin //
NK038(nyi)003:125: srid pa'i btson rar chud pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)003:126: mkha' la mdud pas nyes par nges //
NK038(nyi)003:128: las kyi rlung gis nyes par nges //
NK038(nyi)003:129: dus gsum rgyal ba ma lus la //
NK038(nyi)003:131: rdo rje sems yi ge brgya pa dpa'i dam tshig rjes su bsrungs //
NK038(nyi)003:132: ye shes sems dpa' nye ba nyid du spyod //
NK038(nyi)003:133: rigs pa'i rgyal po bdag la rtag par dgongs //
NK038(nyi)003:134: gsang ba'i dbang phyug bdag la gso bar gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:135: rtog pa'i mchog nyid bdag la dgos par dgongs //
NK038(nyi)003:136: 'dod pa kun byed bdag la chags par dgongs //
NK038(nyi)003:137: dang por mnyam nyid sangs rgyas thugs rje can //
NK038(nyi)003:138: las rnams kun byed bdag mos dge bar 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:139: dus gsum dge bshes dag dang thams cad du //
NK038(nyi)003:140: rdo rje can dang dam tshig sems dpar bsgrub //
NK038(nyi)003:141: bdag kyang rdo rje sems dpa' gtan kyang mi gtong na /
NK038(nyi)003:142: rdo rje sems dpa' rtag tu bdag ma btang //
NK038(nyi)003:143: rjes su yi rang bskul dang skyabs lam brten bsngo ba tshad med bzhi 'gro dang //
NK038(nyi)003:144: lam brten bsngo dang sems bskyed zer ba 'dug dang //
NK038(nyi)003:145: tshangs par gyur pa'i las rnams kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:146: 'gro ba kun la bran bzhin smon //
NK038(nyi)003:148: ha la ha la me bsregs ram //
NK038(nyi)003:149: tig sna tig sna kham chus 'khrus //
NK038(nyi)003:152: dngos po thams cad stong par sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)003:153: e ma stong pa nyid du gsal 'debs ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK038(nyi)003:154: rdzogs pa'i stong par bsgom sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK038(nyi)003:155: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK038(nyi)003:156: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK038(nyi)003:157: stong pa nyid du rab de bzhin gshegs pa'i ting 'dzin no gsal ba'i //
NK038(nyi)003:158: snying rje'i yum ni kun snang ting 'dzin sgom par bya'anama mkha' khyab par //
NK038(nyi)003:159: nges pa las ni rdo rjer rgyu'i ting 'dzin 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:160: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he brjod //
NK038(nyi)003:161: dur khrod chen po rab lam 'bras chen po bzhi 'jigs pa'i /
NK038(nyi)003:162: khrag gi bam las rgya mtsho 'khrug pa'i dkyil //
NK038(nyi)003:163: keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:164: steng gi ram la me 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK038(nyi)003:165: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)003:166: phyog bcu rgya yangs ma chad pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:167: phyi dang nang med kun tu phyi nang rang gsal snang //
NK038(nyi)003:168: 'bar ba'i lha rnams gnyis 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa //
NK038(nyi)003:169: gru chad bzhi yis rnam par brgyan //
NK038(nyi)003:170: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)003:171: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK038(nyi)003:172: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi mas brjid //
NK038(nyi)003:174: khyu mchog ma he gzigs dang stag /
NK038(nyi)003:175: gtum po dom gyi spar bas ni /
NK038(nyi)003:176: dbang ru tra ti ra bam /
NK038(nyi)003:178: ku be ra ti ra bam /
NK038(nyi)003:180: phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK038(nyi)003:181: dbus kyi nyi ma'i snying po las //
NK038(nyi)003:182: h'u las ru lu'i sgra sgrags pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:183: sems dpa'i ye shes sku ru gyur pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:184: rang gi ngang tshul de gzung las //
NK038(nyi)003:185: lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:186: khro zhal rnams la bskul bar bya //
NK038(nyi)003:187: bdag dang sems can ma lus kun //
NK038(nyi)003:188: mchog nyid grub par sbyor bas na //
NK038(nyi)003:189: rgyal ba rgya mtsho kun 'dus pas //
NK038(nyi)003:190: sku yi dbyig tu bdag bskyed cig /
NK038(nyi)003:191: de nas phyogs dus khro rgyal gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:192: sems dpa' bdag la de dbang bskur //
NK038(nyi)003:196: rim gsum gyi ni sku ru bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:197: de nas bcom ldan dgyes chen pos //
NK038(nyi)003:198: dbu dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:199: rdul snyed mtshon cha sna tshogs te g.yas dkar g.yon
NK038(nyi)003:200: dmar dbus nyon mongs pa'i ma gos 'khor la mi
NK038(nyi)003:202: rdo rje kha t+wam rnge'u chung gsal //
NK038(nyi)003:203: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)003:204: 'bar chen me ri klung gi 'khor lo dkyil spyi bo /
NK038(nyi)003:205: dbang phyug me dang dur khrod kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:206: steng nas zhabs bzhi bskyang bskum bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)003:207: dur khrod brgyan yum 'khyud can gar gyi rol //
NK038(nyi)003:208: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:209: rang bzhin phung khams skye mched byin gyis rlabs so //
NK038(nyi)003:210: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya wa ka tsit+ta swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK038(nyi)003:211: sku gsung thugs gsung mgrin pa //
NK038(nyi)003:214: khro rgyal ye shes pa gsal gdab ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:215: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ni //
NK038(nyi)003:216: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyung ste //
NK038(nyi)003:220: hi hi dges pa'i gzi mdangs kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:221: rin chen pad+ma rgyas mkha' gsang rlabs mdzad de //
NK038(nyi)003:222: gnyis yab yum h'u h'u med rol pa'i gzi mdangs kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:223: bde gshegs thugs mtshan byin rlabs nas //
NK038(nyi)003:224: gnyis med 'khril ba'i dges pas thim //
NK038(nyi)003:225: rdo rje'i lam byung yum gyi mkha' //
NK038(nyi)003:226: chos sku byang chub sems su gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:227: lha rnams so so'i snying po'i sgra //
NK038(nyi)003:228: h'u dang bcu ha brgyad dang he bzhi 'phags rnams bskul te phata ces byung nas /
NK038(nyi)003:229: gsung gi phyag rgya gnyis rdzogs te //
NK038(nyi)003:230: 'od zer spro bsdu'i sbyor ba yis //
NK038(nyi)003:231: thugs kyi mtshan gsum pa phyag rgya //
NK038(nyi)003:234: a nu ra ga swa b+ha wa a kha ham /
NK038(nyi)003:235: pu dz+aa a mo ga ham /
NK038(nyi)003:238: phyag rgya chen po'i sku rdzogs nas gsang ba phyogs
NK038(nyi)003:239: bcu'i rdul snyed 'jig rten khams su 'thon par 'gyur
NK038(nyi)003:240: // sems can rgyal ba'i sras bcas nas //
NK038(nyi)003:241: slar 'dus rang gi gnas su 'khod la //
NK038(nyi)003:242: dpal ni khrag 'thung chen po dang //
NK038(nyi)003:243: rin po che dang pad+ma dang //
NK038(nyi)003:244: las karma su gyur te so sor bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)003:245: de kun 'jigs byed chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:246: cha lugs rngams pa'i badz+ra he ru ka dang 'dra bar nga ro yis //
NK038(nyi)003:247: 'bar ba'i klong na dbu gsum pa //
NK038(nyi)003:248: phyag drug zhabs bzhi dri za dang //
NK038(nyi)003:249: gnod sbyin srin pad+ma po gshin rje'i stsegs rat+na //
NK038(nyi)003:250: dregs pa dbus su khyo shug gdan la bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)003:251: btsun mo khrag 'thung chen po rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:252: so so'i sku la 'khril te bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)003:253: dkar mo'i koor ri tshogs dang rkun tsoo ri mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:254: rmongs bra mo ha byed dang ni thal be ta li byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:255: sbos mo pu ka si dang ni gtum mo tsan+d+ha li dang /
NK038(nyi)003:256: sme sha dug sha ni can dang tsan d+ha gtun mo li //
NK038(nyi)003:257: sgo yi nang gi khyams la ro ldan ma /
NK038(nyi)003:261: stag lho dang nub wa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:263: kang lho nub ka dur nub byang bya 'ug gdong gyang shar che //
NK038(nyi)003:264: 'khor lha khyams phyi ma la spyang gdong ma bar rngam pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod //
NK038(nyi)003:265: rdo rje rta gdong srid 'gro ma tshogs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:266: rdo rje gdong mo seng gdong ma 'jig rten spyang gdong ma ro langs ma //
NK038(nyi)003:267: sgo bzhir rngam pa'i gzugs kyis gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:268: srin mo smug nag zhing mnan la sogs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:269: 'jig rten ma mo shar du nyi shu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:270: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor phyi las bskyed rol na //
NK038(nyi)003:271: bran gyi tshul du gnas shing 'khod //
NK038(nyi)003:272: de ltar gsal bar bkod pa'i sngags //
NK038(nyi)003:273: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru
NK038(nyi)003:274: ka ma h+aa tsan+d+ha sarba dush+tam ta ka ha na
NK038(nyi)003:275: da ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:276: badz+ra ma dbus h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)003:277: ma h+aa tsan d+ha sarba dush+tam ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:278: rat+na lhom ha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)003:279: ma h+aa tsan d+ha sarba dush+tam ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:280: pad+ma nub ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma ha
NK038(nyi)003:281: tsan d+ha sarba dush+tam ta ka ha na da ha
NK038(nyi)003:282: pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:283: karma byang ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa
NK038(nyi)003:284: tsan d+ha sarba dush+tam ta ka ha na da ha
NK038(nyi)003:285: pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:286: sarba ta shara th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sarba dush+tam h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:287: badz+ra dbus da ra kro ta ma ha kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:288: ma h+aa sur+ya rat+na lho ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri de ba h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:289: sh+r+ai shwa pad+ma nub bi mu ka ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri kha hi h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:290: sarba a mo byang ka ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri bi sha h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:291: badz+ra ke'u shar ha badz+ra tso'u ho lho /
NK038(nyi)003:293: badz+ra be ta li byang ha //
NK038(nyi)003:294: badz+ra pu ka si shar lho ha //
NK038(nyi)003:295: badz+ra kasma ri lho nub ha /
NK038(nyi)003:296: badz+ra sma nub byang shwa ni ha /
NK038(nyi)003:297: badz+ra tsan+d+ha byang shar li ha /
NK038(nyi)003:299: badz+ra bya kri lho mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)003:300: badz+ra sri la mu kha nub he /
NK038(nyi)003:301: badz+ra shwa na nub byang mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)003:302: badz+ra kri ta mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)003:303: badz+ra kam ka mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)003:304: badz+ra kha kha mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)003:305: badz+ra hu lu mu kha he /
NK038(nyi)003:306: badz+ra +aar+ya te tso te nga tsa /
NK038(nyi)003:307: badz+ra a lho mo ka h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:309: badz+ra sa smi sa la byang ya sa ti ho /
NK038(nyi)003:310: badz+ra ma srin mo g.yag nu rak+sha si b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:311: badz+ra tshangs pa sbrul pra ma ni b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:315: badz+ra si ma ka lam b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:322: re ti re ma ti b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:327: ma h+aa mam ra na b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:333: badz+ra ma h+aa ka la b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:336: badz+ra lam b+ho d+ha ra b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:337: de dag gis ni dkyil 'khor bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:338: dam tshig dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)003:339: da ni ye shes dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)003:341: dbyangs dang ldan pa'i lha mo yis //
NK038(nyi)003:342: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK038(nyi)003:343: mi dmigs thugs kyi da la nas //
NK038(nyi)003:345: mi dmigs mkha' ltar dag pa khyab pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)003:346: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:347: thugs rje ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK038(nyi)003:348: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:350: e ha ye hi dza dza dza /
NK038(nyi)003:351: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:352: zhes brjod pas ni phyag bya ste //
NK038(nyi)003:353: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK038(nyi)003:354: byams dang snying rjes sgra zin mi mnga' yang //
NK038(nyi)003:355: thugs rjes gdug pa 'dul mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:356: 'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:357: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK038(nyi)003:358: 'dod dgur bsgyur gyi bka' nyan yang sprul bsam mi khyab //
NK038(nyi)003:359: bdud 'dul ye shes pho nya drug cu'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:360: 'khor bcas rab 'bar gzugs can 'khrul mo che /
NK038(nyi)003:361: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK038(nyi)003:362: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:363: 'jig rten 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dbang phyug ma //
NK038(nyi)003:364: ci 'gyis bka' nyan yang mkha' 'gro so gnyis dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK038(nyi)003:366: bdud 'dul ye shes pho nya drug cu'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:367: 'khor bcas rab 'bar kun la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:370: ta th+aa ga ta b+han+d+ha na kha ro ya mi i dan du pa /
NK038(nyi)003:377: ni he sa d+ho ta ki ni ho //
NK038(nyi)003:378: zhes spyod ni lus ngag gus thod skam brgyad pa byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:380: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:381: thugs rje khro dpal rngam pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)003:382: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK038(nyi)003:383: de nyid du ni bdag la gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:384: badz+ra kro ti sa ma ya h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:385: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya phata /
NK038(nyi)003:386: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya rgya thod skam ho //
NK038(nyi)003:387: de bstim lus kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)003:388: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar bstan //
NK038(nyi)003:390: sku gsung thugs su bdag sbyor la //
NK038(nyi)003:391: pho brang da la rang las sprul //
NK038(nyi)003:392: nga ni bdud kyi bdud bdag ste //
NK038(nyi)003:395: sh+r+ai he ru ka sa ma ya mud tra pra ban dza ya /
NK038(nyi)003:406: bud d+ha sh+r+ai a pa s+t+wam pa ya nan //
NK038(nyi)003:407: so so'i rigs dbu brgyan gsal bar bsgom kyis 'bras bur 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:408: snying gar mi bskyod rdo rjes mtshan //
NK038(nyi)003:409: de las ma mo brgyad spros te //
NK038(nyi)003:410: phyi rol mchod yon chab la sogs pa byin gyis rlabs //
NK038(nyi)003:411: dbyangs dang ldan pas dbul bya ste //
NK038(nyi)003:412: dang po thun mong gyii rdzas lngas mchod //
NK038(nyi)003:413: de nas khyad par rdzas kyis mchod //
NK038(nyi)003:414: bdud rtsi sman nang mchod gyi mchod rdzas la //
NK038(nyi)003:416: sbrang rtsi btab par bya ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:417: bla med mchod gtor ba pa dam par sbyar ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:418: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK038(nyi)003:419: 'dod pa'i yan tan lnga yi rab brgyan te //
NK038(nyi)003:420: dam tshig gsang ba'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:421: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK038(nyi)003:422: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK038(nyi)003:423: dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te //
NK038(nyi)003:424: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK038(nyi)003:425: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:427: mkha' 'gro gsang ba'i tshogs bcas kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:428: ma lus gshegs nas mnabs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:430: mnyam thun mong du kun dbul lo pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK038(nyi)003:431: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK038(nyi)003:432: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo /
NK038(nyi)003:433: longs spyod lnga ldan mchod pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)003:435: dang po bdag nyid rtogs bsgom te //
NK038(nyi)003:436: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK038(nyi)003:437: blo ngan sems can snying re rje //
NK038(nyi)003:438: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK038(nyi)003:439: sarba sha trum ma ra ya kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:440: 'khyil ba'i mchod rten mnyam sbyor bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:441: bdag nyid mnyes pa'i mnyes bsgom te //
NK038(nyi)003:442: thams cad rang bzhin med pas na //
NK038(nyi)003:443: dgyes mnyam pa yi mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK038(nyi)003:448: de nas 'khril te snyoms zhugs pas //
NK038(nyi)003:449: dges ma nyam mchog gi mchod par rol //
NK038(nyi)003:450: mi dmigs 'khor rnams mi dmigs pa thugs kyi mchod pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:451: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyi ngang //
NK038(nyi)003:452: de nas phyi rol thon pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:453: ma mo rnams kyi bstod pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:455: gtum sku la bstod pa chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK038(nyi)003:457: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:458: mche ba zang yag za byed ho //
NK038(nyi)003:460: rngam bstod pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ltir //
NK038(nyi)003:461: rug chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK038(nyi)003:462: a a ha la'i gad rgyangs gsungs la bstod pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:463: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che ho //
NK038(nyi)003:464: khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK038(nyi)003:465: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu thugs la bstod pa bzang //
NK038(nyi)003:467: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che ho //
NK038(nyi)003:468: h'u khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po yon tan la bstod pa po /
NK038(nyi)003:471: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che ho //
NK038(nyi)003:473: bdud 'dul gyis ni bdud chen po //
NK038(nyi)003:474: bdud kyi bdud ste bdud rnams 'joms //
NK038(nyi)003:476: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che'o //
NK038(nyi)003:478: rdo rje brag chen sra ba dbyings ma nor ba po //
NK038(nyi)003:479: rdo rje chu bo bdud chen po //
NK038(nyi)003:480: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar bsreg /
NK038(nyi)003:481: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che'o //
NK038(nyi)003:483: sgeg pa dpa' ba rta mgrin gyi bskul pa 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:484: rgod dang zhal g.yas dang gshed g.yon dang 'jigs dbus par byed pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:485: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:486: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK038(nyi)003:487: gar gyi phyag rgya 'bar bas dbang phyug non yum la bya //
NK038(nyi)003:488: h+r+aih myos byed stong bas lhag par 'dod pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)003:489: 'dul ba'i dbang gis gshams na stong bas 'jigs tshul ston //
NK038(nyi)003:490: zhi ba'i sku yang tshangs pa stong bas lhag par ston /
NK038(nyi)003:491: thams cad dkyil 'khor gsum du snang bar mdzod cig ho //
NK038(nyi)003:492: h+r+aih rnam par 'dul ba'i ngo mthong thabs kyis rnam par gnon /
NK038(nyi)003:493: ho yab la he ha ha yum la he he khyab hi hi dgyes pa'i gad mo gad do //
NK038(nyi)003:494: dbang phyug phyogs skyong bcu la /
NK038(nyi)003:495: thams cad shig shig rab tu shig /
NK038(nyi)003:496: bdud kyi rtsal kyis stobs kyi ngo mtshar rmad byung ba //
NK038(nyi)003:497: rtogs pa mang po'i rgyud kyi gdul bya ma lus pa //
NK038(nyi)003:498: ye shes sgyu ma ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:499: de rjes sngon gyi gnas su bzhugs thim nas //
NK038(nyi)003:500: dkyil 'khor pa rang gi 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dkyil 'khor phyag rgya'i nga rgyal ni //
NK038(nyi)003:501: sngon du gsungs pa'i khro bo'am zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK038(nyi)003:502: yang na spyan ras gzigs pa yi //
NK038(nyi)003:503: khro bo 'bar ba'i dbu dgu pa /
NK038(nyi)003:504: phyag ni bco brgyad lta bu yis //
NK038(nyi)003:505: snying gar drag po'i 'khor lo bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:506: ru lu rtsa ba'i sngags dag ni //
NK038(nyi)003:507: 'bum mam bye ba'i bar du bzlas //
NK038(nyi)003:508: phyag rgya dngos grub dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)003:509: thun mtshams mnyam par bzhag pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:510: rang gi nor bu rin po che //
NK038(nyi)003:511: yod par ma shes stor bar dran //
NK038(nyi)003:513: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)003:514: chos 'dzin rigs kyi grub gnas su //
NK038(nyi)003:515: thugs rje'i sa la mngon sprul gshegs //
NK038(nyi)003:516: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:517: byams mgon dam pa ston pa zhig gis bstan //
NK038(nyi)003:518: e ma khyod kyis mi shes bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:519: mthong yul kun tu bde ba yis //
NK038(nyi)003:520: sgron mes mun khung gser 'tshol ltar //
NK038(nyi)003:521: gsang ba'i snying po'i mdzod bsnol te //
NK038(nyi)003:522: thig le gcig gis kun la khyab //
NK038(nyi)003:523: thams cad lung chen nges par bstan //
NK038(nyi)003:524: 'jig rten g.yo rdul mi g.yo'i rang bzhin rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:525: 'bar ba lnga bcu'i khro bo'i ngang du snang //
NK038(nyi)003:526: mya ngan 'das nas dang 'khor ba'i rang bzhin rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:527: rtsol med ma bcos de nyid rnam dag las //
NK038(nyi)003:528: thig lhang du le yungs kar tsam zhig gsal bar bsgom //
NK038(nyi)003:529: de las 'od zer rdul snyed spros //
NK038(nyi)003:530: ma rig pa'i mun gsal rags pa'i dngos po kun stong par sbyangs te //
NK038(nyi)003:531: thams cad ma bcos sku ru gsal //
NK038(nyi)003:532: slar 'dus thig le la thim nas sam //
NK038(nyi)003:533: 'od du zhu nas rim gyis bsdus //
NK038(nyi)003:534: rdo rje ye shes pa sems dpa' snying gi nang //
NK038(nyi)003:536: de steng gsang gnas sa rlung dang //
NK038(nyi)003:537: snying kha'i nang nas chu rlung gnyis //
NK038(nyi)003:538: rnam par dag pa zla ba ste //
NK038(nyi)003:539: rdo rje rin chen gnyis rang bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:540: de steng rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK038(nyi)003:541: thig le 'od zer lnga ldan sems //
NK038(nyi)003:542: de stengs mgrin gnas me'i rtsa me rlung dang //
NK038(nyi)003:543: mgo bo'i nang nas rlung dkyil gnyis //
NK038(nyi)003:544: dag pa nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ste /
NK038(nyi)003:545: pad+ma'i rigs dang las rigs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:548: yang nas yang du 'dres par bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:549: yang rgyu mar 'og sgo gnyis 'gog go bag chags 'dzin /
NK038(nyi)003:550: 'gog pa bzhin du mdor bstan lte ba ma skye //
NK038(nyi)003:551: lam thig le las gyur skye 'gag med pa'i chos nyid rnam par dag pas skyed pa sgo'o //
NK038(nyi)003:552: lam mi zad pa'i ma ma ki'i snying gar chos steng sgo nyid rnam par dag pa'i sgo'o //
NK038(nyi)003:553: sam skyon rtog brdul med pa'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK038(nyi)003:554: spyi bo tam thogs pa ta ra na sgrol ba'i ming med pa'i chos nyid //
NK038(nyi)003:556: mum gsung brjod pa las 'das lha nyid chos sku
NK038(nyi)003:557: pa'i chos nyid rnam par thams cad la rnam par
NK038(nyi)003:558: dag pa'i sgo'o / zer ba 'dug snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK038(nyi)003:560: mi thugs g.yo ba'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK038(nyi)003:561: sku cir yang snang ba'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK038(nyi)003:562: sa rgyas bshad ni chu la thim pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:563: kun tu mnyam blos zag med pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:564: lam gyi ye shes smig rgyu lta bu //
NK038(nyi)003:565: chu ni me la sems mi dmigs pa thim pas na //
NK038(nyi)003:566: sems la dbang thob du ba 'dra //
NK038(nyi)003:567: me ni rlung la thim pas na //
NK038(nyi)003:568: ting 'dzin bsgom bzlas 'ba' zhig ldan pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:569: glog gi rnam pa lta bur mthong //
NK038(nyi)003:570: rlung ni rnam par rig pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:571: thim pas 'dod pa rnams bral te //
NK038(nyi)003:572: mar me lta bur mthong ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:573: rnam par rig pa 'od gsal la //
NK038(nyi)003:574: thim pas rnam par snang ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:575: phyi nang mun pa thams cad ni //
NK038(nyi)003:576: nam mkha' ltar ni mthong ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:577: e ma ho dngos po med pa las //
NK038(nyi)003:578: smon dang snying rje'i dbang gis ni //
NK038(nyi)003:579: ji ltar snang ba ma 'gags pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:580: 'dun tshogs lam pa'i dus na rigs kyi mi rtog pa ma gan sa bu //
NK038(nyi)003:581: yid la byed zhes thob ste //
NK038(nyi)003:582: sems dad pa sa dang 'dra mos pa gser dang 'dra /
NK038(nyi)003:583: yid ches pa zla ba dang 'dra gsum thob cing mtha' dbus grol //
NK038(nyi)003:584: rten pa bzhi'i sa sar gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:586: 'phro 'du gcig sgom pa'i las su rung bas pa'i ting 'dzin thob //
NK038(nyi)003:587: sems bzhi rdzogs te mtha' bcu shes //
NK038(nyi)003:588: bdag nyid yi ge phreng bar ni //
NK038(nyi)003:589: snang ba'i ltas mthong bsod nams gter //
NK038(nyi)003:590: dbugs chen mthong lam 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor pa dang po rab dga' /
NK038(nyi)003:591: sems gcig rdzogs nas mtha' chub nas //
NK038(nyi)003:592: 'jigs pa lnga spangs khyad par sa //
NK038(nyi)003:593: yongs su mi ldog ting 'dzin ni //
NK038(nyi)003:594: 'jig rten nor bu rin chen gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:595: gang bar spyod pa'i ltas mthong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:596: sgyu ma sbyong ba'i skyes bu de //
NK038(nyi)003:597: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i cha byad du //
NK038(nyi)003:598: rin chen bdun dang dpung tshogs kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:599: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ston //
NK038(nyi)003:600: lung chen thob pa'i skabs su ni //
NK038(nyi)003:601: seng ge dag la zhon pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:602: thams cad gnon pa'i ltas mthong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:603: e ma ho de bzhin nyid de ni /
NK038(nyi)003:604: rgyu dang rkyen gyis mi bskyed de /
NK038(nyi)003:605: rtog chen grol phyir de skad shar //
NK038(nyi)003:606: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje ni //
NK038(nyi)003:607: de bzhin nyid kyi chos bsrungs //
NK038(nyi)003:608: spros pa med pa de bzhin nyid ni /
NK038(nyi)003:611: sems 'dun rdzogs pa'i sa sar gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:612: 'bras bu nyid la lam shes pas //
NK038(nyi)003:613: lam gyi yan lag bde rdzogs te //
NK038(nyi)003:614: gzhan bdag smin par bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:615: ji ltar 'dod pa'i thabs mchog sbyor //
NK038(nyi)003:616: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skabs su ni //
NK038(nyi)003:617: kun snang ting 'dzin nyid thob ste //
NK038(nyi)003:618: de ni nyi zla'i 'khor lo bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:619: thams cad gsal bar byed ltas mthong //
NK038(nyi)003:623: drang don nges don min pa /
NK038(nyi)003:624: sems su bskyed cing mtha' mtha' drug chub //
NK038(nyi)003:625: steng du gyur pa'i ngo bo la //
NK038(nyi)003:626: de nas rgyal tshab skyes bu la //
NK038(nyi)003:627: chos kyi rgyal po gang de yi //
NK038(nyi)003:628: gdung 'tshob dga' ldan theg chen ston //
NK038(nyi)003:629: mi gnas bcu dus cho 'phrul snang //
NK038(nyi)003:630: bshes gnyen dam pas bka' stsal pas //
NK038(nyi)003:631: sa bcu pa la gnas pa dgongs pas bshad dngos sgra bzhin min pa yang //
NK038(nyi)003:632: chos nyid du rdzogs spyod la chos nyid ma rtogs pa byed //
NK038(nyi)003:633: mi rtog ngang du mi gnas te //
NK038(nyi)003:634: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi byed do //
NK038(nyi)003:635: e ma skyes bu dam pa'i klong //
NK038(nyi)003:636: gang gi ngo bo ci phyir lags //
NK038(nyi)003:637: skyes bu dam pas bka' rtsal pa //
NK038(nyi)003:638: gsang sngags dngos po gang gi lan na brgyad kyis bcings //
NK038(nyi)003:639: mnyam par mi bzhag ci phyir lan ni /
NK038(nyi)003:640: sgom myong ma yin pa ste zer ba 'dug bar du ni /
NK038(nyi)003:641: sangs rgyas dgongs pa myong ba yin //
NK038(nyi)003:642: skyes bu dam pa khyod ci mgu /
NK038(nyi)003:643: gang zhig mos pas su zhig gi /
NK038(nyi)003:644: ji ltar grol gyur ngo bo ci //
NK038(nyi)003:645: skyes bu dam pas bka' rtsal pa //
NK038(nyi)003:646: grol bar 'dod pas bla ma ston //
NK038(nyi)003:647: rig par rang byung zhi ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:648: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)003:649: bsod nams tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)003:650: zhing khams rin chen yod par ni //
NK038(nyi)003:651: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:652: sras 'khor mchog 'jam dpal chen po la //
NK038(nyi)003:653: chos ji ltar rim gyis brgyud pa bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:654: de bzhin 'byor pa'i yo byad la //
NK038(nyi)003:655: rnam gsum tshul du nag+ta bya //
NK038(nyi)003:657: bsod nams tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)003:658: bka' sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)003:659: sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa yi ni //
NK038(nyi)003:660: zhing khams mngon par dga' ba na //
NK038(nyi)003:661: rgyal tshab bston pa skyes bu kun gyis gsungs //
NK038(nyi)003:662: de'i gdam ngag mdor bstan pa bkod pa sngon byung la /
NK038(nyi)003:663: rtags nyams su blangs dang brten pa'i gzhung ltar bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:664: dape'u dang 'bru khung 'og nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK038(nyi)003:665: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:666: mtshon ni kang ka thang dmar na //
NK038(nyi)003:667: ri bo byan rlag 'chongs kyi ri /
NK038(nyi)003:669: kem rus thod pa'i mkhar du brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)003:672: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:673: rang gi btsar 'khor tshogs ldan par bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:674: de nas dpa' bo chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:675: ru lu h'u gi 'od zer spros //
NK038(nyi)003:676: drag po gnas nas gdug pa gug /
NK038(nyi)003:677: gnyis pa zhal du rngub te gnas nas bton //
NK038(nyi)003:678: gzhon nu sme brtseg zhes gyur te //
NK038(nyi)003:679: bskyed dang gnyis su med par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:680: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo //
NK038(nyi)003:681: bur kur ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:683: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:685: hu lu hu lu h'u rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ha ha ham /
NK038(nyi)003:686: zhal du rngubs te lus mi gtsang ba'i gnas nas bor //
NK038(nyi)003:687: de la ming gi rnam grangs ni //
NK038(nyi)003:688: gang gi rgyal po zhes dang bya //
NK038(nyi)003:689: lha chen legs ldan nag po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:690: lha'i ded dpon ka ru na //
NK038(nyi)003:691: tshogs bdag chen po bdud kyi rje //
NK038(nyi)003:692: dge slong rdo rje legs pa thar pa nag po yin //
NK038(nyi)003:693: tshogs bdag chen po des gsol pa //
NK038(nyi)003:694: dpa' bo chen po dgongs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:695: bdag cag skal ldan bzhi pa dkyil 'khor char gcig par gsol ba 'debs pa 'dus pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:696: sgo 'dir da yang zhu ba drug pa drag po
NK038(nyi)003:697: 'khor bcas byang chub tu sems bskyed gcig par gsol
NK038(nyi)003:698: ba gdab par / 'jug par 'tshal lags na //
NK038(nyi)003:699: rgyal pa'i sras su gzung du gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:700: dpa' lnga pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa bo chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NK038(nyi)003:701: h'u h'u h'u 'dul sbyongs drag po'i dkyil 'khor du sbyong ba /
NK038(nyi)003:702: bi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+da la phata phata bgegs skrad pa /
NK038(nyi)003:703: ha la ha la h'u ta kem ta kem dngos po thams cad stong par sbyangs /
NK038(nyi)003:706: ha la 'dul sbyongs drag po'i dkyil du /
NK038(nyi)003:708: kro ta kro ta yam ye shes rlung /
NK038(nyi)003:709: ka wa tsa'i byin rlabs h'u mum /
NK038(nyi)003:710: skal spro ba bskyed pa ldan 'dus pa'i tshogs chen khyed //
NK038(nyi)003:711: bde bar 'ongs gnang ba sbyin pa so legs par 'ongs //
NK038(nyi)003:712: grub pa'i lung sgo gsang ba 'dir //
NK038(nyi)003:713: su dag 'ongs pa slar mi ldog /
NK038(nyi)003:714: tshogs bdag chen pos yang gsol pa //
NK038(nyi)003:715: bdag cag mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:716: don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:717: rtog pa'i dbang gi 'khor ba las //
NK038(nyi)003:718: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)003:719: sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:720: mun pas sgrib pas de ma shes //
NK038(nyi)003:721: byang chub sems kyi lam 'di nas //
NK038(nyi)003:722: sangs rgyas sa la 'jug par bgyi //
NK038(nyi)003:723: dpa' bo chen pos bka' stsal pa //
NK038(nyi)003:724: rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyed //
NK038(nyi)003:725: bdun pa sems bskyed pa la rdo rje lta bu'i sgo nas dam tshig rtsog pa /
NK038(nyi)003:726: rdo rje can du gcig nges na //
NK038(nyi)003:727: gsang ba gsum dang mnyam pa nyid //
NK038(nyi)003:728: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig sbyin //
NK038(nyi)003:729: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig ni /
NK038(nyi)003:730: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nas byung //
NK038(nyi)003:731: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi dam tshig ni //
NK038(nyi)003:732: grub na 'jigs pa'i dus med do //
NK038(nyi)003:733: nag po drug pa drag pa 'khor bcas dbang bskur
NK038(nyi)003:734: cig par gsol ba gdab pa pos yang gsol pa
NK038(nyi)003:735: // ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:736: gzi brjid phung po bla na med //
NK038(nyi)003:737: sangs rgyas rin chen kun 'dus pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:738: rnam par rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:739: dbyig gi ye shes gtso mchog nyid //
NK038(nyi)003:740: rdo rje dam pa mchog 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)003:741: khyed ni dam tshig gtso lags kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:742: dbang phyug rgyal po bdag dbang bskur //
NK038(nyi)003:743: dpa' bo chen po des snang bas //
NK038(nyi)003:744: dgu pa dpa' bo ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur ba /
NK038(nyi)003:745: badz+ra a mri ta a hi hi sarba man+da la h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:747: nag po chen pos yang gsol pa //
NK038(nyi)003:748: bdag ni skyes bu khyod kyi bdag dbang bskur //
NK038(nyi)003:749: sangs rgyas kun gyi de ring bdag dbang bskur //
NK038(nyi)003:750: bcom ldan mchog nyid bdag lags te //
NK038(nyi)003:751: mchog nyid bsgrub phyir dbang yang blang bar bgyi //
NK038(nyi)003:753: mos dang dbang gi rgyu la dbul ba bsnyen pa'i tshogs gsol te //
NK038(nyi)003:754: seng ger sprul te gdan du phul //
NK038(nyi)003:755: la las lus ni gdan du phul //
NK038(nyi)003:756: la las sham thabs dag kyang phul //
NK038(nyi)003:757: bcu pa chos gsung thugs dam mnga' gsol ba /
NK038(nyi)003:758: bur kur e ho shwa mo kro d+ha h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:765: la las thig ler phul byas shing //
NK038(nyi)003:766: la las byug pas mnyes byas nas //
NK038(nyi)003:767: la las phreng bar mdzes pa'i rgyan //
NK038(nyi)003:768: la las 'di yan chad shog 'di ltar gyi phyag 'tshal phul te gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:769: de nas gying gi rgyal po la //
NK038(nyi)003:770: mnga' gsol mchod thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bsgom pa tshul du btab //
NK038(nyi)003:771: nye ba spyor pa lnga yang byin //
NK038(nyi)003:778: dka' thub chen po tshur gson cig /
NK038(nyi)003:779: legs ldan nag po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:780: rang gi rgyal srid la gnas te //
NK038(nyi)003:781: ka gzhan gyi sde pa 'joms byed pa //
NK038(nyi)003:782: khram la btab pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:783: rol cig dgongs shig dam tshig gtso //
NK038(nyi)003:784: khyod tso lags kyi sangs zer /
NK038(nyi)003:785: ka tho sdebs shig gong 'og tshig 'khrugs su 'dug go //
NK038(nyi)003:786: kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:787: bse byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:788: ma dang sring mo bud med la //
NK038(nyi)003:789: dpa' bo khyod kyis rol mdzad cing //
NK038(nyi)003:790: dam tshig chen pos gtso bo nyid la bya ma btang cig /
NK038(nyi)003:791: zhe sdang khro bo rnams la can gyi bdag gi bco brgyad po rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:792: sems can kun gyi srog 'phrog ma //
NK038(nyi)003:794: 'dod chags can gyis bdag po rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:795: bud med kun la 'dod spyod pa /
NK038(nyi)003:796: bse byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:798: sha dang khrag la longs spyod kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:799: gnod yak+sha sbyin chen po ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)003:800: bse byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:801: gser sogs g.yu mkhar blangs nas yid gnag pa'i dgra bgegs ni //
NK038(nyi)003:802: rang gi 'dod par longs spyod srin po rnams la bya kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:803: rtog pa'i rgyal po mi thod can rnams gson cig /
NK038(nyi)003:804: mgo thod bcad nas rtags brten dang //
NK038(nyi)003:805: dge yul mtshan rnal 'byor nges 'bod na //
NK038(nyi)003:806: yid bzhin lta bu'i dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)003:807: rigs ngan rme sha can gyi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:808: ba glang rta sha khyi sha dang //
NK038(nyi)003:809: mi sha glang chen sha sogs bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:810: sring mo khrag 'phrog ma lus pas //
NK038(nyi)003:811: bsad pa'i khrag ni 'di na ma za byed rnams la bsngo pa yin /
NK038(nyi)003:813: bzhes shig dgra bo'i khrag la 'thung //
NK038(nyi)003:814: sprul pa'i phra nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma la men chen po rnams /
NK038(nyi)003:815: thod rus rkang dang 'bru mar khrag /
NK038(nyi)003:816: chang dang a mri ta sbyar ba'i //
NK038(nyi)003:817: rdzu 'phrul grub pa'i dam rdzas bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:818: rigs ngan chen po ma rungs ma //
NK038(nyi)003:819: sha chen gshang lci khu ba khrag /
NK038(nyi)003:821: bdag gi nad rnams bzlog tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:822: dmigs pa'i yul du rims nad thong //
NK038(nyi)003:823: srid pa'i bud med ma rung khyod //
NK038(nyi)003:824: bro gar glu tshig mchod par bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:825: dmigs bya 'joms tshul stab kyis phrogs //
NK038(nyi)003:826: shor ba bzhon nu bdud mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:827: rnal 'byor chen po'i bka' byung gis //
NK038(nyi)003:828: sngags sgra rang gi mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:829: dmigs pa'i phung po rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:830: ngag gi sprul pas dgra bo bslus //
NK038(nyi)003:831: log sred can gyi tshogs rnams nyon //
NK038(nyi)003:832: yang dag ngang du kun rig na //
NK038(nyi)003:833: che chung las gnyis gang byas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:834: gnyis kyi dbang du mi 'gyur gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:836: gsang tshig rten pa'i tshogs rnams nyon //
NK038(nyi)003:837: gshang gci khrag dang sol khu'i gos //
NK038(nyi)003:838: bargya'am stong du gon da ni 'di nas mar bstod par gyis gsungs so nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:840: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:841: bcol pa'i las rnams grub par gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:842: mnga' bdag chen po ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)003:843: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:844: khro bo'i rgyal po gying chen po //
NK038(nyi)003:845: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)003:846: rnal 'byor mtshan po ngas bstod kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:847: khyed kyi mthun pa'i rdzas 'bul gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:848: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK038(nyi)003:849: khas blangs dam bca' mna' bor ba'i //
NK038(nyi)003:850: sngon du rig 'dzin gong mas bsgrubs //
NK038(nyi)003:851: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bsgrub na //
NK038(nyi)003:852: bam ri thod pa mkhar gyi rtser //
NK038(nyi)003:853: ru mtshan nag po pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)003:854: mtshon cha nag po char du phob //
NK038(nyi)003:855: bdud bya nag po'i lding cing 'dzum //
NK038(nyi)003:856: dur khrod mang po'i rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)003:857: mche gtsigs rngam pa'i zhal gdengs shing //
NK038(nyi)003:858: khro bo khro mo'i sprul pa 'khrigs //
NK038(nyi)003:859: srin po pho mo'i skan sgra rdeb /
NK038(nyi)003:860: gnod sbyin pho mo 'brug ltar sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)003:861: za byed pho mo glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:862: lha srin sde brgyad 'khor bcas la //
NK038(nyi)003:863: so so'i mos pa tha dad pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:864: yid bzhin nor bu'i dam tshig ni //
NK038(nyi)003:865: yongs su rdzogs par blang bar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:866: de ltar mchod bstod bskang rjes la //
NK038(nyi)003:867: rang rgyud dam tshig gis gnas te //
NK038(nyi)003:868: de dag rnams la mthun rdzas 'jig rten gzhan brdeg na 'dud rtsi lnga sha khrag ni //
NK038(nyi)003:869: tshogs bdag chen po 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:871: pra ti dzi na kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:872: ma h+aa mam sa kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:874: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:875: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:876: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri tsit+ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:877: zhes zhal du gsol bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:878: de nas gying chen 'khor bcas kyi 'bangs su mchi'o //
NK038(nyi)003:879: bcu gnyis pa khas che zhing mna' skyal /
NK038(nyi)003:881: 'bangs su nan tan ma chung zhig /
NK038(nyi)003:882: de nas slad chad ji bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)003:883: bka' lung bzhin du rjes su bsgrub /
NK038(nyi)003:884: gal te bka' bzhin ma bgyis na //
NK038(nyi)003:885: dam pa'i lung las 'gal gyur nas //
NK038(nyi)003:886: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying //
NK038(nyi)003:887: rul myags skam nas tshig par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:888: ma sring bu mo chung ma rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:889: dbus su mchis skal ma mchis 'bangs su 'bul lo kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:891: phud la 'tshal skal mi ldan gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:892: lhag ma zhal chab bron la gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:893: nye gnas gdung gi ma sring la //
NK038(nyi)003:894: de nas rgyal ba'i 'bangs yin gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:895: khyed kyis ci gyis las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)003:896: bka'i las byung legs par rab tu sgrubs //
NK038(nyi)003:897: ji ltar ma byams bu la gdung ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:898: dam tshig can la dung dung gdung bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:899: gang du ming byams sring la brtse ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:900: yal gam can la lhang lhang brtse bar bgyi //
NK038(nyi)003:901: mdza' bo grogs la ji ltar gdung tshul du //
NK038(nyi)003:902: rnal 'byor bdag la kril kril brtse bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:903: ji ltar g.yog byams dpon la snying brtse ltar //
NK038(nyi)003:904: dam pa rnams la gus pas nye bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:905: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo zhes pas //
NK038(nyi)003:906: rang gi srog la tshad du bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:907: dpa' bo chen pos bka' rtsal pa //
NK038(nyi)003:908: brtse bar byed na mar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:909: gdung bar byed na sring mo ste //
NK038(nyi)003:910: brtson par byed na bran du bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:911: byang chub dag na bur bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:912: 'du bral med na slob mar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:913: bskul bas mgyogs na pho nya bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:914: bka' bcu gnyis bzhin byed na bka' la btags //
NK038(nyi)003:915: rdo rje ljags kyi 'od zer las //
NK038(nyi)003:916: rak+sha sh+ri he ru ka ru tra ma ra tram ha ha ho //
NK038(nyi)003:917: zhes pas dbang du bsdus dang bzlas bsnyen pa'i pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:918: bsnyen pa'i bzlas pa 'bum byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:919: don chen stsal ba zhes su bzhad //
NK038(nyi)003:920: thun mtshams kun tu mchod pa yang //
NK038(nyi)003:921: dung chen la sogs rtags par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:922: don chen bsnyen par gyur pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:923: sna yi bu ga'i h'u ring las //
NK038(nyi)003:924: khro bo gying gi rgyal po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:925: las kyi rgyal po sra bdag ni //
NK038(nyi)003:926: ljang sngon drag po gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)003:927: spros la gnyis su med par bstim //
NK038(nyi)003:928: rgyu zhags mkhar nag skud ma la //
NK038(nyi)003:929: mthing nag dar chen 'bar ba la //
NK038(nyi)003:930: phyi ma ril bu sum sgrub bstim //
NK038(nyi)003:931: rang gi lag pa g.yon par bzungs //
NK038(nyi)003:932: gzungs thag btags te sngags bzlas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:933: nye ba'i bsnyen pa 'bum du bzla //
NK038(nyi)003:934: don chen bsnyen par gyur pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:935: de nas don la 'jug par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:936: rang gi lag pa g.yon pa'i thum po bar ma kha cher phye la //
NK038(nyi)003:937: mkhar nang pho nyas bskul bar bya //
NK038(nyi)003:938: 'bum du bsgrub pa dag ni bzlas //
NK038(nyi)003:939: de nas tshogs kyi mchod pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:940: gsum du byas ste dbul bar bya //
NK038(nyi)003:941: steng du gyur pa'i gsang sngags mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:942: bsgrub pa chen po 'bum du bzlas //
NK038(nyi)003:943: pho nya mngag gzhug dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)003:945: stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams na //
NK038(nyi)003:946: rnam dag lam shes rgyal ba rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:947: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK038(nyi)003:948: brub khungs drag shul can gyis gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:950: skyes bu khyed lta zhig smos /
NK038(nyi)003:951: khyed kyi dam pa 'di la gnas pa'i gang zag dang //
NK038(nyi)003:952: bdag cag rnams kyis pha lags so //
NK038(nyi)003:954: srid pa 'gro ldog kyang bka' las mi ldog kye ma ho khyed lta ci smos //
NK038(nyi)003:955: khyod kyi dam tshig 'di la gnas pa'i gang zag
NK038(nyi)003:956: de 'di ltar lha'i dbang po'i gtsug na nor bu
NK038(nyi)003:967: yul khams kyi skye bo rnams la gang chos su yongs su bsrungs ba rnams bsrungs bar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:970: chos srungs bar de dag la 'tshe ba'i mi dang
NK038(nyi)003:971: mi ma yin pa de dag kyang yongs su gzhom
NK038(nyi)003:973: mtshams gcad cing bar bgyi ste /
NK038(nyi)003:974: de dag gi bsam pa ngan pa dang ci bcol ba thams cad kyi las bagyi'o //
NK038(nyi)003:975: de dag gis kyang chos srungs zhing chos bzhin gnas
NK038(nyi)003:976: nas bdag cag rnams kyis phyir yang 'di bzhin du
NK038(nyi)003:977: 'grub / dam rdzas dang dge mtshan rtags rten rnams ched du 'brel ba'i phyir bcang bar bgyi /
NK038(nyi)003:978: bdag cag rnams kyi dam tshig lags pa'i slad du'o //
NK038(nyi)003:979: rdo rje thabs kyi lta ba'i yul //
NK038(nyi)003:980: dur khrod bdag po'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:981: bdag ni bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)003:982: bka' yi las kyi dus byung bas //
NK038(nyi)003:983: sangs rgyas kun gyi gdul dka' ba //
NK038(nyi)003:984: de dag ma lus bdag gi 'dul //
NK038(nyi)003:985: bka' las de dag mdor bkod pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:986: lho phyogs man+dala sum brtsegs la //
NK038(nyi)003:987: dang po thod pa'i phreng bas rgyan //
NK038(nyi)003:988: de 'og mtshon cha'i char gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:990: nang du rgya sol nag po byug /
NK038(nyi)003:991: de yi nang du ling+ga ni //
NK038(nyi)003:992: ji lta bu'i tshul bzhin bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:993: yan lag phyag rgya bzhi yis brkyang //
NK038(nyi)003:994: tsi ran dang po phra men ma /
NK038(nyi)003:996: bar pa la ni mgo lid+ga la brnyan te /
NK038(nyi)003:997: tha ma la ni srin mo'i dbang mo nyer brgyad tshogs /
NK038(nyi)003:998: gdug pa'i tsher ma'i phur pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:999: mtshon byas byas te rnam par bkod //
NK038(nyi)003:1000: mgul nas btags shing mgo la dar btags rten la gtod //
NK038(nyi)003:1001: da ni las la sbyor ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1002: gtor ma la sogs mchod pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:1003: mnyes shing bskul ba gzhung bzhin bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1004: ji srid mtshan ma rnyed kyi bar //
NK038(nyi)003:1005: las la sbyor ba drag po'i sngags //
NK038(nyi)003:1006: rngam pa'i nga ro 'don par byed //
NK038(nyi)003:1007: ma nyes la sogs gzu dpang gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:1008: de nas pho nya mngag par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1010: 'bar ba drag po mi bzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1011: rtog pa med pa'i rgyal po las //
NK038(nyi)003:1012: rdo rje lcags kyi 'od zer las //
NK038(nyi)003:1013: badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)003:1014: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin phung rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:1015: mngag gzhug pho nyar spro bar bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1016: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:1017: srin mo mngag pa'i drag sngags so //
NK038(nyi)003:1018: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya lho nub dang po /
NK038(nyi)003:1019: gnod sbyin rbad pa'i drag sngags so //
NK038(nyi)003:1020: tsi ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:1022: za byed bskul pa'i pho nya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1023: sngags dang ming du spel nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1024: khros pas bsam la khri'am 'bum du bzlas /
NK038(nyi)003:1026: dung chen btang la bskul ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1027: sngon tshe dpal chen nyid kyi bka' //
NK038(nyi)003:1028: de nas rnal 'byor rgyud kyi bka' //
NK038(nyi)003:1029: da lta rnal 'byor bdag sgrub kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:1030: khas blangs dam bca' bsnyel lam ci //
NK038(nyi)003:1031: dam bca' bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:1032: ji ltar ma byams bu la gdung tshul bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:1033: rnal 'byor can la kril kril brtser ba gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:1034: ji ltar g.yog byams dpon la gdung ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:1035: dam pa rnams la nges par nye bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:1036: rgyal ba kun gyis chos sku pad+ma'i gdung //
NK038(nyi)003:1037: chos rje 'od dpag med pa rdo rje'i chos //
NK038(nyi)003:1038: spyan ras gzigs dbang h+r+ai las rngam tshul ston //
NK038(nyi)003:1039: ngag gi dbang phyug rta gdong zhabs kyis gnon //
NK038(nyi)003:1041: sngo nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:1042: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad ma //
NK038(nyi)003:1043: rdo rje gshog pas bar snang khebs //
NK038(nyi)003:1044: ba spu'i lcags kyu bsreg pa 'dra //
NK038(nyi)003:1045: sdom dang sdig pa smig pa sbrul //
NK038(nyi)003:1046: 'jigs pa'i gzugs kyis sa gzhi khyab //
NK038(nyi)003:1047: thod skyogs ti ra sbrul zhags dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1048: nyi zla khyung dang 'ug pa khra //
NK038(nyi)003:1049: za ra rdo rje mdung rtse gsum pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1050: za ma tog dang rdul yab rnga //
NK038(nyi)003:1051: ri rab phyi bskor stong gsum 'phen //
NK038(nyi)003:1052: klu dbang 'bum gyis brgyan cing klubs //
NK038(nyi)003:1053: dus mtha'i bskal pa'i me bzhin 'bar //
NK038(nyi)003:1054: khro gnyer sdang mig 'bar ba yis //
NK038(nyi)003:1055: nyi shu rtsa brgyad spyan ras gzigs //
NK038(nyi)003:1056: zhabs kyi 'bar ba'i lha brgyad mnan //
NK038(nyi)003:1057: rdo rje srin po khro bor gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:1058: lha dang bdud las rnam par grags //
NK038(nyi)003:1059: che mchog thugs kyi sprul ba las //
NK038(nyi)003:1060: lha chen nag po mi bzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1061: mtsho ni kang ka thang dmar na //
NK038(nyi)003:1062: ri bo byan rlag 'byongs kyi rtse //
NK038(nyi)003:1063: ma la ya yi rtse la lhags //
NK038(nyi)003:1064: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje las //
NK038(nyi)003:1065: sprul pa'i sras mchog rdo rje 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)003:1066: gzhon nu bye ba sa yar mdzad //
NK038(nyi)003:1067: bam ri thod pa mkhar gyi rtser //
NK038(nyi)003:1068: mgon po'i thugs kyi sprul pa las //
NK038(nyi)003:1069: bdud kyi spyod yul kun mdzad de //
NK038(nyi)003:1070: drag tu basngagasa cing bskul ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)003:1071: 'jig rten khams kun phung bar byed //
NK038(nyi)003:1072: thams cad dbyar gyi sprin phung bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:1073: nam mkha'i khams kyi mtha' klas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1074: bam ri thod pa'i rtse la lhags //
NK038(nyi)003:1075: mthun 'jugs thabs kyi cha byad du //
NK038(nyi)003:1076: bam ri thod pa mkhar gyi rtse //
NK038(nyi)003:1077: khrag dang gshang gci sha chen dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1078: rkang dang klad pa klad rgyas dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1079: rnag dang chu ser la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1081: sbrang ma sbrang rgod bung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1082: sbrul dang sdig pa sdoms la sogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1083: ka ka kha keg 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1084: lce spyang stag seng la sogs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:1085: gdug pa sbrul gyi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:1086: lha yi ded dpon ka ru na'i //
NK038(nyi)003:1087: bu mo chung ma sring mo dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1088: 'jig rten dbang phyug lha chen gyis /
NK038(nyi)003:1089: chung ma bu mo ma sring rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:1090: phrogs nas dbang du byas pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:1091: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1092: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad la sogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1093: ma mo phra men gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1094: srin mo sha za khrag phrog ma //
NK038(nyi)003:1095: bdud kyi bla 'dzin bla rkun ma //
NK038(nyi)003:1096: dam nyams 'di yi barla la ya //
NK038(nyi)003:1097: blon mo dmag ded dmag dpon mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1098: ru mtshon nag po phyar nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1099: ru dpon pho nya mngag par bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:1100: rang rang bstan dang lag char ldan //
NK038(nyi)003:1101: ci bgyi bka' nyan bka' sdod 'khor //
NK038(nyi)003:1102: rbod gtong rngam pas dgra snying khos //
NK038(nyi)003:1103: srid pa'i bu mo dri za brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:1104: stag seng wa spyang bzhad sogs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1105: dur bya bya rog 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1106: bstod cing rngam pa'i tshul du 'khod //
NK038(nyi)003:1107: nyams pa 'di yi snying dkyil du //
NK038(nyi)003:1108: cho 'phrul sna tshogs khyed la bsregs //
NK038(nyi)003:1109: srin po nye gnas chen po brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:1110: ke'u ri tse'u ri pra mo ha //
NK038(nyi)003:1111: pe ta li dang puk+ka si //
NK038(nyi)003:1112: kasma ri dang sman sha ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1113: tsan+d+ha li la sogs pa yin //
NK038(nyi)003:1114: srog la hur thum dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:1115: dur khrod pa yi sgo bsrung bzhi //
NK038(nyi)003:1116: brtson mo sdeng mo gar log mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1117: de bzhin mjug mo chen mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)003:1118: gsang sgo 'dzin cing bka' srungs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1120: bar cad bsrung ba'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:1121: dam nyams 'di yi yan lag chings //
NK038(nyi)003:1122: dur khrod bdag mo gru der ma //
NK038(nyi)003:1123: skam ma shin tu skam ma dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1124: ra ro ma dang khrag 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)003:1125: chags pas myos pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod //
NK038(nyi)003:1126: dam nyams 'di yi dbugs long la //
NK038(nyi)003:1127: smyo 'bog gtong 'di pho nya ring mos grub bya ba'i dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)003:1128: nyams su mtshan ma byung na gdab las bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1129: myong bar khros dal gong ma bzhi dus na /
NK038(nyi)003:1130: sngon du bsnyen phul mnga' gsol ba'i //
NK038(nyi)003:1131: mtshon cha nag po thogs nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1132: skabs der thun zor brdeg par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1133: bde gshegs rgyal ba ma lus kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:1134: mar ji bzhin nyid lta bu phyag rgya dngos grub
NK038(nyi)003:1135: byang chub sems dpa' bsod nams tshe spyod par bzhi
NK038(nyi)003:1136: khu lta bu'i snying por gsungs /
NK038(nyi)003:1137: de 'dra'i bstan pa dam pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:1139: de ltar rnal 'byor nga yi dgra //
NK038(nyi)003:1140: pho nya mngag gzhug ma lus kun //
NK038(nyi)003:1142: drag po'i las kyi dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:1143: rdo rje gzhon nu rme ba brtsegs //
NK038(nyi)003:1144: mthing nag khro gnyer ral pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:1145: 'bar ba chen po gar dgu mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:1146: dur khrod bdag po ji bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)003:1147: dbu dang phyag zhabs der mdzad de //
NK038(nyi)003:1148: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:1149: rdo rje zla rtsal nyi ma'i mdangs can dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1150: rdo rje sed+ge nam mkha' rdo rje dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1151: rdo rje spyang khyi rdo rje dus mtshams dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1152: rdo rje phyogs 'dul rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:1153: rdo rje ro langs rdo rje ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1154: legs ldan nag po bdud kyi rje //
NK038(nyi)003:1155: gsung gi nga ro drag po mi bzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1156: 'ur 'ur chems chem drag po'i sgra dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)003:1157: rab tu brtsegs pa'i sku ni mi zad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1158: 'gul ldeg rab g.yo dgra la thun //
NK038(nyi)003:1159: dpa' bo khyod kyi shes rab la //
NK038(nyi)003:1160: bam ri thod pa brtsegs pa'i dbus //
NK038(nyi)003:1161: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i gzer chen gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:1162: brten par btab pa'i nad bdag mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1163: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:1164: thod skyogs khrag gis bkang ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1166: rtag par rang gi longs spyod 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)003:1167: chags pas myos shing skam pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:1168: ched 'ga' drag tu bskul ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)003:1169: sngags sgra drag po mi zad pas //
NK038(nyi)003:1170: rang la rang yang tshig bcad gtum //
NK038(nyi)003:1171: srin po srin mo pho mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1172: drag po'i rang sngags rang zlos shing //
NK038(nyi)003:1173: gdug pa'i lus can mtshon char bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:1174: klad pa'i dkyil du rgyab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:1175: rkang pa'i mthil du sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)003:1176: a bi ra tsi rnag pa'i yin //
NK038(nyi)003:1177: a bi ra rnag pa zer ba'ang 'dug /
NK038(nyi)003:1178: thun 'jug sbyor ba'i sgo nas bstan pa la gnod pa sgral ba 'khrid pa'i thabs sbyar gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:1179: bdud rtsi 'dab sbyor bas zer bas lnga'i mdangs 'byor ba //
NK038(nyi)003:1180: snang ba lnga ni bdud rtsir sbyar //
NK038(nyi)003:1181: byas la mi sog 'phrin las dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1182: spyod pa ma chags ye shes kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:1183: thams cad stong nyid rdo rjer sbyar //
NK038(nyi)003:1184: sgyu ma'i phung po lhag ma la //
NK038(nyi)003:1185: khro bo khro mo'i rta bro brdungs //
NK038(nyi)003:1186: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum //
NK038(nyi)003:1187: gnon 'phrin las bzhi'i bro btab bya'o 'og sha khrag rus spungs lhag ma rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:1188: drag po'i sbyin bsregs brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:1189: rtsal 'byor khros pa'i sems kyis bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1190: lid+ga gcad cing bsregs pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:1191: sangs rgyas nyid kyang 'jigs gyur na //
NK038(nyi)003:1192: gzhan lta smos kyang ci zhig dgos //
NK038(nyi)003:1194: gtad khram gnan pa'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK038(nyi)003:1195: bdud 'dul zhing khams chen po na //
NK038(nyi)003:1196: ston pa gsang bdag nyid kyis gsungs //
NK038(nyi)003:1197: de yi gdam ngag rgyud pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1198: slob dpon h'u ka ra yi ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1199: de yi gdam ngag mdor bkod pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1200: gong du las nyams blangs pa ni la sbyar bas na //
NK038(nyi)003:1201: sa sna mi phung shul la grog mkhar sa sna'i sa gsum gyi 'dag pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:1202: tshad dang rab chad nag mo'i thod pa ldan pa'i mkhar byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:1203: steng du khyi nag po'i thod pa srin po'i mes
NK038(nyi)003:1204: sel pa bya khyung rgyal po sngon 'byung dus dang
NK038(nyi)003:1205: // nang du mon pa nag po ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1206: mche gtsigs zhabs ni bgrad pa'i thog /
NK038(nyi)003:1207: sbyin bsreg byas pa'i thal ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1208: dri ma dmigs pa'i la sogs rjes rnams la //
NK038(nyi)003:1209: lid+ga ming byang bris te bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:1210: a mdze phyi dgu ra ma nu sha spre'u thod dang ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1211: kri sna rab chad kyi mon thod par ku ku ra bzhi yi //
NK038(nyi)003:1212: thod pa kha sbyar zhags pas bsdams //
NK038(nyi)003:1213: ka ru na'i phyag myung dang rgya bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:1214: ming byang gnam lcags 'bar ba'i gzer chen gyis /
NK038(nyi)003:1215: blangs te dur khrod nag po'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1216: mi mthun tsakra bris la mkhar nag gi pa yi rtsar song la dri nag gri /
NK038(nyi)003:1217: gtor ma la sogs mgon nag 'khor bcas lha khang mgon po'i 'og tu gzhug go rngan pas mchod /
NK038(nyi)003:1218: gru gsum khru do rkos byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:1219: gong gi mkhar chen bcug nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1220: g.yam pa nag pos kha bcad nas //
NK038(nyi)003:1221: rdo rje rgya gram gyis mnan bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1222: mgo shar nub tu chu 'bab pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1224: phyogs su rkang 'dom rtsa la sar za byang /
NK038(nyi)003:1225: chu mig nag po ma rungs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1226: lha khang mgon po'i zhabs 'og tu //
NK038(nyi)003:1227: mnan pa byas dang 'grub par gsung //
NK038(nyi)003:1228: gtad khram mnan pa'i dkyil 'khor ro /
NK038(nyi)003:1229: de rding kun gyi 'jug bsdu ba sgrub pa'i gnas phyin nas //
NK038(nyi)003:1230: 'jig rten phyag rgya dngos grub kyi 'das dang 'jig rten bka' bsdod pho nya pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:1231: spyan drangs lha rnams ma lus pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1232: mchod bstod bshags pa bya ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1233: gtang rag lhag ma'i gtor ma gtang //
NK038(nyi)003:1234: de nas dbyings su ci bder gshegs //
NK038(nyi)003:1235: bskyed pa'i lha rnams ma lus bsdu //
NK038(nyi)003:1236: mtshams dang phyag rgya la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1237: ngo bo nyid kyis dgrol bar byas //
NK038(nyi)003:1238: smon lam btab cing spyod lam la //
NK038(nyi)003:1239: sgyu ma'i tshul du ci bder spyad //
NK038(nyi)003:1240: grub rdzogs rim so dang lung bstan ma thob kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:1241: bdag la blo dman ched du ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1242: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i sgrub thabs phye //
NK038(nyi)003:1243: tshad ma dang ldan mkhas pa rnams /
NK038(nyi)003:1244: bdag gi blo la mi bya zhing //
NK038(nyi)003:1245: dam pa rnams kyis bzod par bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:1247: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid thob shog /
NK038(nyi)003:1248: slob dpon tir ma ti'i dgongs pa la /
NK038(nyi)003:1249: rdo rje bkod pa chen po'i rgyud kyi man ngag bstan pa bsrung ba'i rnal 'byor /
NK038(nyi)003:1250: dkyil 'khor tha ma gsum gyis bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1251: yongs kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po'i sgrub thabs
NK038(nyi)003:1252: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i rim pa rnams par phye ba
NK038(nyi)003:1253: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug rnam par snang mdzad myu
NK038(nyi)003:1256: bka' sdod pho nya'i dam la gsum ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1257: dang po sngon du byung ba'i dal la gsum ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1258: dang po sngon du byung ba'i rim pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1259: gdam ngag yod tsam zhig bstan par dam bca' bar bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1260: bka' sdod zhes pa nas 'dir bkod pa zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1261: bka' sdod pho nya'i dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1262: zhes pas bar chad bsrung ba'i don du bstan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1263: sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa'i zhes pa ni mtshan //
NK038(nyi)003:1264: zhing khams ces pas dbul lo //
NK038(nyi)003:1265: mngon par dga' ba ni ming ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:1266: rgyal tshab skyes bu ni ston pa kun tu bzang
NK038(nyi)003:1267: po de'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i gdam ngag mdor bkod
NK038(nyi)003:1269: gnyis pa dam rdzas dang yo byad bsham pa'i rim pa bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1270: rtags zhes pa nas mkhar du brtsigs zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1271: rtags dang brten ni gzhung ltar bshams zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1272: rten thod pa sna tshogs pa'i mkhar du brtsig pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1273: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1274: ru tra nag po de dang po skye ba snga
NK038(nyi)003:1275: ma la smad 'tshong ma'i mngal du zhugs nas btsas
NK038(nyi)003:1276: pa'i dus su ma shi nas ma'i ro dur khrod
NK038(nyi)003:1277: du bskyal bas / ru tra nag po de yang
NK038(nyi)003:1278: ma'i ro'i rtsar bzhag pas cher skyes nas dur bya
NK038(nyi)003:1279: du bskyal bas / kang ka dang / za byed
NK038(nyi)003:1280: dur phag la sogs bsnyen pa'i dus kyi ri bsad
NK038(nyi)003:1281: du bskyal bas / kang ka dang / du 'jug
NK038(nyi)003:1282: pa'o // mtsho kang ka thang dmar byan slag 'chongs
NK038(nyi)003:1284: ri de'i steng na 'dab chags kyi rgyal po zhes pa bya khyung gnas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1285: kim rus thod pa mkhar du gtsigs zhes pa ni
NK038(nyi)003:1286: gong du bshad par bya ba de rnams bsam par
NK038(nyi)003:1287: bya ba las dngos su byar med do //
NK038(nyi)003:1288: de la dang por stegs bu gru bzhi pa rgyar gru bzhi pa'am /
NK038(nyi)003:1289: khru do la sogs pas brgyan pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1290: de'i steng du rak+ta mam sa sha chen btsos pa'i khu ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1291: byang sems kyi chag chag gdab la /
NK038(nyi)003:1292: de'i steng du shog 'dam la mkhar gru bzhi pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1293: dpangs su khru gang de'i sum gnyis pa gcig rtsigs la /
NK038(nyi)003:1294: de'i phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi gdod pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1296: de'i zur bzhir khyung mgo re re /
NK038(nyi)003:1297: g.yas g.yon gnyis la khyung mgo re re ste drug go //
NK038(nyi)003:1298: khyung mgo'i spyi bo na yar dar nag po lce gsum pa re btsugs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1299: mkhar de'i nang du gru gsum 'brub khung bcug la /
NK038(nyi)003:1300: de'i nang du gsang ba'i mgon po'i gzugs kyi 'og tu lid+ga gcig gzhug go //
NK038(nyi)003:1301: gsal shing la gzungs thag gnyis btags la mkhar gyi mthong khung na mar bcug pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1302: gsal shing gi dbal lid+ga'i thog tu 'ong bar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1303: 'brub khung de'i nang du yum gyis rdzas thod tshal dang 'bru mar te /
NK038(nyi)003:1304: mar nag dang rdzas lnga ste bdud rtsi rnams dang phud la sogs pa bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)003:1305: skyed pa'i rgya mdud ni med de /
NK038(nyi)003:1306: gsal shing gi dpal gru gsum la logs gcig la mgon po'i bsnyen sngags bris /
NK038(nyi)003:1307: logs gcig la mi khrag gis dmar por byug go //
NK038(nyi)003:1308: de'i shul nyag gis btang ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1309: spyi bo'i rgya mdud yod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1310: de ni mgon po'i yum gyi rdzas so //
NK038(nyi)003:1311: de nas mkhar gyi lho phyogs sgo'i thad kar 'grub
NK038(nyi)003:1312: khung gcig rtse mo lhor bstan logs mkhar la yong
NK038(nyi)003:1313: bar bskyed de bar bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)003:1314: de'i nang du lid+ga gcig gzhug /
NK038(nyi)003:1315: de'i steng du thod zor dang mda' zor dang rdo
NK038(nyi)003:1316: zor la sogs pa yak+sha gnod sbyin gyi rdzas bshams
NK038(nyi)003:1317: pa'o // shar du sgo'i thad kar 'grub khung bca' ba gong dang mthun /
NK038(nyi)003:1318: de'i nang du lid+ga gzhug pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1319: de'i steng du phur pa'i rnam pa mchog phur dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1321: lcags phur la sogs pa khro bo gong gi rdzas gzhug pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1322: byang du sgo'i thad kar 'brub khung dang lid+ga bca' ba gong dang mthun /
NK038(nyi)003:1323: steng du ma mo'i gling che ba'am chung ba gang
NK038(nyi)003:1324: rung gcig gzhag pa ni za byed ma mo'i rdzas
NK038(nyi)003:1325: so // nub tu sgo'i thad kar 'brub khung dang lid+ga bca' ba mthun /
NK038(nyi)003:1326: de'i steng du yungs dkar dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1332: dug la sogs pa thun rdzas bzhags pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1333: rak+sha srin po'i dam rdzas so //
NK038(nyi)003:1334: de nas lho phyogs su las kyi man+dala sum brtsegs bya ba ni 'og nas ston no //
NK038(nyi)003:1335: de'i nang du lid+ga che ba gcig bcug la /
NK038(nyi)003:1336: skye nas gzungs thag sngon dmar btags la gsal shing
NK038(nyi)003:1337: gis gzungs thag gnyis yod pa'i ya gcig la gdags
NK038(nyi)003:1338: so // lid+ga rangs sa bag zan la bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1339: rjes sa dang dri ma la sogs pa bsreg pa ni gzhan dang mthun no //
NK038(nyi)003:1340: de'i man+dala gsum brtsegs khar bsgrub pa chen po'i dus su /
NK038(nyi)003:1342: tshogs byed pa'i lid+ga la sogs pa'i 'brub khung gcig rtsigs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1343: de'i nang du lid+ga de nang du bcug pa nyid phye nas bsgral /
NK038(nyi)003:1344: nyi phyed na bcug pa dgong mo bsgral ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1346: de nas mnan pa byed tsam na /
NK038(nyi)003:1347: thod pa'i steng du gnon pa'i mkhar gru gsum khru
NK038(nyi)003:1348: gang pa khyung mgo drug dang ldan pas so btang
NK038(nyi)003:1349: ba gcig baca'o // thod pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1351: mdze thod rabs chad nag po'i thod pa la sogs pa bsham mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1352: de ltar rdzas bshams pas brtags ni skye ba mang du blangs pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1354: 'dir gnag dang sgra dang slob dpon dang chos grogs su yongs ste rtags tha ma'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1355: rab ni mngon sum du yer gyis 'ong ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:1356: 'bring ni gnyid khris kyi byung ba'am /
NK038(nyi)003:1357: yang na dam rdzas bsngosa pa'am /
NK038(nyi)003:1358: bcol byed pa'i dus su skad 'don te ci yang yong ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:1359: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa la bcu bzhi las /
NK038(nyi)003:1360: dang po kho nar drag po 'khor dang bcas pa bskyed pa bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1361: ru las zhes pa nas ldan par bskyed zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1363: dang po mkhar dang stegs bu mi dmigs pa las bam rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:1365: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho gcig tu gyur pa na /
NK038(nyi)003:1366: mtsho ko thang dmar gyi ded pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1367: de nas mkhar nang du ru lho'i lcags khang 'brub khung yang /
NK038(nyi)003:1375: dbus kyi ru zhu ba las gri gug rus mtshan pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1376: lho'i ya zhu ba las mdung yas mtshan pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1377: shar du ba zhu ba las phur pa bas mtshan pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1378: byang du ma zhu ba las /
NK038(nyi)003:1379: b+han+d+ha mas mtshan ma nub tu ra zhu ba las mda' gzhu ras mtshan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1380: de rnams ra pa sa zhu ba las /
NK038(nyi)003:1381: dbus su mgon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1382: g.yas gri gug g.yon b+han+d+ha 'dzin pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1383: de'i logs mo'i phyi 'khor gnyis kyi steng du /
NK038(nyi)003:1385: rtsibs log g.yas su dred mo lag rdebs gnyis /
NK038(nyi)003:1386: rtsibs log g.yon par 'phar ba rkang rdebs /
NK038(nyi)003:1387: s+t+aa zur te dpung pa g.yas g.yon seng ge gnyis /
NK038(nyi)003:1389: phyag na klu mtha' yas mgo gsum lus po sbrul du 'dug pa mjug ma zhal du gsol ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1390: klu'i lag pa g.yon khar bcug pa srin po kha phyir lta ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1391: yum nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma ni mgon
NK038(nyi)003:1392: po dang 'khril nas 'khor na 'brub khung gi nang
NK038(nyi)003:1393: na yod pa'o // lhor yak+sha gnod sbyin zangs thogs rgyal po dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1394: yum bswe gdong ma zangs gri rdzu 'phrul can /
NK038(nyi)003:1395: bswe'i skyes bu drug zor gyi rgyal mo mched bzhi'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1396: shar du gtso bo ljang sngon lag na gsal shing
NK038(nyi)003:1397: thogs pa ni lag pa gnyis ka gsal shing la
NK038(nyi)003:1398: 'jus nas 'jal zhing ma mu du btsugs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1399: de'i mthar phyin gyi ging bzhi bcu zhe gnyis /
NK038(nyi)003:1400: 'dzin ging chen po bco brgyad gying gi gtso mo bcu gnyis dgod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1401: byang du dbus su dkar mo phrag gong gnyis su
NK038(nyi)003:1402: nyi zlas brgyan pa'i mtha' 'khor du dkar smug gsum
NK038(nyi)003:1407: nub tu srin mo mgo dgu pa sring mo gdong mo bzhi /
NK038(nyi)003:1408: 'khor gyi lha srin sde brgyad dgod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1409: yang de rnams rags pa cho gas mi bskyed pa ru /
NK038(nyi)003:1410: ya ba ma ra zhes brjod pas de rnams krong krong grub par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1411: ru las tshogs bdag bskyed nas ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1412: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma /
NK038(nyi)003:1413: rang gi 'khor tshogs ldan par bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:1415: gnyis pa drag po'i gnas nas dgug pa bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1416: de nas zhes pa na gdug pa dgug zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1417: de nas dpa' bo chen po zhes pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1419: ru lu ru lu'i 'od zer spros pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1420: bdag he ru kar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu lta bus lho nub mtshams su /
NK038(nyi)003:1422: mathe'u chung gnyis sbrel mdzub mo lcags kyu ltar byas te /
NK038(nyi)003:1423: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:1424: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya hrim
NK038(nyi)003:1425: hrim hrim am ku sha dza dzah zhes pa lan
NK038(nyi)003:1426: gsum 'am lnga'am ci gsal du brjod pas mgon po
NK038(nyi)003:1428: re byan lag mchongs kyi ri rtse /
NK038(nyi)003:1429: ma la ya'i rtse nas rang gi mdun du 'dug par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1430: drag po gnas nas 'dug pa dgug ces pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1431: gsum pa zhal du rngub cing bstim pa ming gi
NK038(nyi)003:1432: rnam grangs dang bcas pa bstan pa ni zhal du
NK038(nyi)003:1433: bzhes pa nas / nag yin zhes pas bstan te zhal du rngub ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1434: sna nas bton zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1435: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:1438: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ru tra ma tra ha ha ham /
NK038(nyi)003:1440: bdag dpal du gsal bas brjod pas mdun na gnas
NK038(nyi)003:1441: pa'i mgon po de dag gi zhal du rngub gyur
NK038(nyi)003:1442: gyi mig / de sna nas bton nas mkhar nang du bskyed pa'i mgon po la bstim mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1444: bzhi pa 'jug par gsol ba gdab pa ni tshogs
NK038(nyi)003:1445: zhes pa nas bzung du gsol zhes pas bstan te
NK038(nyi)003:1446: / tshogs bdag zhes pas mgon po des dpa' bo chen po zhes bos nas gsol ba gdab pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1448: lnga pa byin gyis brlab cing zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1449: dpa' bo zhes pa nas slar mi ldog zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1450: tshogs bdag zhes pas mgon po /
NK038(nyi)003:1451: gong du mgon pos dpa' bo nas gsol ba btab pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1452: dpa' bo chen pos bka' rtsal pa zhes pas bdag badz+ra he ru ka'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1453: h'u h'u nas mum h'u gis byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1454: de'i 'og skal ldan zhes pa la sogs pa ni ting nge 'dzin gyis brjod par bsam pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1455: drug pa drag pos byang chub tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1456: tshogs bdag ces pa nas mjug par bgyi zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1457: tshogs bdag chen pos yang gsol pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1459: dpa' bos byin gyis brlabs spro ba bskyed pa nas /
NK038(nyi)003:1460: mgon pos yang dpa' bo la 'di skad gsol zhes pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1462: bdun pa dpas bos sems bskyed pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1463: rdo rje lta ba'i sgo nas dam tshig dbog pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1464: dpa' bo zhes pa nas dus med do zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1465: de dag thams cad ting nge 'dzin gyis yud tsam bsam te sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1466: brgyad pa drag pos phyag 'tshal zhing dbang bskur bar gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1467: nag po chen pos zhes pa nas dbang bskur zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1468: dgu pa dpa' bos dbang bskur ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1469: dpa' bo chen pos snang zhes pa ni bdag he ru ka ra gsal bas /
NK038(nyi)003:1470: badz+ra a mri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aa /
NK038(nyi)003:1471: zhes brjod pas dbang bskur bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1472: bcu pa drag pos dbang blang cing dbang yon dbul
NK038(nyi)003:1473: bar bstan pa ni nag po chen po zhes pa
NK038(nyi)003:1474: nas dbul te gnas pas bstan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1475: de thams cad ting nge 'dzin gyis bya ba sla ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1476: bcu gcig pa drag pos zhal gyis bzhes shing mna' bskyal bar bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1477: dkrugs nas bstan te 'og ma gi nas de ltar
NK038(nyi)003:1478: mchod zhes pa nas tshad du bzhag ces pa nas
NK038(nyi)003:1479: bstan te sla'o // bcu gnyis pa dpa' bos zhal
NK038(nyi)003:1480: gyis bzhes shing zil gyis mnan nas dbang bsdu bas
NK038(nyi)003:1481: bstan te sla'o // bstan pa ni / de'i 'og nas dpa' bo chen po zhes pa nas /
NK038(nyi)003:1482: bka' la btags zhes pas bstan go sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1483: bcu gsum pa drag po 'khor dang bcas pa la mchod pa btab cing mnga' gsol bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1484: gong nas de nas gying gi zhes pa nas /
NK038(nyi)003:1485: blang byar byos zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1486: 'og de ka dka' thub chen po zhes pa nas /
NK038(nyi)003:1487: longs spyod zhes pas mgon po yab yum la bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1488: gnod sbyin zhes pa nas rang gi 'dod pa'i longs spyod kyis /
NK038(nyi)003:1489: zhes pas yak+sha gnod sbyin la bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1491: dngos grub gsol zhes pa ni shar gyis bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1493: bzhes zhes pas byang gi ma mo la bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1495: 'thung zhes pas nub kyi srin po la bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1496: sprul pa'i zhes pa nas bzhengs zhes pa ni yum la bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1497: rigs ngan zhes pa nas rims nad thong zhes pas phyir bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1498: srid pa'i zhes pa nas sgrubs zhes pa 'khor lo bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1499: gsang tshig zhes pa nas grub par gyis zhes pa rang la bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1500: mnga' bdag zhes pa nas blang bar gyis zhes pas gtso bo btab nas bsngo ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1501: bcu bzhi pa srog gi dbang po mdongs gsol du dbul la /
NK038(nyi)003:1502: bsnyen bsgrub yan lag ji ltar bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1503: rdo rje lcags kyi zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1504: pho nya mngag gzhug dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)003:1506: rdo rje ljags kyi 'od zer las rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ru tra ma tra ha ha ha /
NK038(nyi)003:1507: zhes bsdus te bzlas pa bya zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1508: sngags de nyid ru lu dang sbrel la mang du bzlas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1510: dbang du 'dus par 'gyur zhes bsnyen pa'i bzlas pa
NK038(nyi)003:1511: 'bum byas la zhes pa ni bsnyen pa'i dus su
NK038(nyi)003:1512: rang gi snying ga nas 'od 'phros pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1513: phyogs dus de bzhin gshegs pa spyan drangs la zhes bdag rang la bstim /
NK038(nyi)003:1514: yang phar 'phros pa'i 'od zer mkhar nang gi mgon
NK038(nyi)003:1515: po la thim pas mgon po gzi brjid bskyed la
NK038(nyi)003:1516: bzhugs pa'o // don chen rtsal ba zhes su bshad zhes pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1518: bur kur zhes pas bsnyen pa 'bum du bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1519: thun mtshams su kun tu mchod pa yang zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1520: thun mtshams su gtso bo cha gnyis la mar me la mar me chad pa ltar byas la /
NK038(nyi)003:1522: nang du log nas dal gyi 'khor la chu la chu thim pa ltar bsres la mchod pa bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1523: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpa' he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)003:1524: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la /
NK038(nyi)003:1525: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul /
NK038(nyi)003:1526: thugs rje che dgong dbang dang dngos grub stsol /
NK038(nyi)003:1527: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:1528: de nas mgon po la dbul te /
NK038(nyi)003:1529: rnal 'byor yongs kyi bstan pa bsrung ba zhal bzhes pa'i /
NK038(nyi)003:1530: dpal ldan mgon po legs ldan nag po la /
NK038(nyi)003:1531: rnam dag thug rje na mo sman mchod ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1532: mgon po ni sngags bzhi la stong rtsa re bskyal ba dang mchod pa re bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1534: ma g.yel gyi bskang ba re byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:1535: yang gtso bo gnyis su byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:1536: bzlas pa byed par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1537: nang par thun la 'jug tsa na yang dag gtso bo dang bsres la mchod pa gong ltar bya'o //
