NK038(nyi)003:1538: ma 'phangs ma g.yel gyi bskang ba byed dus gsur chen btang la bskang ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:1539: bcol rangs pa gtong ba yang srid de khams dang sbyar ro //
NK038(nyi)003:1542: don chen rnyed par gyur pa ni mtshan ma bzang po byung ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1543: de'i dus su nye ba'i bsnyen pa ni sna'i bu ga'i dbugs rings la zhes pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1544: dbugs phar rgyu tshur rgyu'i dus su gyur pa h'u
NK038(nyi)003:1545: las 'phros pas khro bo mang po spros nas des
NK038(nyi)003:1546: mgon po bskul / yang 'od 'phros la gsang ba'i mgon po phyogs bcu nas bkug la /
NK038(nyi)003:1547: mkhar nag gi mgon po la bkug la bstim te
NK038(nyi)003:1548: kha dog la sogs pa ni dkyus la gsol lo
NK038(nyi)003:1549: // rgyu zhags mkhar sku sa'i zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1551: gsal shing la btags pa'i gzugs te gnyis bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1552: lho phyogs las kyi man+dala gsum rtseg nang gi //
NK038(nyi)003:1554: gcig rang gi lag tu bzungs te /
NK038(nyi)003:1555: mthing nag dar chen 'bar ba la phye mar ril bu gsum bsgrubs te /
NK038(nyi)003:1558: dar mthing gi khud du thum bu dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1559: bdud rtsi sman gyi thum bu gcig bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1560: bar pa la yungs dkar gyi thum po gcig bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1561: tha ma la khrag gi thum po gcig byas te /
NK038(nyi)003:1562: gzungs thag la btags la thum po gsum po ma nor bas /
NK038(nyi)003:1563: rang gi lag pa g.yon par blangs la gzungs thag blangs te /
NK038(nyi)003:1564: sngags bzlas te nye ba'i snying po //
NK038(nyi)003:1565: bur ku kusma zhes pa'i sngags 'bum du bzlas pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1566: don chen rnyed pa ni mtshan rtags byung ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1567: de nas don la 'jug par bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1569: thun mtshams su lag pa'i thum po bar pa yungs dkar kha phye nas bskul bas /
NK038(nyi)003:1571: khro bos mgon po las la bskul //
NK038(nyi)003:1572: rang gi lag pa g.yon pas thum bu kha phye bas //
NK038(nyi)003:1573: mkhar gyi nang du pho nyas bskul zhes pas //
NK038(nyi)003:1574: yungs kar mkhar nang du brab pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1575: 'bum du bsgrub pa dag ni bzlas zhes pa ku
NK038(nyi)003:1576: ru ku ru zhes pa'i sngags 'bum du bzlas pa'o
NK038(nyi)003:1577: // de nas bsgrub pa chen po la 'jug pa'i dus su tshor bzhing tshogs su btang ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1578: de nas tshogs kyi mchod pa ni gsum du byas te dbul byas te /
NK038(nyi)003:1579: zhes pa ni nyin mo gsum /
NK038(nyi)003:1580: nam gung dang bzhir dbul te /
NK038(nyi)003:1582: tshogs byed pa'i dus su gong gi bsod nams kyis
NK038(nyi)003:1583: dkyil 'khor bzhin du mchod pa dang bshags pa dang
NK038(nyi)003:1584: / bskang ba ni gsum ni gong du bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1585: bar pa la rnams 'byor pas rol te de'i lhag ma bsags la /
NK038(nyi)003:1586: bsgrub pa thon tsam na lhag ma'i tshogs mchod pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1587: tha ma la yang ling+ga byas la /
NK038(nyi)003:1588: lho phyogs su ling+ga sogs 'brub khung du bsags te /
NK038(nyi)003:1589: da nang bsags pa nyin phyed na bsgral la gzugs po mchod par gong ltar stabs /
NK038(nyi)003:1590: mgo bsags la mnan pa'am sbyin bsreg bya ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1591: ling+ga la dgra bo'i shes pa dgug pa la sogs pa 'agre'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1592: de bzhin du nyin phyed kyi ling+ga dgongs mo bsgral /
NK038(nyi)003:1593: dgongs ka'i ling+ga nam phyed na bsgral /
NK038(nyi)003:1594: nam phyed kyi ling+ga nangs par bsgral lo //
NK038(nyi)003:1595: steng du gyur pa'i gsang mchog gi bsgrub pa chen po'i sngags so //
NK038(nyi)003:1596: de'i dus su thum tha ma khrag sna'i thum bus mkhar nang du bskul bas /
NK038(nyi)003:1597: dang po'i dam tshig dran par bsam pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1598: bsgrub pa chen po 'bum du bzlas zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1599: b+hu ra kur ti zhes pa'i sngags bzlas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1600: pho nya mngag gzhug dkyil 'khor zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1604: shin tu dkyus nas gsal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:1605: gnyis pa nyams su blang ba'i rim pa dngos la gnyis las /
NK038(nyi)003:1606: dang po las dang bya bas rdzas bshams pa'i rim pa bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1607: lho phyogs zhes pa nas rten la 'dud zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1608: lho phyogs las kyi man+dala gsum rtseg la zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1609: 'brub khung gi rgyar khru gang pa pangs su khru
NK038(nyi)003:1610: phyed pa nang thang ba la phyi rim gsum du
NK038(nyi)003:1611: brtsegs pa'o // dang po thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)003:1613: bang rim dang po la thod pa'ii phreng ba gdag pa la 'bur du gtod pa'am /
NK038(nyi)003:1614: yang na bang rim la ri mo legs par bri'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1615: de 'og mtshon gyis spras zhes pa ni bang rim bar pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1616: dngos su mtshon cha gri'am mda' 'am ral gri la sogs pa'am /
NK038(nyi)003:1618: de 'og me ri 'bar ba 'phros zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1619: bang rim tha ma'i logs la me ri bri ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1621: ji lta ba'i tshul du bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:1623: ling+ga'i rgyu dri chen dri chu gos dang rjes sa dang bag phye bsgo bsdus la /
NK038(nyi)003:1625: yan lag skud pa sngo dmar gyis dkris la bzhags pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1626: de la yan lag rgya bzhi yis rgyang zhes pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1627: kha rad na dang po phra men ma /
NK038(nyi)003:1629: bang rim dang po la phur pa brgyad la ke'u ri khro bo mo brgyad du mos pa bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1631: bar pa la ni mgo brnyan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1632: bang rim bar pa la phur pa bcu gnyis la sing ha phra men brgyad /
NK038(nyi)003:1633: rta gdong sgo ma bzhir mos pa byas ste dgod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1634: tha ma la ni srin mo'i tshogs zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1635: bang rim tha ma la phur pa nyi shu rtsa
NK038(nyi)003:1636: brgyad dbang mo nyer brgyad du mos pa byas la
NK038(nyi)003:1637: gzug go // gdug pa'i phur pa zhes pa phur pa'i rgyu'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1638: mtshon par byas de rnams par dgod zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1639: koo sing dang dbang mor mos par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1640: mgul nas btags zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1641: 'brub khung de'i nang ling+ga'i mgul nas gzungs thag gis btags pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1643: mkhar nang gi gsal shing la 'dud pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1644: gnyis pa las la sbyar ba dngos bstan pa la drug ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1645: dang po gzu dpang gsol zhing dregs pa'i sngags bzlas
NK038(nyi)003:1646: pa stim zhes pa nas gzu dpang gsol zhes pas
NK038(nyi)003:1647: bstan te / gzhan rnams te go sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1648: ji srid mtshan ma ma byung gi bar zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1649: dgra sod pa'i rtags byung ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1650: las la sbyor pa drag po'i sngags ni bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1651: rngam pa'i nga ros gnon par bya zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1653: ma nyes lags gzu dpang zhes pa ni zor gtong ba'i skabs kyi gyer gtso 'dir blang ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1654: gnyis pa pho nyas mngag cing bskul ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1655: de nas pho nyas mngag ces pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1656: dus la bab zhes pas bstan to //
NK038(nyi)003:1657: de nas pho nyas bdag par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1658: 'bar ba'i drag po mi zad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1659: zhes pa ni khro bo ging gi tshogs so //
NK038(nyi)003:1660: rtog pa med pa'i rgyal po las //
NK038(nyi)003:1662: bdag dpal he ru kar gsal ba'i rdo rje'i ljags ni rdo rje yod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1663: badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la sa ma ya zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1664: khro bo'i sngags te sarba sha trum ma ra phata /
NK038(nyi)003:1665: zhes pa ni sngags bzhi ga sa ru btags pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1666: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin phung rnams zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1668: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya zhes pa ni srin po'i sngags so //
NK038(nyi)003:1669: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya zhes pa ni gnod sbyin rbad pa'i sngags so //
NK038(nyi)003:1670: tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya zhes pa ni za byed ma mo'i sngags so //
NK038(nyi)003:1671: sngags dang ming du spel nas ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1672: zhes rtsa sngags s+w+aa h+aa'i bar du ming gzhug pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1673: khros pas khri'am 'bum du bzlas zhes pa ni gong
NK038(nyi)003:1674: gi gzhi snying cig tu dril ba'i sngags 'bum rdzogs
NK038(nyi)003:1675: pa dang / 'khor bzhi'i ling sngags bzlas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1676: de yang gdam ngag gi dang por lho gnod sbyin bzlas /
NK038(nyi)003:1678: de nas nub srin po'i bzlas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1679: de na ma 'phangs ma g.yel gyi sham du 'di sbrel la bskul ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1680: thang chen gtag la bskul ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1681: zhes pa nas mar la bskul ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1682: de'i bsham du bskul ba ring mo yang sbrel lo //
NK038(nyi)003:1683: gsum pa mtshan ma ma byung na gdab pa'i las bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1684: sngon du bsnyen phur mnga' gsol la zhes pa ni
NK038(nyi)003:1685: bsnyen pa'i dus su mi bsad pa'i mtshon pas byas
NK038(nyi)003:1687: skabs der thun zor rdeg par bya zhes bya ba
NK038(nyi)003:1688: ni pho nya rnams kyi gsham zor gyi pho nya'i
NK038(nyi)003:1689: gong du yum gyi bskul pa 'di gzhug go //
NK038(nyi)003:1690: de nas ling+ga bzhi snying dril ba'i sngags bzlas shing gdab pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1691: bzhi pa sbyor ba'i tshogs bsgral ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1692: mthun 'jug zhes pa nas sbyangs zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1693: don la gnas par gsungs te zhib mo ni ma bstan /
NK038(nyi)003:1694: bsgral thabs ni gong gi 'khor bzhi'i sngags dang bzhi snying gcig tu 'gril ba'i gdam par 'gro ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1695: gong du bzhi snying dril ba'i sngags bzlas bas 'bum
NK038(nyi)003:1696: thon pa'i dus su ma 'phangs ma g.yel la sogs
NK038(nyi)003:1697: nas yum bskul ba man chad byas la /
NK038(nyi)003:1698: mkhar nang gi 'brub khung nang du nang gi ling+ga
NK038(nyi)003:1699: la mtshon cha nag pos bsgral la mgo bo bsag
NK038(nyi)003:1700: / lus po gtor ma'i nang du gong du bstan pa bzhin du btab pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1701: gnod sbyin gyi sngags khri'am 'bum thon pa'am bskul ba 'dra /
NK038(nyi)003:1705: de nas byang du de dang 'dra'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1706: lnga pa phung po lhag ma la bro brdungs zhing bstab pa bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1707: sgyu ma'i zhes pa nas zhal du bstab zhes pas bstan te sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1708: drug pa drag po'i sbyin bsreg gis las la sbyar ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1709: las rnams zhes pa nas ci zhig dgos zhes pas bstan te sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1710: gsum pa nges tshig bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1711: 'brub khung las kyi dkyil 'khor ro zhes pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1712: gtad khram mnan pa'i dal la gsum las /
NK038(nyi)003:1713: dang por sngon du byung ba'i rim pa bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1714: gtad khram zhes pa nas bkod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1715: zhes pas bstan pa shin tu sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1716: gnyis pa sgrub pa pos nyams su blang ba'i rim pa dngos la drug las /
NK038(nyi)003:1717: dang po mkhar gzugs brnyan bca' ba bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1719: bgrad pa'i srog zhes pas bstan te gong du las la sbyor ba na /
NK038(nyi)003:1720: sa sna bdun gyi 'dag pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:1721: zhes pa'i sa sna bdun ni chu pha ra 'gram tshul 'gram gyi sa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1727: dgra bo'i khang pa la tshad dang ldan pa'i zhes pa'i khru gang dpangs su yod pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1729: steng du bya khyung rgyal po bya zhes pa ni
NK038(nyi)003:1730: mkhar gyi gru bzhi dang logs g.yas g.yon du khyung
NK038(nyi)003:1732: nang du zhes pa mkhar de'i nang du mgon po'i gzugs po btags pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1734: gnyis pa ling+ga ji ltar bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1735: sbyin bsreg zhes pa nas bzhag ces pas bstan ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1736: sbyin bsreg byas pa'i thal ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1737: ling+ga la bsgral ba'i mgo bo'i dod //
NK038(nyi)003:1738: sbyin sreg byas la de'i thal ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1739: dri ma ni dngos yin lags so //
NK038(nyi)003:1740: zhes pa khongs nas mchims pa dang lud pa dang snabs so //
NK038(nyi)003:1741: zhes pa rnams la zhes pa ni zhes pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1742: ling+ga byas la bag phye'am yang na 'dags pa spyin pos mgo bsdus la /
NK038(nyi)003:1743: ling byang gro ga'am shog bu'am shing shun la bris la ling+ga'i snying gar gzhug go //
NK038(nyi)003:1744: gsum pa thod pa dang 'khor ji ltar bca' ba bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1745: a dar nas gdams zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1747: ma nu sha dang zhes pa ni sems can rigs ngan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1750: kri sna zhes pa ni rabs chad nag po'i thod pa'am /
NK038(nyi)003:1751: ku ra zhes pa khyi'i thod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1752: mdze po'am rabs chad nag po'i thod pa yin na /
NK038(nyi)003:1753: pho thod mo thod phye la bar du blangs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1754: sbyin sreg gi thal pa la ling+ga byas ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1755: snying gar ming rus bcug pa'i ling+ga de bcug pa'i ling+ga de bcug la /
NK038(nyi)003:1756: de nas rtsar song la zhes pas bstan ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1757: ka ru na'i phyag rgya ni bya khyung gi'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1758: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i gzer chen gyis zhes pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1759: thod pa de lcags kyus blangs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1760: dur khrod nag po na mar sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1761: lnga pa gzu dpangs gsol zhing mnan pa dngos bstan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1764: gtor ma ni dngos yin la /
NK038(nyi)003:1765: sogs khongs nas gser skyems dang bden pa brdar ba la sogs pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1766: gru gsum khru do rkos byas la zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1767: mnan pa byed pa'i sar dong bru ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1768: gong gi mkhar chen bcug nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1770: sa sna bdun las byas pa'i mkhar gzhug pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1771: mkhar nang du thod pa kha sbyar gzhug pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1772: g.yam pa nag pos kha bcad nas zhes pa ni dur khrod kyi g.yam pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1773: rdo rje rgya gram gyis mnan zhes pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1774: dur khrod g.yam pa sngon po yis zhes pa 'bebs
NK038(nyi)003:1775: pa'i dngos la rdo rje rgya gram bris la des
NK038(nyi)003:1776: mnan pa'o // drug pa mnan pa'i sa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1778: chu mig zhes pa nas dal zhes pa'i bar bstan ste shin tu sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1779: gsum pa gshegs gsol bsdu dang lus bsrung gi cho ga bstan pa ni de rting zhes pa nas /
NK038(nyi)003:1780: ci bder spyod zhes pas bstan te /
NK038(nyi)003:1781: de rting bsgrub pa'i gnas phyin nas zhes pa ma nan pa byas pas rting la'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1782: 'jig rten 'das dang zhes pa ni dal gyi lha'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1783: 'jig rten pa ni mgon po dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1785: yum nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1786: spyan drangs lha rna mas ma lus la /
NK038(nyi)003:1787: zhes pa ni ye shes pa 'og min nas spyan drangs pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1788: 'jig rten pa phyogs bcu nas spyan drangs pa gnyis so //
NK038(nyi)003:1789: mchod cing zhes pa ni nang du 'ong nas bdag gtso dang bsres te /
NK038(nyi)003:1790: tshogs rje zhes pa ni sman mchod byed pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1791: de nas mgon po la yang rnal 'byor yongs kyi zhes pas mchod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1792: bshags pa ni bdag cag ma rig lus dang zhes pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1793: gtang rag ni phrin las gzhung srang ba'i mchod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1794: de nas bsgrub pa chen po'i dus na mar gyi
NK038(nyi)003:1795: mchod pa bzhi tshogs byas pa'i lhag ma'i cho ga
NK038(nyi)003:1796: bya'o // de nas 'bru gsum tha mar mum btags la gshegs su gsol ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1797: de nas dbyings su ci bder gshegs zhes pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1798: bskyed pas lha rnams bdag gi thugs kar h'u las bsdu ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1800: mjug gi don la grub dang zhes pa la sogs pa sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1801: bdag gis 'di byas bsod nams kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:1802: kun gyi rdo rje 'dzin thob shog /
NK038(nyi)003:1803: gal te 'gal bar gyur na ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1804: 'phags pa rnams kyis bzod par bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:1805: slob dpon gyi sku drin ngor /
NK038(nyi)003:1806: sgrub thabs kyi tig 'grel legs par sdebs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1808: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:1809: spyir bzlas pa la gnyis te //
NK038(nyi)003:1812: ngag gis bzlas pa la gnyis //
NK038(nyi)003:1813: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bzlas pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1815: rdo rje'i bzlas pa la gnyis te //
NK038(nyi)003:1816: rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang de kho na nyid kyi bzlas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1817: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bzlas pa la gsum ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1818: bsnyen pa dang bsgrub pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1820: bsnyen pa ni bskyed pa'i rim pa rdzogs nas mchod bstod tshul bzhin du byas pa'i rjes la /
NK038(nyi)003:1821: bzlas pa'i dus su zhi rgyas dbang drag gi bzlas pa ni bsnyen pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1822: bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du me tog dor te gang
NK038(nyi)003:1823: la babs pa'i lhas bdag la dbang bskur te gzi
NK038(nyi)003:1824: byin dang ldan par byas pa ni bsgrub pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1825: las la sbyor ba'i dus su bdag gi gser skyems la sogs pa'i mchod rten gzu dpang gsol /
NK038(nyi)003:1826: de nas bdag nyid steng gi nam mkha' la sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa dmigs te /
NK038(nyi)003:1827: sngags kyi 'od zer gyis 'od du zhu ste bdag la thim //
NK038(nyi)003:1828: gzi byin dang ldan par byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:1829: de nas ngag gi bzlas pa byas pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1830: bdag gi zhal na phar drag po sngags kyi 'od
NK038(nyi)003:1831: zer kha dog nag po sna la lcags kyus mtshan
NK038(nyi)003:1832: pa 'phros te / drag po'i tshad ni gyi mda' 'phangs pa lta bu'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1833: lha gnod sbyin rgyud la phog pa ni lcags kyi thog rgyab pa lta bu'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1834: snying po byang chub kyi rgyud bsdus te /
NK038(nyi)003:1835: tshur 'ongs pa ni thag pa mkhar nag gi sgril ba lta bu'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1836: de nas bdag nyid la thim pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1837: bdag dpal chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:1838: dgra bo'i rnam par shes pa bdag rnal 'byor gyi go bgos pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1839: nyon mongs pa'i yid bcad pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1840: phung po'i lhag ma la mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la bstab par bya ba ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1841: de ltar de'i sbyor ba dang ldan pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1842: nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du tshogs kyi mchod pa dang bstab pa bya zhing /
NK038(nyi)003:1843: bzlas pa bya ba ni las la sbyar ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1844: 'jig rten pa'i bzlas pa bya ba la gsum ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1848: de la dang po rtags dang rten bshams te /
NK038(nyi)003:1849: sa sna bdun gyi 'dag pa la mkhar byas te /
NK038(nyi)003:1850: chu ru khru gang logs bzhi la ldog dkar dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1852: ru mtshon chen po bzhi dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1853: dur bya nag po brgyad dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1854: steng du khyung gi mu tra gnyis /
NK038(nyi)003:1855: de'i nang du gru gsum mthing nag gi nang du /
NK038(nyi)003:1857: khro bo'i steng du mda' sgro yud lnga pa gcig
NK038(nyi)003:1858: la dug med nag po btsugs la mgul du dar
NK038(nyi)003:1860: de la dang po ril bu'i phur ma brten pa'i rdzas /
NK038(nyi)003:1861: bar ma khro la bu brab pa'i rdzas /
NK038(nyi)003:1862: tha ma phye ma mchod pa'i rdzas /
NK038(nyi)003:1863: phur pa lid+ga'i snying gar btsug la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:1864: khro mo'i rten du nam mkha' nag mo gser mig
NK038(nyi)003:1865: ma gcig la mda' bya rgod kyi phod bzhi la
NK038(nyi)003:1866: dar lce bzhi dang bcas te mad'i ltogs du btsug
NK038(nyi)003:1867: la bzhag go // khro bo'i rdzas ni me tog sna tshogs kyis bkang ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1868: sha khrag sna tshogs pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1870: ri rab spyi skor gyi thod sbram kyang bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)003:1871: khro mo'i rdzas su thod pa tshal bu gcig gis nang du rkang sna tshoogs dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1873: mar dang khrag sna tshogs dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1874: de rnams kyis bkang la bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)003:1875: shar phyogs su khro bo'i mkhar byas la dmigs bya'i
NK038(nyi)003:1876: ling+ga'i steng du mchog phur gcig la mkhar nag gam
NK038(nyi)003:1877: rgyu zhags kyis btags la snying gar btsugs la bzhag
NK038(nyi)003:1878: / rgyu zhags kyi sna ri rab spyi skor gyi dmigs la btags la /
NK038(nyi)003:1879: k+ai la ya nyi shu rtsa gcig sgrol ging du byin gyis brlabs la sbas la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:1880: lho phyogs su gnod sbyin gyis mkhar du ling+ga'i steng
NK038(nyi)003:1881: du bse mdung dmar pos ba dan bcas te bzhag
NK038(nyi)003:1884: nub phyogs su srin po'i mkhar du ling+ga'i steng du sbrul mgo gdeng ka gsum bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:1885: g.yas su sha sna deb tshe gang /
NK038(nyi)003:1886: g.yon du klu sman sna tshogs pa deb tshe gang /
NK038(nyi)003:1888: byang phyogs su ma mo'i mkhar du //
NK038(nyi)003:1889: ling+ga'i steng du dar mthing gi gur phub //
NK038(nyi)003:1890: thun sna tshogs pa b+han+d+ha gang bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:1891: dgra bo lha dang bral ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:1892: rgya tshil la sogs pa yang bsham //
NK038(nyi)003:1893: de nas khro bo zhal bcas la //
NK038(nyi)003:1894: mkhar gyi nang du mda' la skyon te /
NK038(nyi)003:1895: rnal 'byor bdag nyid la kha bstan te bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:1896: de nas bsnyen bsgrub tshul bzhin bya //
NK038(nyi)003:1897: de nas las la sbyor ba'i dus su bsad pa'i 'brub khung las kyi dkyil 'khor byas te /
NK038(nyi)003:1899: bden pa brdar ma nyes pa'i dpang gzug /
NK038(nyi)003:1900: de nas drag po'i sngagsa bzlas pa'i dus su /
NK038(nyi)003:1901: bdag dpal chen po'i thugs ka nas /
NK038(nyi)003:1902: las kyi mgon po gsal shing can zhal gcig phyag gnyis gcer bu ral pa gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK038(nyi)003:1903: sku mdog sngo nag phyag na gsal shing nag po /
NK038(nyi)003:1904: g.yon zangs gri nag po thogs pas cig car gyis
NK038(nyi)003:1905: phyungs nas bzhi po'i mgon po dang gnyis su med
NK038(nyi)003:1906: par byas nas / bdag dpal chen po'i las ci bgyis zhes bka' nyan par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1907: rnal 'byor nyid kyis dmag gi brda' bstan pas /
NK038(nyi)003:1909: lce spyang dmar po sprul te /
NK038(nyi)003:1910: lha sbyin gyi sna nas yar zhugs /
NK038(nyi)003:1911: nang khrol zhal du rngubs te don snying smad lnga dmar gyis bstan nas slar la byung ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1912: bdag dpal chen po la bstab par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1913: de ltar de'i sbyor ba dang ldan pas nyin mtshan dus drug tu bstab pa'i las bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1914: drag po'i sngags gdon par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1915: de nas mtshan ma rtags la phebs pa dang rnal
NK038(nyi)003:1916: 'byor ba gcig gis mtho mtshams su phyin la rgya
NK038(nyi)003:1917: tshil gyi dud pa btang la /
NK038(nyi)003:1918: lha dang bral ba'i cho ga byas slar log ste phur pas gdab pa dang thun brdeg pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:1921: de nas bstab pa'i las bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1923: de nas mnan pas mas bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1924: sbyin sreg byas pa'i thal ba ling+ga byas te /
NK038(nyi)003:1925: ming byang snying gar gzhug tsakra kha sbyor gyi nang du bcug la /
NK038(nyi)003:1926: mkhar nag gam rgyu zhags kyis bsdams la /
NK038(nyi)003:1927: mnan sar khyer la phur bu bzhi yis sa bdag gi 'bros rgyun bcad la /
NK038(nyi)003:1929: yul gyi lha 'dre la ma nyes pa'i dpang gzug /
NK038(nyi)003:1930: sa bdag la yang klu sman sna tshogs kyi mchod pa sbyin /
NK038(nyi)003:1931: de nas mnan pa'i sa brus te /
NK038(nyi)003:1932: gru gsum khru gang pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1933: de nas rgya mtsho'i gting na gnas pa'i klu bdud ma chen mo kha phye zhig /
NK038(nyi)003:1934: rgyas pa'i dgra bo 'di bstab kyis byas la kha sbyar la gzhug go //
NK038(nyi)003:1935: de'i steng du mgon po mi'u thung gi gzugs skyon /
NK038(nyi)003:1936: de'i steng du khro bo'i mkhar khyung gi phyag rgya dang bcas la bzhag go //
NK038(nyi)003:1937: de'i steng du g.yam pa nag po la rdo rje rgya gram gyis rgyas gdab la kha bcad do //
NK038(nyi)003:1939: de nas gom pa nyi shu rtsa gcig phyir bskyed la zor brdeg /
NK038(nyi)003:1940: log na spogs pa'i las bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1941: g.yas su log na rkang pa la lan gsum bskor la 'phang /
NK038(nyi)003:1943: g.yon du log na yang de ltar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1944: thad kar log na yang 'dug sar tho gcig brtsigs la tshur bskyed la de nas brdeg go //
NK038(nyi)003:1945: de yang log na gnas su phyin la drag po'i sngags gzhug bzlog byas la stong tsho gcig 'don /
NK038(nyi)003:1946: de nas zor gyi las bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1947: de nas gtang rag gi gtor mas mchod /
NK038(nyi)003:1948: ye shes kyi lha gshegs su gsol /
NK038(nyi)003:1949: dam tshig gi lha lus la bsdu'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1950: mtshams ma'i dmigs pa rang bzhin gyis grol /
NK038(nyi)003:1951: de ltar byas nas las la sbyor ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1952: de ltar byas nas kyang lo ru thogs la /
NK038(nyi)003:1953: phyi rtags med na mnan pa blta /
NK038(nyi)003:1954: 'phar nas 'dug na slar la mnan las bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1955: 'phar na lha gnad la dbab pa'i las bya ste /
NK038(nyi)003:1956: mgon po'i gzugs mtho gang pa byas la //
NK038(nyi)003:1957: ru lu'i sngags spyi bor bri /
NK038(nyi)003:1958: bsnyen pa nas nye ba'i bsnyen pa rkang pa g.yas
NK038(nyi)003:1959: pa nas lag pa g.yas pa'i bar du gzhogs g.yas
NK038(nyi)003:1960: la bri / bsgrub pa dang bsgrub pa chen po
NK038(nyi)003:1961: gnyis rkang pa g.yon pa la g.yon pa'i bar gzhogs
NK038(nyi)003:1963: gzhi snying gcig tu dril la 'dabs su bri /
NK038(nyi)003:1964: yig mgo nang du bstan no //
NK038(nyi)003:1965: de nas bdag dpal chen po'i 'og tu zhag gsum gzir gnon bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1966: tha ma 'byung po'i nyin zhag gcig la zangs gri nag pos gtub la /
NK038(nyi)003:1967: drag po'i me sbar la sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1968: de nas thal ba mgon po'i gzugs bya /
NK038(nyi)003:1969: de la bskyed drangs bstim bsnyen sgrub kyi sngags la
NK038(nyi)003:1970: a mri ta btags te bdud rtsi gtor la gso
NK038(nyi)003:1971: / bkrag dang gzi mdangs dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:1972: de nas las sbyor yang yang bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:1973: de ltar byas na sangs rgyas nyid kyang 'jig go //
NK038(nyi)003:1974: snod ngan rnams la ma spel cig /
NK038(nyi)003:1976: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)003:1977: kor ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK038(nyi)003:1978: khyad par gyad kyi nye 'khor gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:1979: drag shul can gyi rtse mo la //
NK038(nyi)003:1980: bcom ldan rdo rje srin po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:1981: bka' dang dam la btags pa yi //
NK038(nyi)003:1982: ma h+aa ka la stobs chen po //
NK038(nyi)003:1983: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:1984: dur khrod ro langs thal ba'i mdog /
NK038(nyi)003:1985: mgon po nag po gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:1986: bam ri thod pa mkhar rtser gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:1987: khrag dang zhag dang sha chen dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1988: rkang dang klad pa klad rgyas dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1989: rnag dang chu ser la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1990: 'dam gyi khru mas yongs su bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:1992: sbrang ma sbrang rgod bung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:1993: sbrul dang sdig pa sdom la sogs /
NK038(nyi)003:1994: kang ka kha skyegs 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:1995: lce spyang stag seng la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:1996: gdug pa can gyi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:1997: lha yi sde dpon ka ru ni //
NK038(nyi)003:1998: chung ma bu mo sring mos bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:1999: bam ri thod pa mkhar gyi dbus //
NK038(nyi)003:2000: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i gzer chen gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:2001: rtag par btab pa'i nang bdag nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2002: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2003: thod skyogs khrag gis bkang ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2004: 'bru mar rdzas lngar chang sbyar ba //
NK038(nyi)003:2005: rtag par rang gi longs spyod 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)003:2006: rang nyid dang ni tshim par 'byung //
NK038(nyi)003:2007: gtso bo yab kyi zhal du stob //
NK038(nyi)003:2008: chags pas myos shing skam pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2009: 'dod pa'i dbang mo skam mar grags //
NK038(nyi)003:2010: bde gshegs sras kyi bka' sdod ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2011: 'dir gshegs thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2012: yab yum gnyis su med pa las //
NK038(nyi)003:2013: 'khor na gnas pa ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2014: srid pa'i nye gnas chen mo brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:2015: ke'u ri ma dang tsi'u ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2016: pra mo ha dang pe ta li //
NK038(nyi)003:2017: pus ka si dang kasma ri //
NK038(nyi)003:2018: sma sha ni dang tsan+d+ha li //
NK038(nyi)003:2019: ma mo chen mo brgyad kyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:2020: srid pa'i bu mo dri za brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:2021: seng+ha ma dang bye kri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2022: sri la ma dang shwa na ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2023: kri ta ma dang kang+ka ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2024: khwa kha ma dang hu lu ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2025: ma mo phra men brgyad kyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:2026: gtum zhing rngam pa'i ma tshogs ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2027: shin tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs kyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:2028: dur khrod pa'i sgo srung ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2029: shar du dri za'i bu mo ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2030: stag gdong chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2031: lho ru gshin rje'i bu mo ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2032: phag gdong chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2033: nub tu klu yi bu mo ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2034: sbrul mgo chen po gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2035: byang du gnod sbyin bu mo ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2036: sprel gdong chen po gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2037: gsang sgo bsrungs zhing bka' bsgo nod //
NK038(nyi)003:2038: dud khrod bdag mo gru 'degs ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2039: skam ma shin tu skam ma dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2040: ra ro ma dang khrag 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2041: chags pas myos pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod //
NK038(nyi)003:2042: 'jig rten dbang phyug lha chen gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:2043: ma sring bu mo chung ma rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2044: phrogs nas dbang du byas pa yin //
NK038(nyi)003:2045: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2046: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad la sogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2047: ma mo phra men gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2048: sring mo sha za khrag 'phrog ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2049: bdud kyi ming 'dzin bla rkun ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2050: blon mo dmag dpon sde dpon mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2051: ru dpon pho nya mngag par bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:2052: rang rang gdan dang lag char bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:2053: ci bgyis bka' nyan bka' sdod 'khor //
NK038(nyi)003:2054: rbod gtong rngam pa'i tshul du 'khod //
NK038(nyi)003:2055: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2056: khyed ni dbang phyug chen mo ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2057: snang srid thams cad dbang du bsdud //
NK038(nyi)003:2058: rgyal chen rigs bzhi g.yog tu 'khol //
NK038(nyi)003:2059: lha srin sde brgyad bran du byas //
NK038(nyi)003:2060: gying dang gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2062: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2063: rdo rje srin po'i spyan lnga ru //
NK038(nyi)003:2064: ji ltar khas blang dam bcas bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:2065: don dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)003:2066: nor bu rin chen bzhin du khur //
NK038(nyi)003:2067: 'khor rnams bu gcig bzhin du srungs //
NK038(nyi)003:2068: dam tshig can la srung gyis shig /
NK038(nyi)003:2069: sgrub pa po la brtse bar bgyi //
NK038(nyi)003:2070: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bsgrub kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:2072: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:2073: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i phrin las grub mdzod cig /
NK038(nyi)003:2074: gal te bka' bzhin ma byas na //
NK038(nyi)003:2075: rdo rje yak+sha srin po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2076: snying gi skyil nas khrag drangs nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2079: bka' dang dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK038(nyi)003:2080: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:2081: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:2082: sh+r+ai ma h+aa ka la yak+sha de ba dgra bgegs
NK038(nyi)003:2083: kyi snying khrag la thum ril ma h+aa ka la
NK038(nyi)003:2084: dgra bo'i srog rtsa la 'dus 'dus dza dzah sa
NK038(nyi)003:2086: mtsho ni kor ka thang dmar gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:2087: ri bo byan slag mchongs kyi rtser //
NK038(nyi)003:2088: bcom ldan mgon po nag po che //
NK038(nyi)003:2089: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gcer bu'i sku //
NK038(nyi)003:2090: g.yas na gri gug 'bar ba thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2091: g.yon na b+han+d+ha lcang lo thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2092: zhabs kyis dam nyams brgyangs shing bgrad //
NK038(nyi)003:2093: sho ra re de ma btang cig /
NK038(nyi)003:2094: ched 'ga' drag tu bskul tsam na //
NK038(nyi)003:2095: rab tu byung ba'i cha lugs can //
NK038(nyi)003:2096: g.yas na gseg shang 'bar ba thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2097: g.yon na bdud kyi par nag thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2098: chos gos nag po sku la gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2099: rgyab na glegs bam po ti khur //
NK038(nyi)003:2100: drag sngags bzlas shing mi snying za /
NK038(nyi)003:2103: byang shar mtshams su gnas bcas nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2104: rnam par snang mdzad gtsug tor can //
NK038(nyi)003:2105: phyag na rdo rje'i bka' sdod pho nya mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2106: kor mo kam ka mchu rigs khros pa'i sems //
NK038(nyi)003:2107: 'khor gyi ma mo'i tshogs rnams kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:2108: sho ra ched shar lho mtshams su gnas bcas nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2109: dbyugs dpal sngon mo be con 'chang //
NK038(nyi)003:2110: gshin rje gshed po'i sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2111: sku la ber chen sngon po gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2112: de'i bka' sdod pho nya mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2113: gcer bu kham nag gyen du bardzesa //
NK038(nyi)003:2114: kha nas khrag 'dzag thod phreng can //
NK038(nyi)003:2115: ral pa spyi bcings mig nas me dpung 'phro //
NK038(nyi)003:2116: g.yas na gsal shing g.yon na lcags kyu thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2117: don snying rnam lnga za zhing rab tu bgrad //
NK038(nyi)003:2118: sho ra ched shar gyi phyogs su gnas bcas nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2119: sdong na mthing nag thod phreng can //
NK038(nyi)003:2120: nag po ral can tshig cing khro //
NK038(nyi)003:2121: phyag na phyag drug cho 'phrul la //
NK038(nyi)003:2122: zhabs gnyis zhabs sna cho 'phrul rkang //
NK038(nyi)003:2123: g.yas g.yon dang po gsal shing thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2124: g.yas gnyis bse mdung ba dan can //
NK038(nyi)003:2125: g.yon gnyis rgyu zhags dmar po 'phen //
NK038(nyi)003:2126: g.yas tha lto ru 'khrol zhing sdigs mdzub bskyod //
NK038(nyi)003:2127: g.yon tha don snying za zhing thod pa'i zor chen 'phen //
NK038(nyi)003:2128: khyod kyi zhabs kyi long bu nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2129: stag smad rgyal mo khyug ge khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2130: gnod sbyin tshogs kyi sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2131: nyi ma lho nub ya ki na //
NK038(nyi)003:2132: zhe sdang dug mtsho'i nang shed nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2133: lcags mkhar rtse dgu'i nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)003:2134: bse sgong khra bo'i khang pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:2135: gnod sbyin zangs thogs rgyal po bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)003:2136: dbu la rgya mdud 'khor los brgyan //
NK038(nyi)003:2137: bse yi mdung dmar chems se chem //
NK038(nyi)003:2138: ba dan dmar po glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2139: bse khrab lus la khros pa'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2140: mdun na yum chen gtum pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2141: bse gdong zangs mgrin rdzu 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)003:2142: khros pa'i zhal la ha ri'i spyan //
NK038(nyi)003:2143: mchan na nad kyi rkyal pa sbed //
NK038(nyi)003:2144: lag na rims kyi zo bu 'phen //
NK038(nyi)003:2145: de gnyis 'khril ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK038(nyi)003:2146: zor gyi rgyal po mched rnams 'byung //
NK038(nyi)003:2147: shar phyogs gnod sbyin stag gi thabs //
NK038(nyi)003:2148: lho phyogs gnod sbyin gshin rje'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2149: nub phyogs gnod sbyin mgo dgu pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2150: byang phyogs gnod sbyin sog po gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2151: bse khrab lus la si li li //
NK038(nyi)003:2152: gong chen 'bar ba'i gang smig nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2153: khrag mda' dug mda' dgra la ya //
NK038(nyi)003:2154: ru zor nag po dgra la thun //
NK038(nyi)003:2155: yungs zor khro bo khro mo 'khril //
NK038(nyi)003:2156: zor gyi rgyal po ru 'phen na //
NK038(nyi)003:2157: ri rab rdo 'phen hu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)003:2158: rgya mtsho zho 'khrog chi li li //
NK038(nyi)003:2159: ming po rdo rje dmag 'dren na //
NK038(nyi)003:2160: srin mo rdo rje dam la 'du //
NK038(nyi)003:2161: bse yi gyad chen bskyod tsam na /
NK038(nyi)003:2162: mon gyi sprul pa phyogs rnams 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2163: lcags kyi gzhu la zangs kyi shul //
NK038(nyi)003:2164: drag po'i phyogs kyi rgyud kyis 'dul //
NK038(nyi)003:2165: lcags mda' nag po kun tu 'phro //
NK038(nyi)003:2166: nyi zla khyung dang 'ug pa khra //
NK038(nyi)003:2167: sprul pa chen mo phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK038(nyi)003:2168: nam gyi phar phyed tshur phyed na //
NK038(nyi)003:2169: ming po 'dre dang srin po snying gi sgo nga bcag du gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2170: srog gi dbugs la 'dus la brdungs //
NK038(nyi)003:2171: khyod kyi sta zur g.yas g.yon nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2172: pho seng g.yas la mo seng g.yon //
NK038(nyi)003:2173: ral pa sngon po sigs se sig /
NK038(nyi)003:2174: mche ba gangs ri gtam pa 'dra /
NK038(nyi)003:2175: khro bo'i tshogs kyi sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2176: skyes mchog drag po mi bzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2177: la las stag gi shams thabs can //
NK038(nyi)003:2178: la la rak+ta'i thig le can //
NK038(nyi)003:2179: la la thal chen tshom bu can //
NK038(nyi)003:2180: la la thod pa'i rgyan bcas klubs //
NK038(nyi)003:2181: ser nag sbrul gyi rgyan gyis spras //
NK038(nyi)003:2182: phyag na mtshon cha sna tshogs bsnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2183: sho ra ched 'ga' dbu gsum phyag drug spyan gsum can /
NK038(nyi)003:2184: phyag na rlung gi ba dan thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2185: de la ming dang mtshan btags pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2186: khro bo khams gsum dbang sdud bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2187: nyin mtshan gung la sprul pa 'phro //
NK038(nyi)003:2188: dam nyams 'di yi srog dbugs la //
NK038(nyi)003:2189: rngub cig ma btags dbugs longs shig /
NK038(nyi)003:2191: gcer bu ral pa gyen du rdzes //
NK038(nyi)003:2192: g.yas pa gri gug g.yon pa b+han+d+ha 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)003:2193: de la ming dang mtshan btags pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2194: khro bo badz+ra gying ka ra //
NK038(nyi)003:2195: srog bdag chen po mi bzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2197: sho ra ched mthing nag khros pa'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)003:2198: mi mgo dbyug tho phyag na bsnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2199: chibs su mi ro bam pa chibs //
NK038(nyi)003:2200: de la ming dang mtshan btags pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2201: dur khrod bdag po mi bzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2202: dam nyams 'di yi khang khyim du //
NK038(nyi)003:2203: mi rung sna tshogs ltas ngan thong //
NK038(nyi)003:2204: ched 'ga' 'bring gi ri ti dga' byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2205: keng rus rngams pas shin tu khros //
NK038(nyi)003:2206: dur khrod thal ba'i rkyal pa 'degs //
NK038(nyi)003:2207: ched rdo rje srin po'i khro bo bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2208: khyod kyi bka' sdod sprul pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2209: lam srang bzhi mdo dag na sdod /
NK038(nyi)003:2210: dam nyams bya ru mi rungs sna tshogs thong //
NK038(nyi)003:2212: nag po mi bzad spyan gsum pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2213: phyag na spu gri nag po thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2214: de la sho sha spyi gdong dgra la chod //
NK038(nyi)003:2215: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2216: ya 'gal gnam la ma mkhal sa //
NK038(nyi)003:2217: spu gri ral gri so ba bsnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2218: srig zan chen mo mi zad pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2219: de la rdo rje spyang kyi mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2220: 'phar spyang dur spyang za byed bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2221: dam nyams dgra bo ma lus bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:2222: ched 'ga' nam gyi phar phyed tshur phyed na //
NK038(nyi)003:2223: skyes pa dar ma'i srog gcod cing //
NK038(nyi)003:2224: sring mo gri gug 'khor lo thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2226: de la rdo rje zla mtshan mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2227: dgra bo 'di yi srog dkyil du //
NK038(nyi)003:2228: glo bur gyi ni skyin thang phob //
NK038(nyi)003:2229: ched sku mdog dmar po khram shing thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2230: lce spyang dmar po sprul par 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2231: nyi ma'i gung la rgyug tsam na //
NK038(nyi)003:2232: za ma mo yi srid kyang 'phrog /
NK038(nyi)003:2233: mi zad lag rings chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2234: de la rdo rje nyi ma'i mdangs chen po //
NK038(nyi)003:2235: dam nyams 'dii yi rnam shes rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2236: cham la phab pa'i dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)003:2238: mun nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:2240: g.yas na g.yag gi ru mtshon 'degs //
NK038(nyi)003:2241: mi ro sprul pa pho nyar 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2242: de la rdo rje ro langs chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2243: 'di la las kyi thun chen phob //
NK038(nyi)003:2244: ched 'ga' mi bzad khro bo chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2245: dus rnams dam nyams sgrol byed pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2246: rnal 'byor nga dang rgyas pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)003:2248: de la rdo rje du mtshams mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2249: dus bzhi dag tu nyul byed pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2250: khas blangs dam bca' ma g.yel bar //
NK038(nyi)003:2251: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK038(nyi)003:2252: ched 'ga' ljang sngon drag po mi zad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2253: phyogs bzhi dag tu rgyug byed pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2255: de la rdo rje phyogs 'dul mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2256: rnal 'byor pa yi dgra bgegs chom //
NK038(nyi)003:2257: ched 'ga' rdo rje nag po khros pa'i bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2258: phyag na sbrul gyi zhags pa thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2259: zas su klu yi sha la za //
NK038(nyi)003:2260: skom du klu yi khrag la 'thung //
NK038(nyi)003:2261: de la rdo rje phag gdong mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2262: khyed kyi bka' bsgo dam bcas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2263: dam bcas bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:2264: ched 'ga' nam mkha'i khams su h'u sgra sgrogs /
NK038(nyi)003:2265: rngam pa'i nga ros drag sngags zlos //
NK038(nyi)003:2266: mche ba rngam pas dgra snying za //
NK038(nyi)003:2267: de la rdo rje seng chen mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2268: rnal 'byor nga la brnyas pa'i dgra //
NK038(nyi)003:2269: zil gyis gnon la thams cad sgrol //
NK038(nyi)003:2270: ched mi rtog ngang la bzhugs pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)003:2271: thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:2272: mtshon cha sna tshogs char pa 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)003:2273: de la rdo rje nam mkha' mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2274: rnal 'byor dgra bgegs myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)003:2275: ched mi rtog ngang la bzhugs pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)003:2276: thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:2277: mtshon cha sna tshogs char pa 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)003:2278: de la rdo rje nam mkha' mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2279: rnal 'byor dgra bgegs myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)003:2280: ched zhe sdang 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2281: nag po khros pa'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)003:2282: ltas ngan sna tshogs sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2283: de la rdo rje nag po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2284: dam nyams 'di yi snying dkyil du //
NK038(nyi)003:2285: ltas ngan sna tshogs sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2286: chos bzang lha yi mdun sa na /
NK038(nyi)003:2287: lha yi dmag dpon chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2288: ru mtshon nag po thogs nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2289: 'jig rten sa g.yob phung bar byed //
NK038(nyi)003:2290: de la lha yi ded dpon ka ru na //
NK038(nyi)003:2291: bswe byang khram la btab pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2292: 'khor ba lus kyi snying dkyil du //
NK038(nyi)003:2293: cho 'phrul sna tshogs khyed la sogs /
NK038(nyi)003:2294: ched rgyal ba'i dgongs pa kun 'dus pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:2296: yag sha srin po khros pa'i lus //
NK038(nyi)003:2297: spyan mig nag po khros shing ldog de la //
NK038(nyi)003:2298: rdo rje rme brtsegs mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:2299: khyed kyi bka'i yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)003:2300: bka'i yi las kyi dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)003:2301: gdul dka' ma lus khyed kyi thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2302: ched gnod sbyin sprul pa'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:2303: bdud tshogs du ma sprul par 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2304: klu srin du ma'i rje bo ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2305: drag po'i sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:2306: de la rdo rje tshogs bdag bdud kyi rje //
NK038(nyi)003:2307: khyod ni sprul tshogs kun gyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2308: rnal 'byor pa dang rgyas pa'i dgra //
NK038(nyi)003:2309: skad cig yud la brlagsa par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:2310: khyod kyi rtsibs logs g.yas g.yon na //
NK038(nyi)003:2311: 'phar ba rkang rdebs khyugs se khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2312: dred mo lag rdeb chems se chem //
NK038(nyi)003:2313: za byed tshogs kyi sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2314: bar snang khams su gnas bcas te //
NK038(nyi)003:2315: rdo rje rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2316: khyod kyi dbus kyi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2317: shar phyogs khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2318: dkar mo ral can 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)003:2319: sangs rgyas rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2320: khyod kyi shar gyi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2321: lho phyogs khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2322: ser mo ral can sprul pa'i bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2323: rin chen rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2324: khyod kyi lho yi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2325: nub kyi khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2326: dmar mo ral can sa yar sprul //
NK038(nyi)003:2328: khyod kyi nub kyi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2329: byang phyogs khams na za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2330: nag mo ral cig rngams pa'i zhal //
NK038(nyi)003:2331: las kyi rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2332: khyed kyi byang gi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2333: dkon mchog gsum gyi bstan pa srungs //
NK038(nyi)003:2334: khyod kyi smin ma'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2335: bya khyung rgyal po ka ru na /
NK038(nyi)003:2336: ye shes mig la gser gyi gog pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:2337: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i mchu sder can //
NK038(nyi)003:2338: phyag na rdo rje'i bka' sdod cing //
NK038(nyi)003:2339: mgon po tshogs kyi sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2340: khyod kyi lag pa g.yas pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:2341: mtha' yas gdengs ka gsum pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:2342: khyod kyi lag pa g.yon pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:2343: srin po byid ti rak+sha gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2344: de gnyis tshogs pa'i byin rlabs las /
NK038(nyi)003:2345: khyab 'jug chen po kun tu rgyu //
NK038(nyi)003:2346: 'jigs byed chen po r+aa hu la //
NK038(nyi)003:2347: lus po gcig la mgo dgu la //
NK038(nyi)003:2348: mgo lus med par mig gis gang //
NK038(nyi)003:2349: lag na sbrul zhags gri gug thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2350: zla ba nyi ma khyur mid byed //
NK038(nyi)003:2351: nyi zla'i rjes gcod shar du rgyu //
NK038(nyi)003:2352: nyin mo rgyu ba'i phyogs rnams 'joms //
NK038(nyi)003:2353: mtshan mo rgyu bas mtshams rnams 'joms //
NK038(nyi)003:2354: dmag dpon chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2355: gza' mchog chen po'i dus la dbang phyug chen po'i khyod kyi pho nya chen po rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2356: gdong mo chen mo phyogs 'dul ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2357: shar gyi stag sring zor ba'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2358: khyod kyi shar kyi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2359: lho yi bam sring dred mo'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2360: khyod kyi lho yi nub kyi rkang srin chu srin gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2361: khyed kyis nub byang gi 'brog srin ba lang gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2363: gnam kyi dkyil nas 'brug chen ldir //
NK038(nyi)003:2364: bar snang khams nas glog chen 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2365: sa yi dkyil du thog chen 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)003:2366: rgya mtsho'i gting nas ser chen 'drel //
NK038(nyi)003:2367: dam nyams dgra bo'i yul 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)003:2368: king kang dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2369: glo bur gyis ni skyin thang phob //
NK038(nyi)003:2370: srog la hur thum dus la babs //
NK038(nyi)003:2371: phyogs mtshams nas stag mgo nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2372: srid pa'i rgyal po chen po bcu //
NK038(nyi)003:2373: mdog ni ma nges khros pa'i mdog /
NK038(nyi)003:2374: lag na tshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2375: bstan pa bsrungs bar dam bcas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2376: khyod kyis dam tshig dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2377: dam nyams dgra bo'i snying dkyil du //
NK038(nyi)003:2378: khyed kyi dus pa de ru thob //
NK038(nyi)003:2380: rgya mtsho zhe 'khrog chi li li //
NK038(nyi)003:2382: gnam sa dkrugs pa'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2383: dam nyams 'di yi dbugs long la //
NK038(nyi)003:2384: snying gi sgo nga da chod cig /
NK038(nyi)003:2385: mdze nad drag po'i 'khor lo yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2386: dam nyams dgra bo'i lus sprul pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:2387: dam nyams dgra bo smyo ru chug /
NK038(nyi)003:2388: smyo 'bog gtang ba'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2389: lkugs pa lug gi sprul pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2390: dam nyams dgra bo lkugs su chug /
NK038(nyi)003:2391: smra byed sprul ba'i 'khor lo yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2392: dam nyams dgra bo 'cham du chug /
NK038(nyi)003:2393: skye mched sprul pa'i 'khor lo yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2394: dam nyams dgra bo rlung la bskur //
NK038(nyi)003:2395: brlag byed sprul pa'i 'khor lo yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2396: dam nyams dgra bo phung du chug /
NK038(nyi)003:2398: dam nyams dgra bo med par gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:2400: pho nya ring mo yin no //
NK038(nyi)003:2401: ru dar ma mo'i rjed byang yi ger bri bar bya //
NK038(nyi)003:2402: le'u so gcig pa nas sgrub thabs smra te /
NK038(nyi)003:2403: rtags rten bsham pa'i thad kar //
NK038(nyi)003:2404: spyir mgon po la sgrub thabs gnyis bzhugs te /
NK038(nyi)003:2405: zur tsho stod na yod pa de de'i chog khrigs
NK038(nyi)003:2406: legs po ka med de byin rlabs shin tu che
NK038(nyi)003:2407: gsung / phyis pan+di ta gzhon nu bum pas 'ongs
NK038(nyi)003:2408: pa'i dal bdun pa'i sgrub thabs bya ba gcig byung
NK038(nyi)003:2409: gsung / ste / de dang gnyis yod gsungs /
NK038(nyi)003:2410: cig la bdun pa'i sgrub thabs su phug na //
NK038(nyi)003:2412: dang po ji bzhin nyid kyi dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2413: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK038(nyi)003:2414: ces pas dngos po rnams kyi lugs /
NK038(nyi)003:2415: rtsa ba byang chub kyi dal la bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2416: gnyis pa byang chub kyi sems kyi dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2417: dar nas nyid rtogs pa la bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2418: gsum pa bsod nams tshogs kyi dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2419: tshogs kyi dngos po rnams dang /
NK038(nyi)003:2420: bsod nams bsogs pa la bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2421: bsod nams tshogs kyi dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2422: tshogs kyi dngos po rnams dang /
NK038(nyi)003:2423: tsha tsha gdab pa la sogs pa phyag rgya dngos kyi dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2425: ji rung ma rung dam pa rgyan cig dgos /
NK038(nyi)003:2426: dal bdun pa'i nang du gzhug pa'i dam pa rgyan da kas bya'o gsung /
NK038(nyi)003:2427: lnga pa bka' sdod pho nya'i dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2428: dal cig de'i dbus su keng rus kyi dal khru gang gru bzhi pa rtsig /
NK038(nyi)003:2429: de'i gzhug la rtags rten mda' bya rgod gcig gzhug /
NK038(nyi)003:2430: nam mkha' snying gar nye gnas kro ti shwa ri'i rten du bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:2431: de'i phyir gsang ba'i yum bzhi dgod /
NK038(nyi)003:2434: de'i phyir sgo ma la sogs dgod /
NK038(nyi)003:2435: de'i phyir klu dang 'bu chen po dang /
NK038(nyi)003:2436: rnag dang khrag dang bya byi stag dred la sogs dgod bsnyen bsgrub bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2437: drug pa 'brub khung las kyi dal ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2438: byang shar du 'brub khung byas la /
NK038(nyi)003:2439: de'i nang du ling+ga bcug la thun la sogs pa brab par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2440: bdun pa gtad khram gnan pa'i dal gyi mchod rten la 'bar ling gnan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2441: dpal mgon po yid bzhin nor bu'i sgrub thabs /
NK038(nyi)003:2442: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyis dpal gyi bsnyen pa
NK038(nyi)003:2443: tshul dus dang grangs dang mtshan ma la sogs pa'i
NK038(nyi)003:2445: de nas chos skyong ba'i dpal mgon po nag po la 'phrin las gzhol ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2446: rang dpal gyi ting nge 'dzin du bzhugs la /
NK038(nyi)003:2447: khros pa'i cha byad kyi nga rgyal cher bskyed la
NK038(nyi)003:2448: bdag gi thugs ka nas yi ge bam gcig 'thon
NK038(nyi)003:2449: te / zhu ba las bam rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:2450: zhes pas rak+ta'i rgya mtshor bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:2451: ram las ri bo ma la ya bskyed /
NK038(nyi)003:2452: de'i steng du bam ri thod mkhar du bskyed /
NK038(nyi)003:2453: de'i nang du lcags khang 'bar ba yi ge ru gcig bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:2454: phyogs bzhir yang lcags khang bzhi bskyed /
NK038(nyi)003:2459: ru zhu ba las phyag mtshan dang /
NK038(nyi)003:2460: dang por bskyed pa ni zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2462: g.yon na tsan dan gyi be con 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2464: dar nag gi ber gsum brtsegs sku la gsol ba /
NK038(nyi)003:2465: gser ga rin chen sked la bcings pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2466: stag dang ba tis gong lag byas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2467: dbu dang phyag zhabs sbrul dang rin po ches brgyan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2468: de ltar gsal ba'i long bu'i steng g.yas g.yon du stag mi zan gnyis /
NK038(nyi)003:2469: rtsibs logs g.yas su dred mo lag pa rdebs pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2470: rtsibs logs g.yon du 'phar ba rkang pa rdebs pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2471: dpung pa g.yas g.yon du seng ge ral pa sprugs pa gnyis /
NK038(nyi)003:2472: spyi bor bya khyung rgyal po klu za ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2473: gdan rdo rje brag dang bam gyi steng du bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)003:2474: de'i g.yas su las kyi bdud po khros pa gcer bu nag po bya rog gi gdong can /
NK038(nyi)003:2475: g.yas gri gug g.yon thod khrag /
NK038(nyi)003:2476: sbrul gyis brgyan pa bam ro'i steng na zhabs brdebs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2477: g.yas su las kyi srin po smug nag gcer bu sha za ba /
NK038(nyi)003:2478: ral gri dang snying thogs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2479: mche ba gtsigs pa kha phyir lta ba /
NK038(nyi)003:2481: rgyab na las kyi bdud mo lcags kyu thod khrag
NK038(nyi)003:2482: 'di yang las kyi bya rog gdong can du 'dod
NK038(nyi)003:2483: pa yin gsung // thod pa dang g.yag rog pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2484: mdun nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma mthing nag g.yas ral gri /
NK038(nyi)003:2486: sku la ra thul gyon pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2487: bam gyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2489: shar du sa la ljang sngon gsal shing can bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2490: lhor ya las gnod sbyin zangs thogs yab yum bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2491: nub tu ra las srin po r+aa hu la bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2492: byang du ma las za byed ma dkar mo shel phreng ma bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)003:2493: dkar mo shel phreng gser gyi rdo rje'i thor tshugs can dbu la g.yu'i bya khyung yod pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2496: sku stod dar gser gyi ngang ris can sku smad stag gi sham bu /
NK038(nyi)003:2497: chibs su sed+ge dkar mo chibs pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2498: rol du sman sha yu chung rol phyag na gser
NK038(nyi)003:2499: gyi gri zhags bsnams pa rnam snang dkar mo 'bum
NK038(nyi)003:2500: gyis bskor ba'o // de rnams lhar gsal ba'i mdun du bskyed la //
NK038(nyi)003:2501: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu 'phros pas /
NK038(nyi)003:2502: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:2503: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la ya hrim hrim /
NK038(nyi)003:2504: am gu sha dzah dzah zhes brjod pas mtsho ko ka thang dmar gyi steng /
NK038(nyi)003:2505: ri bo chen po ma la ya'i rtse mo nas
NK038(nyi)003:2506: nag po bzhugs pa'i snying ga nas lcags kyu'i bzung
NK038(nyi)003:2507: nas drangs la bdag gi mdun du 'ongs par bsam
NK038(nyi)003:2508: zhing de nyid dbang du bsdu ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2509: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yoh ha la ra la b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:2511: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ha ha /
NK038(nyi)003:2512: ru tra ma tra ha ham kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2513: zhes brjod cing bdag nyid dpal chen por gsal ba'i
NK038(nyi)003:2514: zhal du nag po chen po de bsdus la thugs
NK038(nyi)003:2516: de lta bu lan grangs nyer gcig gam /
NK038(nyi)003:2519: de'i mthar lam bstan pa'i phyir sdig pa sbyang zhing byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2520: h'u h'u h'u kho rang gi rgyud la bsags pa'i
NK038(nyi)003:2521: sdig pa kun drangs par bsam mo bi sha badz+ra
NK038(nyi)003:2522: / kro ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u ta kem ta kem phata /
NK038(nyi)003:2523: ha la sdig pa gzhol ba /
NK038(nyi)003:2524: sdig pa bsreg pa ha la ram /
NK038(nyi)003:2528: zhes brjod cing byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2529: badz+ra a mri ta e na hi sarba man+da la h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:2530: a b+hi shiny+tsa mam h'u h+r+aihtha 'di gyer gyi mgo la bcug kyang chog /
NK038(nyi)003:2531: dal bdun pa'i lugs yin pas gzhan du mi dgos
NK038(nyi)003:2532: de nas h'u lam ka gsum gyi zhes pa'i tshig
NK038(nyi)003:2533: brjod la / sngon gyi dam bca' dran par bsam zhing //
NK038(nyi)003:2534: bdag lhar gsal ba'i mdun na mgon po //
NK038(nyi)003:2535: nag po 'dar yang bred cing bdag gi bka' nyan gsung sdod byed par bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:2536: de nas dam tshig dbang gis dam bsres pa de la mchod pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2537: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la ni ma h+aa a ha ra /
NK038(nyi)003:2545: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2546: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2547: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2548: ma h+aa mam sa kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2549: ma h+aa rak+ta ma h+aa ba su ta ma h+aa
NK038(nyi)003:2550: go ro tsa na dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag la
NK038(nyi)003:2551: / m+aa ra ya kh+aa hi hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2552: zhes phyi nang gi mchod pas mchod la 'di skad do //
NK038(nyi)003:2554: dka' thub chen po tshur nyon cig /
NK038(nyi)003:2555: legs ldan nag po ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2556: rgyal ba'i bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:2557: khram la btab pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2558: ma ra ya yi las bcol gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:2559: tshe srog hur thum myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)003:2560: rol cig dgongs shig dam tshig can //
NK038(nyi)003:2561: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2562: zhe sdang dregs pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2563: sem can kun gyi srog 'phrog nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2564: sha la za zhing khrag la 'thung //
NK038(nyi)003:2565: dam nyams dgra bo myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)003:2566: ma ra ya yi dus la bab /
NK038(nyi)003:2573: de nas bsnyen sgrub bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2575: dang po bsnyen pa'i yan lag ni sngags dang po bzlas pas /
NK038(nyi)003:2576: bdag lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros pas /
NK038(nyi)003:2577: phyogs bcu dus bzhi nas bde bar gshegs pa thams cad spyan drangs la /
NK038(nyi)003:2580: dbang blang ba dang gzi byin bskyed par byas la /
NK038(nyi)003:2581: bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK038(nyi)003:2582: 'od zer mgon po'i thugs kar phog pas mgon po gsal gdab //
NK038(nyi)003:2584: dgra bgegs kyi tshe srog la dbang bskur ro //
NK038(nyi)003:2586: sngags brgya brgya stong stong la bdud rtsis mchod nas
NK038(nyi)003:2587: khri tsho bdun nam 'bum tshun chad 'don par bya'o
NK038(nyi)003:2588: // de ltar bsgrubs nas spyod lam byed na /
NK038(nyi)003:2589: stan las langs pa'i dus na gtso cha gnyis su bsam la spyod lam bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2590: stan la 'dug pa'i dus su gtso bo gnyis po
NK038(nyi)003:2591: mar me gcig tu bsdoms pa ltar bsres la gnyis
NK038(nyi)003:2593: bla ma dang yi dam la mchod mdun gyi mgon
NK038(nyi)003:2594: po la sman gyis mchod la sku gsung thugs kyi
NK038(nyi)003:2595: dngos grub blang / sman gyi bskang bshags bya /
NK038(nyi)003:2596: yi ge brgya pa mang du brjod //
NK038(nyi)003:2597: de nas yang nye bsnyen bya ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2598: bdag dpal du gsal ba'i sna bug nas rlung rgyu ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2599: h'u ces brjod pas dbugs de h'u du gyur nas /
NK038(nyi)003:2600: h'u las 'od 'phros pas khro bo mang por gyur
NK038(nyi)003:2601: nas 'phros pas yang bla ma dang yi dam kun
NK038(nyi)003:2603: slar dbang dang dngos grub tu thim 'dus /
NK038(nyi)003:2605: bdag nyid gtso bo la thugs kyi rgyud bskul zhing gsol ba gdab /
NK038(nyi)003:2606: yang phar la 'phros pas gdug pa can gyi tshogs thams cad btul nas dbang du bsdus /
NK038(nyi)003:2607: khyad par rang rgyud dang sprul pa'i mgon po dbang du bsdus shing bkug nas /
NK038(nyi)003:2608: ting nge 'dzin gyi dam tshig mgon po la bstim la gnyis su dbyer med par bsam par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2611: tsan dan gyi phur mas bskul ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2612: sman gyi thum po la basngagasa shing mgon po'i thugs
NK038(nyi)003:2613: kar phur mas bskul bas nga rgyal dregs pa'i tshogs
NK038(nyi)003:2614: zhi nas / sngon gyi dam bca' gnyan po dran
NK038(nyi)003:2615: cing dam tshig gnyan po las mi 'da' bar bsrung
NK038(nyi)003:2616: nas rnal 'byor pa 'khor dang bcas pa la bar
NK038(nyi)003:2617: chad mi byed cing dam tshig ldan par bsam mo
NK038(nyi)003:2618: zhi nas / // de nas bsgrub pa bya ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2619: thun mtshams kyi gtso bo cha gnyis dang man chad bya lugs gong dang mthun no //
NK038(nyi)003:2620: bsad pa'i rdzas ni yungs dkar thum po la sngags la //
NK038(nyi)003:2621: yungs dkar khro bor gyur khro bos mgon po bskul bas mgon pos 'khor rnams bzhi bskul nas /
NK038(nyi)003:2622: drag po'i las byed par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2623: sngags de la bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:2628: de nas bsgrub pa chen po ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2629: khrag skam gyi thum po la /
NK038(nyi)003:2630: sngags nas bskul bas sngon dpal gyi spyan sngar khas
NK038(nyi)003:2631: blangs shing dam bcas pa dran nas las byed par
NK038(nyi)003:2632: bsam mo // sngags kyi sham bu dgra bgegs kyi srog shing dang /
NK038(nyi)003:2633: sarba sha trum ma ra ya rbad dza zhes btags shing bzlas /
NK038(nyi)003:2635: de nas ma g.yel ma 'da' bya //
NK038(nyi)003:2639: phrin las gzhol las la song bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:2642: lha chen mgon po nag po khyod //
NK038(nyi)003:2643: mtsho ni kang ka thang dmar nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2644: ri bo byan slag 'chongs kyi rtser //
NK038(nyi)003:2645: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2646: che mchog thugs kyi sprul pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2647: dpal ldan mdog nag gzi brjid can //
NK038(nyi)003:2648: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gcer bu yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2649: g.yas pa gri gug sngon po bsnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2650: g.yon pa thod khrag zhal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2651: zhabs gnyis dam nyams brgyangs shing bgrad //
NK038(nyi)003:2652: dgra bo dam nyams che ge mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2653: sho ra re ste ma btang cig /
NK038(nyi)003:2654: ched 'ga' drag tu bskul ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)003:2655: dge slong rab tu byung ba'i cha lugs can //
NK038(nyi)003:2656: phyag g.yas gseg shang g.yon pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:2657: bdud kyi par bu nag po bsnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2658: glegs bam khur cing chos gos ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2659: nag po phyin ka log tu gyon //
NK038(nyi)003:2660: kha nas drag po'i sngags bzlos shing //
NK038(nyi)003:2661: dam nyams gsum po sgrol ba'i las la brtson //
NK038(nyi)003:2662: btsun pa tshul khrims nyams pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2663: sngags pa dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2664: skye bo mi chos mna' zan dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2665: 'di gsum bsgral ba'i las gyis la //
NK038(nyi)003:2666: snying khrag rlon pa zas su zo //
NK038(nyi)003:2667: shor ra re ste ma ched 'ga' byang shar mtshams su gnas bcas shing //
NK038(nyi)003:2668: rnam par snang mdzad gtsug tor can //
NK038(nyi)003:2669: phyag na rdo rje'i bka' nyan pho nya mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2670: dkar mo mchu rings khros pa'i sems //
NK038(nyi)003:2671: las kyi ma tshogs 'khor bcas kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:2672: dam nyams dgra bo che ge mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2673: sho ra re ched 'ga' gcer bu nag po 'jigs tshul can //
NK038(nyi)003:2674: khams nag ral pa gyen du bardzesa //
NK038(nyi)003:2675: kha nas khrag 'dzag thod phreng brgyan //
NK038(nyi)003:2676: mig nas me yi phung po 'bar //
NK038(nyi)003:2677: sna nas rlung nag bu yug tshub //
NK038(nyi)003:2678: g.yas na gsal shing me 'bar thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2679: g.yon na lcags kyus dgra snying 'byin //
NK038(nyi)003:2680: don snying za zhing khrag la 'thung //
NK038(nyi)003:2681: dam nyams ro yi steng na bgrad //
NK038(nyi)003:2682: ma ra ya yi dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2683: sho ra ched gdong gsum gdong nag thod phreng can //
NK038(nyi)003:2684: nag po ral can 'khril cing khro //
NK038(nyi)003:2685: phyag bzhi phyag drug cho 'phrul lag /
NK038(nyi)003:2686: zhabs bzhi zhabs gnyis rdzu 'phrul rkang //
NK038(nyi)003:2687: g.yas kyi dang po gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)003:2688: gnyis pa bse mdung ba dan dmar po can //
NK038(nyi)003:2689: tha ma 'brong ru khrol cing sdig mdzum sbreng //
NK038(nyi)003:2690: g.yon gyi dang po khrag zor dgra la 'phen //
NK038(nyi)003:2691: gnyis pa rgyu zhags dmar po sdog cing 'debs //
NK038(nyi)003:2692: tha ma dgra bgegs don snying 'bab cing za //
NK038(nyi)003:2693: khyod kyi zhabs kyi long bu las //
NK038(nyi)003:2694: stag smad rgyal mo khyugs se khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2695: gnod sbyin tshogs ni sprul par 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2696: sho ra re ched nyi ma lho nub pha gi na //
NK038(nyi)003:2697: zhe sdang dug mtsho'i nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)003:2698: bse sgo khra bo'i kha yi nang //
NK038(nyi)003:2699: lcags mkhar sngon po'i nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)003:2700: gnod sbyin zangs thogs rgyal po bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)003:2701: dbu la rgya mdud 'khor los brgyan //
NK038(nyi)003:2702: bswe yi mdung dmar chems se chem //
NK038(nyi)003:2703: ba dan dmar po glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2704: bse khrab lus la khros pa'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2705: de yi yum chen gtum mo ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2706: bswe gdong zangs kyi rdzu 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)003:2707: sngo dmar lus la ha ri'i mig /
NK038(nyi)003:2708: mchan nas nad kyi rkyal pa 'debs //
NK038(nyi)003:2709: lag na rims kyi gru gu 'phen //
NK038(nyi)003:2710: de gnyis 'khril ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK038(nyi)003:2711: zor gyi rgyal po mched bzhi byung //
NK038(nyi)003:2712: shar phyogs gnod sbyin stag thabs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2713: lho phyogs gnod sbyin gshin rje'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2714: nub phyogs gnod sbyin mgo dgu pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2715: byang phyogs gnod sbyin sog po gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2716: bse khrab khra bo si li li //
NK038(nyi)003:2717: go chen 'bar ba rgyun mig nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2718: khrag mda' dug mda' dgra la ya //
NK038(nyi)003:2719: bu skyogs nag po dgra la thun //
NK038(nyi)003:2720: yungs zor khro bo khro mor 'khrigs //
NK038(nyi)003:2721: zor gyi rgyal po bskyod tsam na //
NK038(nyi)003:2723: rgya mtsho zho 'khrog chi li li //
NK038(nyi)003:2724: ming po rdo rje dmag 'dren na //
NK038(nyi)003:2725: srin mo rdo rje dam la 'dus //
NK038(nyi)003:2726: bse yi gyad chen bskyod tsam na //
NK038(nyi)003:2727: mon gyi lus la mdung rtse rkang //
NK038(nyi)003:2728: lcags kyi de ni dal bu la //
NK038(nyi)003:2729: zangs kyi de ni bshul gyis spras //
NK038(nyi)003:2730: drag po sngags kyi rgyud kyi brdungs //
NK038(nyi)003:2731: bse yi lan phran g.yon la spras //
NK038(nyi)003:2732: skyes bu lag pa g.yon du thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2733: mon gyi dug mda' nag po la //
NK038(nyi)003:2734: khyung dang 'ug pa khra yi sgron //
NK038(nyi)003:2735: gzer chen gnam thog made'u gsal //
NK038(nyi)003:2736: dung gi hor shum g.yas su spras //
NK038(nyi)003:2737: skyes bu'i lag pa g.yas su thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2738: gnod sbyin bye ba sa yar bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:2739: nam gyi phar phyed tshur phyed na //
NK038(nyi)003:2740: ming po rdo rje dmag 'dren gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:2741: sring mo rdo rje'i dam la 'dus /
NK038(nyi)003:2742: snying gi sgo nga bcag re ran //
NK038(nyi)003:2743: dgra bo'i srog dbugs rngubs re ran //
NK038(nyi)003:2744: dug mda' dgra bo'i snying la rgyob //
NK038(nyi)003:2745: khyod kyi rtsibs logs g.yas g.yon nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2746: 'phar ba rkang rdebs khyugs se khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2747: dred mo lag rdebs chems se chems //
NK038(nyi)003:2748: za byed tshogs kyi sprul pas 'gengs //
NK038(nyi)003:2749: snang srid khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2750: nag mo ral can bye bar bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:2751: rdo rje rigs kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2752: khyod ni phrin las mnga' bdag mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2753: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)003:2754: shar phyogs rigs kyi za byed mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2755: dkar mo ral can 'bum sder bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:2756: sangs rgyas rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2757: shar gyi dgra bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:2758: lho phyogs rigs kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2759: ser mo ral can khros pa'i bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2760: rin chen rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2761: lho yi dgra bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:2762: nub phyogs rigs kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2763: dmar mo ral can sa yar bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:2765: nub kyi dgra bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:2766: byang phyogs rigs kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2767: ljang mo ral can rngam pa'i zhal //
NK038(nyi)003:2768: las kyi rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2769: byang gi dgra bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:2770: khyod kyi sta zur g.yas g.yon na //
NK038(nyi)003:2771: pho seng g.yas la mo seng g.yon //
NK038(nyi)003:2772: g.yu ral sngon po nyigs se nyigs //
NK038(nyi)003:2773: mche ba gangs ri gtam pa 'dra //
NK038(nyi)003:2774: khro bo'i tshogs kyi sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2775: skyes mchog 'bar ba mi bzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2776: la la stag gi sham thabs can //
NK038(nyi)003:2777: la la rak+sha'i thig le can //
NK038(nyi)003:2778: la la thal chen tshom bu can //
NK038(nyi)003:2779: la la thod pa'i gwa sha can //
NK038(nyi)003:2780: la la zhing lpags rgyan gyis klubs //
NK038(nyi)003:2781: ser nag sbrul gyi chun skor can //
NK038(nyi)003:2782: stangs thabs lag gar sna tshogs byed //
NK038(nyi)003:2783: lag na mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2784: dgra bgegs dam nyams myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)003:2785: ched 'ga' dbu gsum phyag drug spyan dgur ldan //
NK038(nyi)003:2786: phyag na rlung gi ba dan sngon po can //
NK038(nyi)003:2787: de la ming dang mtshan gsol pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2788: khro bo khams gsum dbugs sdud bya //
NK038(nyi)003:2789: nyin mtshan gung la dgung la sdud //
NK038(nyi)003:2790: dam nyams dgra bo'i srog dbugs la //
NK038(nyi)003:2791: rngubs cig ma btang dbugs longs shig /
NK038(nyi)003:2792: dam nyams sgrol cig sho ra re //
NK038(nyi)003:2793: khyod kyi smin bus dkyil 'khor nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2794: bya khyung rgyal po ka ru na //
NK038(nyi)003:2795: ye shes gser mig g.yas su gshog pa gdengs //
NK038(nyi)003:2796: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i chu sder can //
NK038(nyi)003:2797: zas su gdug pa'i ro nyi za //
NK038(nyi)003:2798: phyag na rdo rje'i bka' sdod cing //
NK038(nyi)003:2799: mgon po'i thugs kyi sprul pa de /
NK038(nyi)003:2800: khyod kyi lag pa g.yas pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:2801: mtha' yas gdengs ka gsum pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:2802: khyod kyi lag pa g.yon pa na //
NK038(nyi)003:2803: srin po rak+sha byi ste gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2804: sprul pa bar snang khams kun khyab //
NK038(nyi)003:2805: dgra bgegs thal ba rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:2806: khyod kyi bka' sdod ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2807: srin po rak+sha mgo dgu dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2808: klu mo hab sham gnyis kyi bu /
NK038(nyi)003:2809: khyab 'jug chen po kun tu rgyu //
NK038(nyi)003:2810: gza' rgod 'jigs de r+aa hu la //
NK038(nyi)003:2811: lus po gcig la mgo bo dgu /
NK038(nyi)003:2812: mgo lus med par mig gis bkang //
NK038(nyi)003:2813: lag na gri gug sbrul zhags thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2814: nyi ma zla ba khyur mid byed //
NK038(nyi)003:2815: nyi ma'i rjes gcod nub tu rgyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2816: nyin mo rgyugs pa'i phyogs bzhi 'joms //
NK038(nyi)003:2817: zla ba'i rjes gcod shar du rgyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2818: mtshan mo rgyugs pa'i phyogs bzhi 'joms //
NK038(nyi)003:2819: dmag dpon chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2820: gza' mchog chen po r+aa hu la //
NK038(nyi)003:2821: nam mkha'i dkyil nas 'brug sgrogs shing //
NK038(nyi)003:2822: bar snang khams nas glog dmar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)003:2823: sa gzhi'i steng du thog chen 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)003:2824: dgra bo'i klad pa'i dkyil du rgyob //
NK038(nyi)003:2825: rgya mtsho'i gting nas ser chen 'dril //
NK038(nyi)003:2826: king kang dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2827: glo bur king kang dgra la phob //
NK038(nyi)003:2828: tshe srog hur thum dgra la phob //
NK038(nyi)003:2829: phyogs bzhi'i srin mo'i sde bzhi yang //
NK038(nyi)003:2830: pho lhog rims nad dgra la phob //
NK038(nyi)003:2831: phyogs bzhi'i mtshams bzhi steng 'og nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2832: ma rung lha srin dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2833: kha dog ma nges khros pa'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)003:2834: lag na mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2835: bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2836: dam tshig nyan gyi dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2837: drag po'i phrin las chen mo ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2838: bcol pa'i phrin las dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)003:2839: skabs 'di na mar bka' sdod kyi las mkhan bdud mgon nag po'i bskul pa bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2840: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la hur thum ka la kro ta /
NK038(nyi)003:2843: a ta ya sarba sha trum tsi ta ma ra ya rbad /
NK038(nyi)003:2847: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2848: 'gro ba'i don du ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)003:2849: kong ka thang dmar lang+ka'i yul //
NK038(nyi)003:2850: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo ru //
NK038(nyi)003:2851: bdud rgyal nag po btul nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2853: dbang bskur ming btags dam tshig phog /
NK038(nyi)003:2854: chos skyong srung mar dam bcas nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2855: rigs nges rgyal ba'i sras su byas //
NK038(nyi)003:2856: de tshe khyod kyi khas blangs nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2857: rnal 'byor yongs kyi grogs bya zhing //
NK038(nyi)003:2858: gtsug gi nor bu 'bar ba ltar //
NK038(nyi)003:2859: bkur zhing dgos pa thams cad bsgrub //
NK038(nyi)003:2860: dam las ma 'da' khas blangs sgrubs //
NK038(nyi)003:2861: bstan pa bsrung ba'i mgon gyur pas //
NK038(nyi)003:2862: de phyir mgon po nag por grags //
NK038(nyi)003:2863: khyod ni sde brgyad kun gyi rje //
NK038(nyi)003:2864: de phyir lang ka'i bdag por grags //
NK038(nyi)003:2865: khyod ni lha srin tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2866: de phyir tshogs bdag chen por grags //
NK038(nyi)003:2867: khyod ni dam chos bsgrub pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2868: de phyir legs ldan nag por grags //
NK038(nyi)003:2869: khyod ni ma mo kun gyi gtso //
NK038(nyi)003:2870: dam nyams rnams kyi gshed ma mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:2871: de phyir sgrol ging chen por grags //
NK038(nyi)003:2872: mtshan drug nas ni spyan 'dren pas //
NK038(nyi)003:2873: gru gsum mthing nag lcags khang nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2874: spyan 'dren ga nas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:2875: dmar gyi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:2876: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:2877: h'u mnga' bdag chen po ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2878: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)003:2879: khro bo'i rgyal po ging chen po //
NK038(nyi)003:2880: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)003:2881: dus ngan gdul ka'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2882: ma thogs myur du bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:2883: rnal 'byor chen po yongs bstod cing //
NK038(nyi)003:2884: khyed la mthun pa'i rdzas 'bul gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:2885: sngon gyi skal pa dang po la //
NK038(nyi)003:2886: khas blangs dam bcas mna' bor ba'i //
NK038(nyi)003:2887: dam bcas tha tshig ma 'da' zhig /
NK038(nyi)003:2888: sngon yang rig 'dzin gong mas bsgrubs //
NK038(nyi)003:2889: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bsgrubs pas //
NK038(nyi)003:2890: bam ri thod pa'i mkhar rtse nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2891: sgrol ging chen po sku bskyod la //
NK038(nyi)003:2892: ru mtshon nag po pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)003:2893: mtshon cha sna tshogs char du 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)003:2894: bdud mda' nag po zengs se zengs //
NK038(nyi)003:2895: bdud bya nag po lding cing 'dzum //
NK038(nyi)003:2896: sna tshogs dur khrod rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)003:2897: mche gtsigs rngam pa'i zhal gdangs nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2898: nyams pa'i snying khrag zhal du rngub //
NK038(nyi)003:2899: lha chen khyod kyi bka' 'khor nas //
NK038(nyi)003:2900: sprul pa'i khro bo khro mor 'khrigs //
NK038(nyi)003:2901: srin po srin mo rkan sgra rdebs //
NK038(nyi)003:2902: gnod sbyin pho mo'i dmag dpung bzlog /
NK038(nyi)003:2903: za byed pho mo sha khrag rol //
NK038(nyi)003:2905: so so'i bzhugs sa tha dad pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:2906: yid bzhin nor bu'i thugs dam ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2907: yongs su rdzogs par bsgrub par byos //
NK038(nyi)003:2908: tshogs bdag chen po 'khor bcas la //
NK038(nyi)003:2909: ma h+aa b+ha ling ta pra ti dza kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2910: ma h+aa mam sa kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2911: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2914: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ru tra ma tra ha ha ho /
NK038(nyi)003:2915: h'u dur khrod bdag po tshur nyon cig /
NK038(nyi)003:2916: mnga' bdag chen po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2917: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa khyod //
NK038(nyi)003:2918: khro bo'i chen po gying chen po //
NK038(nyi)003:2919: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)003:2920: tshogs bdag chen po tshogs la rol //
NK038(nyi)003:2921: lha chen dpal 'bar tshogs la rol //
NK038(nyi)003:2922: ma h+aa ka la tshogs la rol //
NK038(nyi)003:2923: dur khrod bdag po 'khor bcas rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2924: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:2925: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)003:2926: bcol ba'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:2928: yid bzhin nor bu'i sgrub thabs //
NK038(nyi)003:2929: +thiih nga'i bla ma'i zhal nas chos skyongs 'di zhal gcig phyag bzhi par yod par 'dug ste /
NK038(nyi)003:2930: phyag gnyis par byas pa mang bar 'dug /
NK038(nyi)003:2931: phyag bzhi phyag drug rdzu 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)003:2933: de ltar na phyag bzhi'i g.yas gong ma na gri gug /
NK038(nyi)003:2934: 'og ma na tsan dan gi dbyug pa sngon po ste /
NK038(nyi)003:2936: g.yon gong ma na thod khrag /
NK038(nyi)003:2937: 'og ma na lcags kyi par ru nor bu rin po che sna tshogs kyis bkang ste /
NK038(nyi)003:2939: dar nag gi ber yod pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2941: de ltar du byas na gzhung dang mthun par yod par 'dug gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)003:2943: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:2944: su zhig bsnyen bsgrub bzhi la rtag tu gnas 'dod pa des /
NK038(nyi)003:2945: bdag gzhan gyi don bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:2946: gnas dben par sha chen snying chen la sogs pa /
NK038(nyi)003:2947: sha khrag sna tshogs la gtor ma snod bzang ba ban d+ha'am /
NK038(nyi)003:2949: spyan gzigs dkar gsum mngar gsum la phug 'khur ba sgog pa lnga dang /
NK038(nyi)003:2950: 'byor tshad gtor mar blug la gtor ma'i dbus su lha bshos nag po zur gsum pa bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:2952: ma h+aa ka la'i bris sku dgram //
NK038(nyi)003:2953: de nas bdag khro bo che mchog tu bsgom //
NK038(nyi)003:2954: ting nge 'dzin gzengs bstod la bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i sngags sbrel la bzlas so //
NK038(nyi)003:2955: b+hur kur ma h+aa pad+ma rde b+hur byi bye ma
NK038(nyi)003:2956: na se e ho sh+ri kro ta h'u h'u phata
NK038(nyi)003:2957: phata / u tsusma kro ta h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:2959: de re re la yang bsnyen pa 'bum du bsnyen par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:2961: lang ka yul gyi grong brdal gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:2962: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)003:2963: kong ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK038(nyi)003:2964: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo la //
NK038(nyi)003:2965: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:2966: bdud kyi sde rnams btul nas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:2967: gsang sngags dkyil 'khor bskor ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)003:2968: ming gi dbang bskur bran du khas blangs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:2969: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:2970: mgon po nag po chen po dang //
NK038(nyi)003:2971: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:2972: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)003:2973: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2975: pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:2976: 'dir gshegs mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)003:2977: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:2978: bcol pa'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:2979: tshogs kyi bdag po ma h+aa ka la /
NK038(nyi)003:2980: 'dus pa chen po rnal 'byor pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2981: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi ma h+aa b+ha lid+ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2985: go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:2986: e ha hi sta ka lam i dan du pa
NK038(nyi)003:2987: ti pa gan+d+ha b+ha lid+ta pra ti dza ho kh+aa
NK038(nyi)003:2988: hi / ces gtor ma bstabs te mchod /
NK038(nyi)003:2989: tshogs bdag la gtor ma dam rdzas longs spyod dang
NK038(nyi)003:2990: chang phud bdud rtsi dang rak+ta'i rgya mtsho zhal du
NK038(nyi)003:2991: gsol bas mnyes par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:2993: rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyed //
NK038(nyi)003:2994: rdo rje can du gcig nges pa //
NK038(nyi)003:2995: gsang ba gsum dang mnyam sbyar phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:2996: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig sbyin //
NK038(nyi)003:2997: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig 'di //
NK038(nyi)003:2998: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nas byung //
NK038(nyi)003:2999: dal gsum gyi dam pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3000: grub na 'jigs pa'i dus med do //
NK038(nyi)003:3002: e ha hi sa ma ya h'u h+r+ai tha /
NK038(nyi)003:3003: zhes bdud rtsi gtor bas tshogs bdag gi gnas snying
NK038(nyi)003:3004: gar h'u lce la am klad pa'i dung khang du
NK038(nyi)003:3005: thim pa las sku gsung thugs kyi dam pa phog
NK038(nyi)003:3009: ces dam tshig blangs nas dam bcas par bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:3010: de nas dam chu blud pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3011: khro bo'i ting 'dzin gsar la gsang ba gsum gyi dam pa rnams /
