NK038(nyi)003:3012: khyed kyi rab tu bslus gyur na //
NK038(nyi)003:3013: de kun khros nas khrag chen pos //
NK038(nyi)003:3014: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te 'thung //
NK038(nyi)003:3015: i dan te na ra kan /
NK038(nyi)003:3018: sa ma ya rak+sha rak+sha si ti si na badz+ra
NK038(nyi)003:3019: a mri ta ho kan zhes bdud rtsi gtor bas
NK038(nyi)003:3020: / ting nge 'dzin khos bdud rtsi 'thungs pas snying
NK038(nyi)003:3021: la thim pas yi ge h'u mthing nag tu gsal
NK038(nyi)003:3022: / ba de / khos dam ma nyams na bdag gi grogs byas nas ye shes sems dpa' /
NK038(nyi)003:3023: nyams na yak+shasa lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu pas gnyen po byas par bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:3026: zhes bdud rtsi gtor te mna' bsgag par bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:3028: rdo rje chu ste bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:3029: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar //
NK038(nyi)003:3030: bsre ba'i mchog ste srog gi snying //
NK038(nyi)003:3031: snying dang snying gi grogs por bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3032: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya a /
NK038(nyi)003:3033: ces bdag gi lan gsum blangs khos kyang zos 'thung nas dam las mi 'dal bar bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:3034: bdag dang gcig tu 'grogs byed bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:3036: ma h+aa gling gi grub gnas su //
NK038(nyi)003:3037: rdo rje srin po'i spyan sngar ru //
NK038(nyi)003:3038: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3039: dam tshig nyan las ma 'da' cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3040: ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK038(nyi)003:3043: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:3044: ces bcol byas las bcol ba 'agre'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3045: de nas smon lam btab ste /
NK038(nyi)003:3046: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:3052: gtor ma byang shar mtshams su bskyal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:3054: +thii tshogs bdag rgyun gyi yi dam 'di la /
NK038(nyi)003:3055: dang la man+dala bcas la gtor ma dang mchod pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3057: khro bor bsgom la byin gyis rlabs //
NK038(nyi)003:3058: de nas dam mthung gzhung srang /
NK038(nyi)003:3060: bstod pa bya de nas ru las tshogs bdag bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:3071: mgon po cen ltar mchod pa la gtor ma rkyang par gtong na //
NK038(nyi)003:3074: skad cig las dpal du bskyed la //
NK038(nyi)003:3080: de nas mgon po gzhung bsrang la //
NK038(nyi)003:3082: ces pas dur khrod lcags mkhar bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:3084: ru ma h+aa ka la h'u zhes bskyed do //
NK038(nyi)003:3085: de nas ye shes kyi mgon po spyan drangs la bstim pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3087: 'dus pa chen po rnal 'byor 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3088: sa ma ya ha ka lahdzahmh'u bam ho /
NK038(nyi)003:3090: de yang ma h+aa pany+tsa zhes mchod pa la sogs pa dang smon lam btab bo //
NK038(nyi)003:3091: de nas bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i snying po dril la bzlas so //
NK038(nyi)003:3093: rgyun du byas na las gang 'dod 'grub po /
NK038(nyi)003:3094: +thii mgon po la tshogs dbul ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3096: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:3097: bar snang khams na bzhugs tsam na //
NK038(nyi)003:3098: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3099: lag tu rdo rje byin pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3100: dbang bskur ming btags mtshan gsol ba //
NK038(nyi)003:3101: mtshan ni ma h+aa ka la ste //
NK038(nyi)003:3102: tshogs bdag rdo rje phreng ba can //
NK038(nyi)003:3103: bdag gi bsnyen bsgrub mos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)003:3104: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:3105: 'phrin las snyan snyung gsol ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3106: lha yi dgra lha chen por mnga' gsol ba //
NK038(nyi)003:3107: lha min dmag tshogs 'dus pa'i mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)003:3108: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs thal ba'i rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:3109: khyed kyi go mtshon cir yang ma nges kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3110: sku la bse khrab nag po gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3111: g.yas pa gsal shing dgra la 'phyar //
NK038(nyi)003:3112: g.yon pa shin gyi mdung ring bsnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3113: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs thog ser 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)003:3115: kun bzang lha yi spyan snga ru //
NK038(nyi)003:3116: nyid kyi thugs dam zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:3117: khas blangs dam bcas mnyel lam ci //
NK038(nyi)003:3118: dam bcas bzhin du bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3119: nye gnas kro ti shwo ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3120: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:3121: da yang bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3122: srin po'i nye gnas chen po brgyad rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3123: dam rdzas da yang 'gres gus pa'i ma mo chen po brgyad rnams dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3124: dam rdzas da yang dur khrod ma mo sgo bsrung bzhi rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3125: dam rdzas da yang dur khrod bdag mo gru 'degs bzhi rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3126: dam rdzas da yang srin mo chen mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:3127: dam rdzas da yang ma h+aa ka la'i lha tshogs rnams /
NK038(nyi)003:3128: tshogs bdag mgon po 'khor bcas dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3129: yang dag bsrung mar dam bcas shing //
NK038(nyi)003:3130: bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:3131: legs ldan nag po bdud kyi rje //
NK038(nyi)003:3132: gsang mtshan rdo rje ro langs te //
NK038(nyi)003:3133: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3134: dam rdzas da yang bcol pa'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3135: 'khor gnod sbyin sde bzhi thugs dam can //
NK038(nyi)003:3136: kro ta khro bo ging gi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3137: yak+sha gnod sbyin dregs pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3138: rak+sha srin po rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3139: tsit+ta za byed ma mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3140: dam rdzas da yang sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung du gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3141: bka' sdod las mkhan shan pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3142: nag po gri gug thod khrag 'thung //
NK038(nyi)003:3143: khyod ni bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)003:3144: dam nyams dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i ging //
NK038(nyi)003:3145: dam rdzas da yang bstan pa'i dgra bgegs myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)003:3146: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la rak+mo kro ti shwa ri /
NK038(nyi)003:3148: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kh+aa hi //
NK038(nyi)003:3153: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:3155: rak+sha tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya ma h+aa b+ha lid+ta kh+aa hi la sogs brjod ho /
NK038(nyi)003:3160: dregs pa can gyi dbang phyug /
NK038(nyi)003:3161: chos skyong yongs kyi rje bo //
NK038(nyi)003:3162: srin po bya yi gshogs pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:3163: ljang nag chen po phyag na tsan dan gyi beng chen bsnams nas //
NK038(nyi)003:3164: byang phyogs gnod sbyin phyir 'brang zhing //
NK038(nyi)003:3165: lho phyogs gshin rje'i sna 'dren pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3166: tshogs bdag chen po bzhi'i mnga' bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:3167: mon pa nag po dang mgon po nag po'i tshogs la dbang bsgyur ba khyod /
NK038(nyi)003:3168: dam rdzas kyi gtor ma chen po 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:3169: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrungs ba'i phrin las rgya chen po mdzad du gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3170: ces pa la sogs pa gang 'dod pa'i smon lam btab //
NK038(nyi)003:3173: khro bo'i tshogs tha ma'i gong du mdzad cing gada'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3175: dpal ldan mgon po nag po ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3176: mthing nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:3177: khyed kyi gsang ba'i mtshan gsol ba //
NK038(nyi)003:3178: ro langs rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:3179: gsang ba'i mtshan du grags pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:3180: bskal pa bzang po'i yun du ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3181: rnal 'byor yongs kyi mgon po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:3182: dge bsnyen legs ldan nag po lags //
NK038(nyi)003:3183: gang dag chos pa rnams kyis shing //
NK038(nyi)003:3184: rnal 'byor srung mar khas blangs te /
NK038(nyi)003:3186: sa brgyad non pa'i sems dpa' mchog /
NK038(nyi)003:3187: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrungs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3188: rnal 'byor tshogs rnams rdzogs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3189: bskal pa phyi mar lung yang bstan //
NK038(nyi)003:3191: thal bas khyab pa'i zhing zhes par //
NK038(nyi)003:3192: rdzogs sangs rgyas par lung yang bstan //
NK038(nyi)003:3193: khyed kyi mthu dang rtsal gyis su //
NK038(nyi)003:3194: bdud dang srin po la sogs 'dul //
NK038(nyi)003:3195: dgra bgegs ma lus thal bar rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:3196: bstan bsrung khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK038(nyi)003:3197: dpal ldan mgon po nag po che //
NK038(nyi)003:3198: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:3199: phrin las thams cad grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3200: khyod kyi bka' yi 'khor gnas pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3201: chos skyong bsrung ma thams cad dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3202: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:3203: bdag dang rnal 'byor sgrub kun gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3204: dkon mchog phyogs su gtogs pa yi //
NK038(nyi)003:3205: gnod byed thams cad bzlog pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3206: dus ma yin par 'chi ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3207: bkra mi shis pa sna tshogs rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3208: de dag khyod kyi bzlog tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3209: bdag gi don rnam 'grub pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3210: dgra bgegs gtan du gzhom du gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3211: yid yang rtag tu bde ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3212: longs spyod phun sum tshogs ldan shog /
NK038(nyi)003:3214: ji ltar slob mar dam bcas bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:3215: bde gshegs bstan pa khyed nyid la //
NK038(nyi)003:3216: bsrung zhing rgyas par bya ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3217: nad dang rims dang dug rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3218: chu dang mkha' 'gro rkun po dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3219: dus ma yin par 'chi ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3220: bkra mi shis pa thams cad rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3221: de dag khyed kyi bzlog tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3222: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i las rnams mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3226: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:3227: mgon po tshogs bdag gi mdos la drug ste /
NK038(nyi)003:3228: dang po mthun rdzas la sogs te //
NK038(nyi)003:3229: dbus su man+dala gru bzhi pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3230: de'i steng du ri rab gru gsum pa ga la ting lo bzhis brgyan g.yag dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3239: rnga mo la sogs gzugs kyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:3240: bshos bu gru gsum ting lo can //
NK038(nyi)003:3242: ban+d+he nag po g.yag zhon pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3243: ban d+he nag po stag zhon pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3244: bud med nag mo ral pa can la sogs pa nam mkha' dang rgyang bu /
NK038(nyi)003:3246: pho gdong mo gdong khram shing la gzug /
NK038(nyi)003:3247: bshos bu man chad rab nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK038(nyi)003:3250: gnyis pa yi dam gang byed kyi 'phrin las gzhung bsrang la 'dzab bzlas la dpal la bstod /
NK038(nyi)003:3251: gsum pa bskul pa bya zhing bsnyen bsgrub pa'i sngags drag tu bzlas /
NK038(nyi)003:3252: bzhi pa mdos byin gyis rlabs la spyan drangs te 'di skad do //
NK038(nyi)003:3254: lcang lo can gyi pho brang nas //
NK038(nyi)003:3255: nag po chen po spyan 'dren na //
NK038(nyi)003:3256: thugs rjes dgongs la gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3257: bam ri thod mkhar chen po nas //
NK038(nyi)003:3258: dge bsnyen legs ldan chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:3259: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:3260: nag po chen po spyan 'dren na //
NK038(nyi)003:3261: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3262: rnal 'byor dgra bgegs bsgral ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3263: bla med 'bras bu bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:3264: rdzas la brten nas 'bod lags na //
NK038(nyi)003:3265: rnal 'byor mgon gyur dgongs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3266: tshogs bdag de la sbyor ba'i yum //
NK038(nyi)003:3267: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3268: nag po chen po khrag 'thung gtso //
NK038(nyi)003:3269: 'jigs pa'i rgyal mo dbang mo che //
NK038(nyi)003:3270: tshogs bdag dgyes pa bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)003:3271: dam rdzas 'di la dgongs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3272: mchod pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3275: dam rdzas 'di la dgongs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3276: phrin las mdzad phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3277: tshogs bdag chen mo 'khor bcas rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3278: mos shing 'dud pa'i tshul gyis gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3279: dga' dang gus pa'i tshul gyis gshegs su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3280: mgon skyabs phrin las mdzad phyir mkhar bas brtson par
NK038(nyi)003:3281: mdzad dmag bas mang bar glog bas myur bar mdzad
NK038(nyi)003:3282: phyir log 'dren zil gyis gnon cing bsrung ma dam
NK038(nyi)003:3283: par dgongs nas lnga pa mtshan nyid brjod la pu
NK038(nyi)003:3286: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK038(nyi)003:3287: sangs rgyas mi bskyod bstan pa de //
NK038(nyi)003:3288: zhing khams mngon par dga' ba bya //
NK038(nyi)003:3289: de lta bu yi bskal pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:3290: spyir ni 'khor ba thog mtha' med //
NK038(nyi)003:3291: ru trar 'khor ba'i dus tsam na //
NK038(nyi)003:3292: yab la de ni mtshan gsol ba //
NK038(nyi)003:3293: khyim bdag ke'u ka mas bya //
NK038(nyi)003:3294: nyid la de ni mtshan gsol pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3295: thar pa nag po zhes kyang bya //
NK038(nyi)003:3296: g.yog la de ni mtshan gsol ba //
NK038(nyi)003:3297: dan phag nag po zhes kyang bya //
NK038(nyi)003:3336: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK038(nyi)003:3337: dngos po bzhi la gnas bcas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3338: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)003:3358: thub dka' gzhon nul zhe sdang drag po skyes /
NK038(nyi)003:3375: za byed dur phag la sogs te //
NK038(nyi)003:3380: dbang du bsdus te chags pa spyod //
NK038(nyi)003:3384: bya ni ne le sha zan dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3386: 'dom gyi skye bo'i lus dag blangs //
NK038(nyi)003:3387: drag po'i lag bdag myong bar 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:3389: de ltar shin tu brgyud pas ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3390: shin tu rtsub pa'i lus blangs nas //
NK038(nyi)003:3391: drag po'i las bdag myong bar 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:3392: de 'phros nad dang mu ge dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3393: mtshon gyis bskal pa la sogs skyes //
NK038(nyi)003:3394: skye ba de yi phyi ma la //
NK038(nyi)003:3399: skye ba de'i phyi ma la //
NK038(nyi)003:3400: yul ni lang ka pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)003:3401: smad tshong ma'i mngal du zhugs //
NK038(nyi)003:3411: ru tra dregs pa zhes kyang bya //
NK038(nyi)003:3412: nag po gdug pas smyon pa des //
NK038(nyi)003:3418: g.yas na khyung gi rgyal mtshan dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3420: g.yon na zhag pa nag po dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3426: las kyi ded dpon drag po des //
NK038(nyi)003:3427: tshangs pa dang ni brgya byin dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3428: rgyal chen bzhi yi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:3429: gnod sbyin ded dpon bzhi rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3430: khyod kyi bran dang g.yog tu 'khol //
NK038(nyi)003:3431: klu dang sa bdag pho nyar 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)003:3432: dmigs pa'i sems can rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:3433: lang ka mgrin bcu srin po de //
NK038(nyi)003:3434: dregs pa ru tras dbang du byas //
NK038(nyi)003:3435: kun kyang bdag gi gtso bo zer //
NK038(nyi)003:3436: srin phrug kun kyang 'dar zhing rig /
NK038(nyi)003:3437: dregs pa nag po chen po des //
NK038(nyi)003:3438: bltas na kun kyang rgyal bar byed //
NK038(nyi)003:3439: bzung na kun kyang myags par byed //
NK038(nyi)003:3440: gnod sbyin bya yi gshog pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:3441: 'phur bas gzugs khams dbang du sdud //
NK038(nyi)003:3442: 'jig rten srid pa gsum na yang //
NK038(nyi)003:3443: dregs pa bzhi las su zhig che //
NK038(nyi)003:3445: ri rab mdzub mo'i rtse la yang //
NK038(nyi)003:3446: 'jig rten srid pa gsum na yang //
NK038(nyi)003:3447: dregs pas bgying zhing klad la bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:3448: de ltar rtag tu gtum pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3449: dngos po bzhi ni dbang du byas //
NK038(nyi)003:3450: bam ri thod pa mkhar gyi rtse //
NK038(nyi)003:3451: khrag dang gshangs gci sha chen dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3452: rkang dang klad pa klad rgyas dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3453: 'dam gyi phru mas yongs su bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:3455: sbrang ma sbrang rgod bung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3456: sbrul dang sdig pa sdom la sogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3457: kam ka kha keg 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3458: lce spyang stag seng la sogs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:3459: gdug pa can gyi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:3460: lha yi ded dpon ka ru na'i //
NK038(nyi)003:3461: bu mo chung ma ma sring dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3462: 'jig rten dbang phyug lha chen gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3463: ma sring bu mo chung ma rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3464: phrogs nas dbang du byas pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3465: lha chen pho mo 'khor dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:3466: ru tra'i phru ma grong rdal te //
NK038(nyi)003:3467: che mchog rdo rje srin po des //
NK038(nyi)003:3468: sngon byung thugs rjes 'brel ba yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3470: 'bar ba chen po gar dgu yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3471: bcom nas dbang du bsdus byas te //
NK038(nyi)003:3472: thugs rjes 'khor ba'i sa las bsgral //
NK038(nyi)003:3473: dkyil 'khor gsum gyis dbang yang bskur //
NK038(nyi)003:3474: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod bdag /
NK038(nyi)003:3475: ming gis dbang bskur bran du byas //
NK038(nyi)003:3476: rnal 'byor yongs kyi mgon po ste //
NK038(nyi)003:3477: dge bsnyen chen po khros pa'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)003:3478: bam ri thod pa brtsegs pa'i dbus //
NK038(nyi)003:3479: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i gzer chen gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3480: brtan par btab pa'i nad bdag ste //
NK038(nyi)003:3481: khro bdag chen po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3482: mi bzad stag gi sham thabs can //
NK038(nyi)003:3483: dbu gsum phyag drug gdug pa can //
NK038(nyi)003:3484: gdug pa 'dul phyir mtshon cha bsnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3485: zhing chen glang chen ko rlon gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3486: mi bzad stag gi sham thabs can //
NK038(nyi)003:3487: sbrul nag 'jigs pa'i sku rags bcings //
NK038(nyi)003:3488: dbang drag las rnams rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3489: khyed kyi rnal 'byor las mdzod cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3490: lha dmag gnyen la bdud dmag bzlog /
NK038(nyi)003:3492: khyod kyis skyabs cing bsrung du gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3493: shes rab gsum gyi mnyes pa'i yum //
NK038(nyi)003:3494: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3495: thod skyogs khrag gis bkang ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3496: 'bru mar rdzas lnga chang sbyar ba //
NK038(nyi)003:3497: rtag par rang gi longs spyod 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)003:3498: chags pas myos shing skam pas na //
NK038(nyi)003:3499: tshogs bdag nyid kyang gnyis med 'khril //
NK038(nyi)003:3500: de yi 'khor tshogs gsang ba'i yum //
NK038(nyi)003:3501: dur khrod ma mo gru 'degs ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3502: skam ma shin tu skam ma dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3503: ra ro ma dang chang 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3504: chags myos mdangs kyis 'khod pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3505: las bzhi tshul gyis grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3506: srin po'i nye gnas chen po brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:3507: ke'u ri la sogs 'khor gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)003:3508: rab 'jigs dur khrod ma mo brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:3509: rnal 'byor grub pa'i las rdzogs ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3510: yang dag don rnams grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3511: srid pa'i bu mo dri za brgyad //
NK038(nyi)003:3512: stag seng wa spyang bzhad sogs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3513: dur bya bya rog 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3514: bstod cing rngams pa'i tshul du 'khod //
NK038(nyi)003:3515: seng gdong la sogs phra men ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3516: thun 'jug thabs kyi don byed ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3517: gang la gang 'dul grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3518: dur khrod sa yi sgo bsrung bzhi //
NK038(nyi)003:3519: gdong mo brtson mo gar log mo //
NK038(nyi)003:3520: de bzhin 'jug mo chen mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)003:3521: gsang sgo 'dzin cing bka' sgo bsrungs //
NK038(nyi)003:3522: khyed rnams rnal 'byor las mdzod cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3523: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3524: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad la sogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3525: ma mo phra men gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)003:3526: srin mo sha za khrag phrog ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3527: bdud kyi ming 'dzin bla kun ma //
NK038(nyi)003:3528: blon mo dmag dpon ded dpon mo //
NK038(nyi)003:3529: ru dpon pho nya mngag par bcas //
NK038(nyi)003:3530: 'khor bcas pho nya khyed rnams kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3531: bdag cag rnams kyi las grub mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3532: sngon tshe dpa' bo'i spyan snga ru //
NK038(nyi)003:3533: de nas slan chad bka' bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)003:3534: bka' lung bzhin du rjes su sgrubs //
NK038(nyi)003:3535: ji ltar khas blangs ji bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)003:3536: da lta rnal 'byor bdag lus sgrub //
NK038(nyi)003:3537: dam pa'i lung la 'gal gyur na //
NK038(nyi)003:3538: khyed cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying //
NK038(nyi)003:3539: rul myags skam nas tshig par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:3540: zhes ni mna' bor dam bcas so //
NK038(nyi)003:3541: dam bcas de las ma mda' cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3542: ma sring bu mo chung ma rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3543: 'bangs su byas so ma g.yel cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3544: nye gnas gdung ba'i ma sring rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3545: deng nas rgyal ba'i 'bangs yin gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:3546: dam pa rnams kyi bran gyis cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3547: khyed rnams bka' yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)003:3548: bka' yi las byung myur du bsgrub //
NK038(nyi)003:3549: ji ltar ma byams bu la gdung ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:3550: dam tshig can la dung dung gdung bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3551: gang du sring byams ming la brtse ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:3552: dam pa rnams la nges par brtse bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3553: ji ltar khas blangs tshul bzhin sgrubs //
NK038(nyi)003:3554: thugs dang mthun pa'i rdzas 'bul ba'i //
NK038(nyi)003:3555: ji ltar 'dod bzhin bsnams su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3556: ji ltar 'dod bzhin bsnams nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3557: yid dang mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3558: rdzogs pa'i las rnams grub nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3559: phrin las rnam bzhi'i dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3560: dus gsum dbang du bsdus nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3561: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3562: thugs dam gnyan po bdag skongs pas //
NK038(nyi)003:3563: thugs mchog mgon po 'dir gshegs la //
NK038(nyi)003:3564: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di la rol //
NK038(nyi)003:3565: phud dang rak+ta bzhes su gsol //
NK038(nyi)003:3566: phyi yi mchod pa bsngo ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3567: bshos bzang zhal zas mar me dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3568: mi glud rin chen mdzes pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3569: mthun pa'i srog chags gzugs 'bul gyi //
NK038(nyi)003:3570: tshogs bdag yab yum 'khor bcas kyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3571: mdos mchog dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:3572: longs spyod glud kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3574: phul ba 'di dag bzhes nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3575: mkhar gyis sa dgra da srungs shig /
NK038(nyi)003:3576: pho gdong khram shing 'di phul bas //
NK038(nyi)003:3577: phul ba 'di dag bzhes nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3578: pho bdud bsgyur la khrams kha phyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3580: phul ba 'di dag bzhes nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3581: 'khor gyi sa dgra da srungs shig /
NK038(nyi)003:3583: drug pa thugs dam bskang zhing las bcol ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3584: rgyu sha khrag yod na legs /
NK038(nyi)003:3587: klad khrag dbul te 'di skad do //
NK038(nyi)003:3589: tshogs bdag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3590: las la gzhol cing zhal du bstab pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3591: dam nyams dam tshig log pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3592: logs spyod skye bo sngags bzlog mkhan //
NK038(nyi)003:3593: ma nyes klan ka 'tshol ba rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3594: dngos su bsgral ba'i sha khrag dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3595: gzugs la bkug nas bstim la sogs //
NK038(nyi)003:3596: tshogs bdag yab yum thugs dam bskang //
NK038(nyi)003:3597: gti mug sha yi mchod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3598: tshogs bdag yab yum thugs dam bskang //
NK038(nyi)003:3599: bskang gyur phrin las bcol ba ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3600: ma nyes kha yogs da bsgyur cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3601: zhe sdang rus pa'i mchod pa 'dis //
NK038(nyi)003:3602: tshogs bdag yab yum bskang gyur thugs kyi sdug pa zhi ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3603: bar chad 'khu ldog med par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3604: ba su ta yi mchod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3605: tshogs bdag bskang gyur thugs rjes breng breng rgyun ma gcod //
NK038(nyi)003:3606: tsit+ta snying gi mchod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3607: tshogs bdag bskang gyur yid la gnag pa sho ra re //
NK038(nyi)003:3608: go ro tsa na'i mchod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3609: tshogs bdag bskang gyur rgyal po gdan las bskyod pa re //
NK038(nyi)003:3610: zhing chen g.yang gzhi'i mchod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3611: tshogs bskang gyur 'dul zhing mtha' nas zog pa re //
NK038(nyi)003:3612: yan lag bzhi'i mchod pa yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3613: tshogs skongs phyog bzhi dgra rnams rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)003:3614: glo ba rmugs kyi rgyal po yis //
NK038(nyi)003:3615: tshogs skongs 'bangs kyi blo log byed pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3616: grogs kyi gdug pa bshoms pa rnams /
NK038(nyi)003:3617: 'di rnams khyed kyi zhi bar mdzod //
NK038(nyi)003:3618: mdos mchog dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)003:3619: zhes byang shar ram yang na rten yod pa'i sar skyal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:3620: yang na dgra phyogs su bskyal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:3621: ma mo dpon g.yog dang sdeb na bkra shis la mthu che'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3622: mgon po'i mdos zab lags so //
NK038(nyi)003:3623: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:3624: mgon po'i tshogs la bskang ba'i rdzas ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3637: ce spyang dur bya kang ka /
NK038(nyi)003:3643: ban+d+he nag po g.yag zhon pa /
NK038(nyi)003:3647: lha bshos nag po zur gsum pa /
NK038(nyi)003:3648: 'brang rgyas rab nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK038(nyi)003:3658: de rnams ri rab la gzug /
NK038(nyi)003:3659: pho gdong g.yas la khram shing /
NK038(nyi)003:3660: ma mo dag la pho gdong ste /
NK038(nyi)003:3662: shar du khro bo gying gi rten du sed+ge gcig bya /
NK038(nyi)003:3663: lho ru gnod sbyin zangs thogs kyi rten du rta gcig mi bzhi bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3664: nub tu srin po'i rten du r+aa hu la gcig bya /
NK038(nyi)003:3665: byang du ma mo'i rten du mi mo ral pa can cig bya /
NK038(nyi)003:3666: bskong na nang la bzlog na phyi'i /
NK038(nyi)003:3667: rgyas pa la mgon po zhal gyi nam mkha' g.yas g.yon ljang gu dbus nag /
NK038(nyi)003:3668: tsakra rtsibs drug lcags kham nam mkha' shar rgyang bu dkar po gnyis /
NK038(nyi)003:3674: phyogs gsum zan gyis zur la khrag gi thig le bdun bdun byas pa gsum bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3676: dkyil 'khor bdun pa 'di la don gsum ste /
NK038(nyi)003:3681: phyag bcom ldan 'das dang dam h'u khro la bca' ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3683: de la gzhi byin gyis ma brlabs slob dpon mnyes
NK038(nyi)003:3684: na gsang sngags ni snod med cing 'bras rgya gar
NK038(nyi)003:3685: bu med par gdams pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3687: de yang bla ma la rag lus pas bla ma bsten par gdams pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3688: bla ma sangs rgyas dang mnyam par gdams pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3689: snod ldan la sbyin zhing snod med la mi sbyin par gdams pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3693: zhor la gshegs gsol bsdu zhing spyod lam bstan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3702: grangs dbye ba'i sgo nas thabs gang gis sbyang ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3703: gang zag gang gis sbyang ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3705: thabs gang gis sgo nas sbyang ba /
NK038(nyi)003:3717: gnas rdzas gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3719: ye shes dal gyi cho ga'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3721: sngon du bsod nams tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3722: ye shes kyi tshogs stong par bsgom pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3723: dbang chen gzhal yas gdan dang bcas par bsgom pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3725: de la gnyis gtso dang 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)003:3727: rgyu'i he ru ka bskyed cing gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3728: 'bras bu'i he ru ka yab yum bskyed pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3736: gnyis su med par bstim pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3737: byin dbang gi rgyas gdab pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3738: pu tsa rgyas par dbul ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3744: gzhung gsung zhus gdams pa'i nges tshig dang bcas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3747: sngon gyi gdams pa btsal ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3749: lha sgyu ma ltar dmigs pa'i rten dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3750: 'od zer 'phros 'dus khrus byas pa'i thig le'i rten dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3751: nyams su blang ba dngos dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3752: de la lam gang zag rten dang sbyar ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3753: dang po la gnas bdun pa'i rim pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3758: 'gog pa'am brtan pa'i rim pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3759: 'byung ba'am bskyed pa'i rim pa bstan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3764: bka' sdod pho nya la gsum /
NK038(nyi)003:3767: sgom rim nges tshig dang bcas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3769: ru las gtso 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3771: zhal du rngubs bstim ming grangs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3773: dpa' bos byin gyis brlabs te spro ba bskyed pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3774: drag pos sems bskyed 'jug pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3775: dpa' bo'i dam dbog pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3776: drag pos phyag 'tshal zhing gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3779: drag pos dbang blang zhing yon dbul ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3780: drag pos zhal bzhes mna' bskyal ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3781: dpa' bos zhal bzhes dbang bskur ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3782: drag po 'khor bcas la p+au dza dbul zhing mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3783: srog snying phul te bsnyen pa bsgrub bya thabs so //
NK038(nyi)003:3789: las dal bya zhing rdzas bshams pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3790: gzu dpang gsol zhing rdzas bshams pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3791: gzu dpang gsol zhing basngagasa pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3792: pho nya mngag cing bskul ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3793: mtshan ma byung na gdab pa'i las dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3794: sbyor ba'i cho gas bsgral ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3795: phud lhag la bro brdungs ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3796: drag po'i mes las la sbyar ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3797: gtad khram mnan pa'i dal la gsum sngon 'byung dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3804: thod pa dang tsakra bya ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3805: bskyel ba'i sa bstan pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3809: zhor la gshegs gsol go sla /
NK038(nyi)003:3812: bla ma'i gdams pa'i rjed byang byas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3814: dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:3815: mdo phran rnams kyi bshad lugs ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3816: dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3818: snga ma spyir rgyal ba'i zhal nas gsung pa'i bka' la rgyud /
NK038(nyi)003:3819: de la brten te mdzad pa'i bstan bcos man ngag go //
NK038(nyi)003:3820: de yang rgyud ma yin te /
NK038(nyi)003:3821: man ngag tu ngos bzung ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:3822: de la bshad thabs lnga ste /
NK038(nyi)003:3823: man ngag gi ngo bo dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3828: ngo bo gcig la gnyis te /
NK038(nyi)003:3829: brjod bya don gyi man ngag gi ngo bo dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3830: brjod byed tshig gi man ngag gi ngo bo'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3832: bya sla tshegs chung don che dpag dka' ba'i phyir man ngag go //
NK038(nyi)003:3834: de kho na nyid cig char gyi man ngag dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3835: mngon par rtogs pa rims kyi man ngag go //
NK038(nyi)003:3836: snga ma ni rdzogs chen la sogs pa'i man ngag gong dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3837: mdo rang rang gi de kho na nyid cig char man ngag la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3839: theg pa spyi la 'jug pa mngon par rtogs pa rim gyi man ngag dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3840: theg pa gnas skabs la 'jug pa mngon par rtogs pa rim gyis pa'i man ngag go //
NK038(nyi)003:3841: snga ma ni theg chen sgron ma dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3842: theg pa chen po shes rab kyi rim pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3845: skol mdo bcu gnyis pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3847: gnas skabs kyi man ngag la gnyis te /
NK038(nyi)003:3848: rgyud dbu zhabs spyi la 'jug pa mngon par rtogs
NK038(nyi)003:3849: pa tshig rgyud gtan la 'bebs pa'i man ngag dang
NK038(nyi)003:3850: / rgyud gnas skabs la 'jug pa mngon par rtogs
NK038(nyi)003:3851: pa rgyud don bslab cing nyams su blangs ba'i man
NK038(nyi)003:3852: / ngag go // rgyud ci la 'jug pa mngon
NK038(nyi)003:3853: par rtogs pa rim gyis man ngag ni bzhi ste
NK038(nyi)003:3854: / ngag go // / 'brel pa ni lung bstan ye shes snang ba rgyan dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3860: rnam bshad chen po la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3861: khog dbub pa'i man ngag ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3862: don bsdus rgya po dza che d+har+m+aa bo d+hi chung dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3863: byung rgyal po dza tshul bsdus pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3865: me long d+har+m+aa bo d+hi gsal byed /
NK038(nyi)003:3867: man ngag spyi gcod grangs bdun bstan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3868: sa gcod kyi man ngag ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3869: rnam shan+ta rak+ai ta grangs gser gzong la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3870: tig ga'am gegs sel gyi man ngag ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3871: ser ka rtsa 'grel la sogs pa'i man ngag rnams so //
NK038(nyi)003:3872: rgyud gnas skabs la 'jug pa'i man ngag ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3873: don bsdus la gzhi gzungs ba dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3874: rgyud 'grol dang sgo mo sdur dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3876: thag bcad pa dang nyams blangs dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3877: la dor spyod pa dbang rim dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3878: man ngag don dang mdor bsdus rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:3879: rnal 'byor bslab pa'i mtha' bcur bzhed /
NK038(nyi)003:3880: zhes pas bcu ru bshad pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3881: lung bstan las lta spyod dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3884: brgyad du gtan la 'bebs pa yin //
NK038(nyi)003:3885: ces pa rgyud don brgyad du bshad de /
NK038(nyi)003:3886: de kho na nyid lta ba'i man ngag ni //
NK038(nyi)003:3891: lam ring stod me long bstan pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3896: gong gi theg pa spyi la 'jug pa'i man ngag tu ngos bzung ba kun no //
NK038(nyi)003:3897: gnyis pa zin chags med pa spyod pa'i man ngag ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3898: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:3903: lung gi rdo rje las rim dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3904: dal gyi mngon la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3905: bzhi pa rim pa bkod pa dbang gi man ngag ni rin chen phreng ba'i smad dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3906: rna rgyud rdo rje zam pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3910: dbang don rgya chen bshad pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3911: dbang gi man ngag gsang ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3913: dbang gi rim pa la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3914: lnga pa mi 'da' ba dam tshig gi man ngag ni dam tshig can 'phrang chen po dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3916: dam tshig spyi khrus bshags pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3918: khrus lung rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3919: drug pa don du gnyer ba bsgrub pa'i man ngag ni gnyis te /
NK038(nyi)003:3928: skabs ra ta ma ti 'grel dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3929: ru tra lam rgyal po dza rtsa 'grel la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3930: bdun las g.yo dor pa rim yin rol pa phrin las kyi rim pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3932: ro bi ma la bsreg bcu bzhi pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3933: mdo'i bi ma dngos po gnyis pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3935: drag po bde bar gsal mdzad 'dul byed la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3936: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi man ngag ni gnyis te /
NK038(nyi)003:3937: mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi man ngag ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3938: zhi khro rtog pa bi ma la lha brgyud kyi man ngag dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3939: khro bo h'u ka ra las rtsa 'phreng dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3940: bsam gtan d+harma bo d+hi cho ga'i sgron ma la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3941: mtshan med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis man ngag ni /
NK038(nyi)003:3947: bsam gtan rig pa'i nyi ma dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3948: bsam gtan yig sgron rtsa 'grel dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3949: bsam gtan me long snang ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3951: bdud rtsi lung gi bsam gtan dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3952: bsam gtan sgron ma la sogs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:3953: man ngag gi dgos ched la bzhi ste gzhung 'thor ba gcig tu bsdus pa'i dgos ched /
NK038(nyi)003:3954: rtogs dka' bde blag tu rtogs pa'i dgos ched /
NK038(nyi)003:3955: gang zag mos pa dang tha dad 'dir mos gzhug pa'i dgos ched /
NK038(nyi)003:3956: chos kyi bya ba mang ba'i dgos ched do //
NK038(nyi)003:3957: bshad thabs dngos la lnga ste /
NK038(nyi)003:3958: yid ches shing khungs btsun par bya ba'i phyir rgyud
NK038(nyi)003:3959: sku che ba'i lo rgyus dang rtsom pa'i tshe gang
NK038(nyi)003:3961: bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshug par
NK038(nyi)003:3962: bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gang
NK038(nyi)003:3964: bstan pa la mtshan nges shing don gyi mdo tsam
NK038(nyi)003:3965: zhig rtogs par bya ba'i phyir mtshan ci las gdags
NK038(nyi)003:3966: pa dang / rtsams pa don yod par bya ba'i phyir gang zag su'i don du mdzad pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3967: man ngag gi don shes shing khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir dbu zhabs su //
NK038(nyi)003:3969: de rnams man ngag rang rang gi skabs dang sbyar la rgyas par bshad do //
NK038(nyi)003:3970: mtshan las 'dogs lugs lnga ste don dpe /
NK038(nyi)003:3982: gsum mam bzhi'am lnga la sogs pa'am /
NK038(nyi)003:3983: ban+d+he mgon po yis mdos phran khog dbubs 'di rje yi gsung la brten /
NK038(nyi)003:3985: khog dbub me ston mgon pos mdzad rdzogs so //
NK038(nyi)003:3986: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:3987: mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3988: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la zhus pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3990: srid pa yongs kyi dgrar langs kyang //
NK038(nyi)003:3991: skabs dang las dbang dpung chung pas //
NK038(nyi)003:3992: gtan du 'grogs shing bza' kha cig /
NK038(nyi)003:3993: kha dam snying ring zhe mkhon gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3994: lha khros bdag la chad pa gcod //
NK038(nyi)003:3995: bdag phung brlag srid ji ltar bgyis //
NK038(nyi)003:3996: de skad ces ni gsungs pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:3997: ma h+aa gu rus bka' stsal pa //
NK038(nyi)003:3998: mnga' bdag rgyal po chen po lags //
NK038(nyi)003:3999: 'khon la rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NK038(nyi)003:4000: khri lan dum kyi 'grogs shing za kha cig pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:4001: nan dbang drag pos 'grogs shing za kha cig pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:4002: kha dam zhe nag dbang med 'grog shing za kha cig pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:4003: 'gras che zhing nag stabs kyi za kha cig pa dang bzhi'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4004: mnga' bdag rgyal po chen po lags //
NK038(nyi)003:4005: khri lan 'khon rnams bag kyis sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)003:4006: khri lan rdzas rnams cha bzhir bsgo //
NK038(nyi)003:4007: cha gcig dkon mchog mchod rdzas bya //
NK038(nyi)003:4008: cha gcig mkha' 'gro'i gtor tshogs bya //
NK038(nyi)003:4009: cha gcig sngags pa bdag nyid za //
NK038(nyi)003:4010: cha gcig 'gro drug yongs la bsngo //
NK038(nyi)003:4011: gtang rag nyid dang da ka yin //
NK038(nyi)003:4012: nan dbang drag pos 'grogs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:4013: dbang med ngan rdzas btab pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:4014: 'gras chen gsum ni don gnyis sdeb //
NK038(nyi)003:4015: 'khon nag rang sar bzhag pa dang //
NK038(nyi)003:4017: mi dmigs gsum gyis zin pas na //
NK038(nyi)003:4018: 'khon nag rang sar bzhig pa yin //
NK038(nyi)003:4019: kho yi tshe srog 'phrog pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:4020: bdag gi phung po skye mched rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:4021: lhag pa'i lha yi dal du bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:4022: thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' bsam //
NK038(nyi)003:4023: mdun du chos skyong bsrung ma bskyed //
NK038(nyi)003:4024: kho yi rang sa'i zas dang skom //
NK038(nyi)003:4025: zas ni kho yi tshe yin te //
NK038(nyi)003:4026: skom ni kho yi snying khrag yin //
NK038(nyi)003:4027: tshe dang srog dbug khrag la rten //
NK038(nyi)003:4028: khrag kyang r+n+ri yi rang bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)003:4029: r+n+ri ni dgra bo'i srog tu shes //
NK038(nyi)003:4030: snying khrag r+n+ri ru gnas pa de //
NK038(nyi)003:4031: lag pa hom spar lcags sder gyis //
NK038(nyi)003:4032: rang dbang med par bdag la bstab //
NK038(nyi)003:4033: bdag gi phung po'i lha tshogs kyi //
NK038(nyi)003:4034: sha dang khrag dang bcud la rol //
NK038(nyi)003:4035: kho nyid sdong po dgyel ba 'dra //
NK038(nyi)003:4036: lhag mas chos skyong bsrung ma mnyes //
NK038(nyi)003:4037: r+n+ri yi bdag nyid lus sems rgyas //
NK038(nyi)003:4038: tshe dang bkrag dang gzi mdangs ldan //
NK038(nyi)003:4039: de ltar bsam pas stobs bskyed la //
NK038(nyi)003:4040: gtang rag nyid kyang de dag ste //
NK038(nyi)003:4041: bar chad rtseg log ci la yong //
NK038(nyi)003:4042: 'di yang ngan thabs sbyor ba ste //
NK038(nyi)003:4044: gu rus gdams pas rgyal po mnyes //
NK038(nyi)003:4045: ma dpe bum thang gter du sbas //
NK038(nyi)003:4046: rno myur log pa med pas chongs //
NK038(nyi)003:4048: dpal gsang ba'i sbas pa'i chang drug rdo rje nag po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:4049: ma h+aa ka la'i man ngag /
NK038(nyi)003:4051: gud du sbas pa'i chong chung //
NK038(nyi)003:4053: sngags kyi spu gri 'dir bstan par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4056: bka' sdod pho nya'i dal la dar //
NK038(nyi)003:4057: 'brub khung las kyi dal dang mtha'i bsdud mnan pa'i dal gsum //
NK038(nyi)003:4058: ma h+aa ka la sgrub gzhung de //
NK038(nyi)003:4059: rgyas par gzhung du bkod pa bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:4061: bca' lugs gtor ma la sogs kun //
NK038(nyi)003:4062: gzhung bzhin bshams te mthun par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:4063: phyir bsnyen 'bur kur tshe bzhi la //
NK038(nyi)003:4064: grangs ni 'bum phrag re re bskyal //
NK038(nyi)003:4065: bya thabs bsgom lugs gzhan gsung bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:4066: khyad par 'di ni bsad pa'i mchong //
NK038(nyi)003:4067: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yi bsad pa bstan //
NK038(nyi)003:4068: dang pos bsnyen pas bsad pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:4069: bcu gnyis rtsibs ldan tsakra la //
NK038(nyi)003:4070: bsnyen pa'i sngags bkod dkyil du bgrad //
NK038(nyi)003:4071: phyi ma'i mu khyud ye shes lha //
NK038(nyi)003:4072: nag po phyag gnyis gri thod can //
NK038(nyi)003:4073: de yi lte bar chud bris la //
NK038(nyi)003:4075: sngags mthar spu gri gcod byed sbyar //
NK038(nyi)003:4076: che ge mo m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4078: h'u h'u phata phata s+w+aa h+aa rnam par dor //
NK038(nyi)003:4079: thun rdzas sngags shing gung gnyis brab //
NK038(nyi)003:4080: 'khor bzhis bsad pa'i sngags kyang brjod //
NK038(nyi)003:4081: mchod gzhung yid bzhin nor bu snyag /
NK038(nyi)003:4082: phyi nang gsang ba'i bskul pa'am //
NK038(nyi)003:4083: pho nya rgyas bsdus spros dang sbyar //
NK038(nyi)003:4084: gtor tshogs dbul zhing bskang mchod bya //
NK038(nyi)003:4085: rmi lam nyams sbyar lid+ga bsad //
NK038(nyi)003:4086: mnan bsreg 'phang bas las mtha' brtul //
NK038(nyi)003:4087: des ni nyams pa sgrol bar 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:4088: nye bsnyen bdag gis bsad 'dod na //
NK038(nyi)003:4089: nye bsnyen tsakra rtsibs bcu gnyis //
NK038(nyi)003:4090: nye bsnyen sngags bkod dkyil dang mtha' /
NK038(nyi)003:4091: gong ma bdag dang nges mthun sbyar //
NK038(nyi)003:4092: nag po zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i //
NK038(nyi)003:4093: ltor chu bris la 'brub khung ste //
NK038(nyi)003:4094: rtsang gi kha la brgyangs te bzhag /
NK038(nyi)003:4095: sngags mthu spru gri gdags par bya //
NK038(nyi)003:4096: che ge mo ma ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4097: thun brab bcol bskul bskang tshogs rnams //
NK038(nyi)003:4098: gong du bstan pa bzhin shes par bya ste //
NK038(nyi)003:4100: bsgrub pa bdag gis bsad 'dod na //
NK038(nyi)003:4101: tsakra rtsibs brgyad bsgrub sngags dgod //
NK038(nyi)003:4102: zhal gcig phyag gnyis ltor chu bri //
NK038(nyi)003:4103: mtha' dbus bsnyen pa'i bri tshul bzhin //
NK038(nyi)003:4104: sngags la bsad pa'i spu gri gdags //
NK038(nyi)003:4105: che ge mo m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4106: gzhan ni gang yang gong mar mthun //
NK038(nyi)003:4107: nyams pa gang yin nges sgrol 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:4108: bsgrub chen bdag gi bsad 'dod na //
NK038(nyi)003:4110: dkyil mtha' bsnyen pa'i skabs bzhin bri //
NK038(nyi)003:4111: zhal gsum phyag drug lto bar ro //
NK038(nyi)003:4112: sngags mthar spu gri gdags ste bsad //
NK038(nyi)003:4113: che ge mo ma ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4114: sde bsad 'dod na kun la yang //
NK038(nyi)003:4115: spu gri nges pa 'di dag sbyar //
NK038(nyi)003:4116: sarba sha trum m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4117: pha tshan sde bsad man ngag go //
NK038(nyi)003:4118: gang byed kun la bar skabs su //
NK038(nyi)003:4119: rbad sngags 'dis kyang las la bskul /
NK038(nyi)003:4120: ru tra ma tra ma ra tra /
NK038(nyi)003:4125: srog la thum ril ri rbad b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:4126: gang byed sngags la nga ro dbyung //
NK038(nyi)003:4127: zur gsal mi tshig gnyid la 'dre //
NK038(nyi)003:4128: bar ma bcad par smra bcad bzlas //
NK038(nyi)003:4129: the tshom spangs te bsad pas bsgrub //
NK038(nyi)003:4130: gnas dben mi 'grul rnam par bcad //
NK038(nyi)003:4131: gang la bya ba gdon mi za //
NK038(nyi)003:4132: grangs ni khri phrag re re ste //
NK038(nyi)003:4133: de yang rmi rtags mtshan nyams ces //
NK038(nyi)003:4134: sod pa'i rtags mang nges ldan la //
NK038(nyi)003:4135: phur pa btab cing gris gtub rtsegs //
NK038(nyi)003:4136: mtha' bsdud las mtha' brtul bar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4137: de ltar ma yin don med 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)003:4138: rnal 'byor nyams drod ldan pa gces //
NK038(nyi)003:4141: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:4142: sngags kyis mthus yig bstan pa ni //
NK038(nyi)003:4143: ye shes lha yi bsnyen pa la //
NK038(nyi)003:4144: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:4145: gtso 'khor bcas pa'i sngags kyang yin la gtso 'khor bskyangs pa yang de nyid do //
NK038(nyi)003:4146: ye shes lha'i bsad pa'i sngags ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4147: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:4148: sarba sha trum ma ra ya phatah che ge mo
NK038(nyi)003:4149: m+aa ra ya phatah las kyi lha gtso 'khor 'dus
NK038(nyi)003:4150: pa'i sngags ni / b+hu ru ku ma h+aa ka la ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4151: kro ta ya k+sha tsid de d+he ba rak+sha a ta /
NK038(nyi)003:4153: mchod 'bul gang yang sham bu'i sngags so so'i btags la 'bul /
NK038(nyi)003:4154: pany+tsa a mri ta rak+ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:4155: ma h+aa b+ha lid+ha kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:4156: zhes pa'i dam tshig mgon po'i sku bskyed pa'i /
NK038(nyi)003:4157: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya ces pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4158: rang rgyud pa'i mgon po spyan drangs pa'i sngags ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4159: bur ma ha ka la sa ma ya hrim hrim /
NK038(nyi)003:4162: badz+ra kro ka dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4163: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4164: tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4166: 'khor tshogs pa bsad pa'i sngags ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4167: badz+ra kro ti dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4168: sarba sha trum ma ra ya phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4169: che ge mo ma ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4170: gsum po la gdags pa des 'agre'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4171: dgra bo dgug pa'i sngags ni ye shes lha dang las kyi lha kun gyi mjug la'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4172: che ge mo a kar+sha ya dza /
NK038(nyi)003:4174: ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:4175: che ge mo a kar+sha ya dzahdzah badz+ra am ku
NK038(nyi)003:4176: sha dza dzah b+hu kur i tsi kyi phyi u
NK038(nyi)003:4177: tsush+ma kro ta / che ge mo badz+ra a kar+sha
NK038(nyi)003:4178: ya dza dzah badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la ma ya
NK038(nyi)003:4179: che ge mo badz+ra ar+sha ya dza dza /
NK038(nyi)003:4180: badz+ra am ku sha dza dzah gsum po 'gre /
NK038(nyi)003:4181: lha dbye gong gi sngags so so la btags pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4182: che ge mo'i de ba pra be sha ya phata phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4184: che ge mo a be sha ya a a /
NK038(nyi)003:4186: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la e ho shwa mo
NK038(nyi)003:4187: kro ta du pa pu tsa pra ti dza h'u
NK038(nyi)003:4188: s+w+aa h+aa / zhes pa la sogs sbyar /
NK038(nyi)003:4192: ne wi t+ye shap+ta la sogs dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4193: pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:4195: bsnyen sgrub bzhi sngags ni go sla'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4197: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:4198: mgon po ji tsam sgrub kyang las mi byed cing g.yel la 'khor du khro 'jug che na /
NK038(nyi)003:4199: nag po gzer cing dbang bu bsdu ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4200: bdag nyid he ru ka'i ting nge 'dzin gsal 'dris su bya te /
NK038(nyi)003:4201: bsnyen sgrub kyi bungs bskyed la /
NK038(nyi)003:4202: mgon po'i tsakli nyid thod ngan du bcug ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4203: 'brub khung du mgo thur la bcugs te gzhug /
NK038(nyi)003:4204: h'u b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la a kar+sha ya
NK038(nyi)003:4205: dza dzah badz+ra am ku sha dza dza ces bzlas
NK038(nyi)003:4206: pas bstim zhing bstim par bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:4207: rang gi lag pa g.yas su gsal shing thogs /
NK038(nyi)003:4208: g.yon du lcags phur thogs la /
NK038(nyi)003:4209: h'u ru lu ru lu h'u phata b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:4210: phata h'u ta kro rma tsu phyi kyi tsi li kur b+hur /
NK038(nyi)003:4211: zhes drag po cung zhig bzlas la /
NK038(nyi)003:4212: de nas mtshang 'bru zhing phur pas sdigs par bya ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4213: sngags de nyid kyi mgo drangs la /
NK038(nyi)003:4214: tshig so so 'di brjod la gdab tshul bstan /
NK038(nyi)003:4215: khyed ru tra nag por skyes pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4216: bsgral ba'i zhing ma shes pa de ni ma rig
NK038(nyi)003:4217: pas lan pa yin pas ma rig pa'i rgya mdud
NK038(nyi)003:4218: gzhom pa'i phyir / khyod kyi lto ba'i dkyil du ki la ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4219: ma h+aa ka la big nan /
NK038(nyi)003:4221: dgra bo che ge mo'i srog la thun bzlog bzlog /
NK038(nyi)003:4222: des 'og ma kun la 'gre shes par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4223: khyod zhe sdang chung bas las ma grub yin pas /
NK038(nyi)003:4224: snying gi dkyil du k+ai la ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4225: ma h+aa ka la big nan la sogs 'gre /
NK038(nyi)003:4226: khyod phrag dog gis mig dang sems g.yengs pas ldan pa'i phyir /
NK038(nyi)003:4227: mig dang rna ba la k+ai la ya 'gre khyed gzhan kyi ru bgrod pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4228: bza' btung gi dbang du stong ste byams pas las
NK038(nyi)003:4229: ma grub pas kha dang sna la ki la ya
NK038(nyi)003:4230: / khyod la rngan pa'i byin pa la ltas shing log pas las ma grub pa yin pas /
NK038(nyi)003:4231: dpral ba'i dkyil du ki la ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4232: de ltar sdigs pa'i sa re rer sngags lan re rer gcig pas sdigs so //
NK038(nyi)003:4233: de nas sngags gong ma bzlas shing khrag dang yungs kar gyi thun brab /
NK038(nyi)003:4235: shar rog gi me sgron gyis sdigs /
NK038(nyi)003:4236: dbang du bsdu ba'i sngags de gsum brgya las mang na rang la bkra mi shis pa 'ong ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4237: chos skyong dang rang nyid shin tu zhe 'gras pas rang phung bar 'gyur la /
NK038(nyi)003:4238: man ngag 'di yod cing shes pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4239: khyod la 'di byed do bya ba bag res sdigs so //
NK038(nyi)003:4240: bka' nyan cing 'khu ldog chung ba las byed do //
NK038(nyi)003:4241: de bas na man ngag 'di shes pa yang gal che la /
NK038(nyi)003:4242: phal cher ni ma byas na bkra shis pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4243: chos skyong snying thag nye ba yin gsung ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:4244: de nas ru'am krum las b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)003:4246: ces lan nyer gcig bzlas shing /
NK038(nyi)003:4248: ma h+aa ka la pany+tsa a mri kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:4249: ces bdud rtsi mang du gtor bas shi ba sos par bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:4250: ma h+aa k+aa la b+ha lid+ta kh+aa h+ai /
NK038(nyi)003:4251: ces pas gtor ma mang du bsngosa shing spungs pa shin tu stobs bskyed par bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:4252: ma h+aa k+aa la rak+sha kh+aa hi /
NK038(nyi)003:4254: rak+ta bstab pas 'thungs te bkrag dang gzi mdangs 'bar bar bsam mo //
NK038(nyi)003:4255: de nas bsnyen bsgrub kyi sngags cung zhig bzlas pas /
NK038(nyi)003:4256: 'khor g.yog mang po rnams dang bcas par bsam /
NK038(nyi)003:4257: de nas drag sngags bzlas shing las la rbad do //
NK038(nyi)003:4258: dbang bsdud gzir mnan gyi 'chong ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:4259: +thii rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:4260: sngags pa gzhan las mgon po 'di bsgrubs nas bdag
NK038(nyi)003:4261: la rbad pas bdag phung la khad par gyur na
NK038(nyi)003:4262: / mgon po rang gshed la dbab cing shi sa bstan par bya dgos so //
NK038(nyi)003:4263: de yang thog mar gtor ma dang mdos la sogs
NK038(nyi)003:4264: pa'i yang yang bskang la don bden pa'i stobs mang
NK038(nyi)003:4265: du brjod / ngan song gi g.yang sa bshad la zhi bar bzlog par bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4266: des kyang zhi bar ma gyur te srog la bsdo na las 'di bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4267: gru gsum thod nang du ling+ga gzhug /
NK038(nyi)003:4268: de'i 'og tu dgra bo'i ling+ga bcug la /
NK038(nyi)003:4269: dgra bo bkug bstim dang por bya /
NK038(nyi)003:4270: de nas mgon po dkug bstim bya ste gzi 'chong ltar bya /
NK038(nyi)003:4271: bdag he ru ka'i bzlas bsgoms rdzogs shing gsal ba des /
NK038(nyi)003:4272: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan gyon la /
NK038(nyi)003:4273: lcags phur dang mthun rdzas thogs te /
NK038(nyi)003:4274: dang la ye shes lha'i sngags sdebs can gyis mgo drangs ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4279: u ne u ne u ne /
NK038(nyi)003:4280: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK038(nyi)003:4282: phata h'u kro ta rma tsu u phyi kyi tsi i kur b+hur /
NK038(nyi)003:4283: nga la gnod pa'i mgon nag ma h+aa ka la big nan /
NK038(nyi)003:4288: tsa ta khas gzer thum ril /
NK038(nyi)003:4293: dam nyams che ge mo kho rang gi srog la thun bzlog bzlog b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)003:4294: che ge mo r+n+ri tsit+ta hur thum /
NK038(nyi)003:4296: ban+d+he'i srog la ma ra ya rbad rbad rbad /
NK038(nyi)003:4297: thun re la bargya'am stong gis gnyis ka stabs gcig tu bsad do //
NK038(nyi)003:4300: rdo rje srin po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)003:4301: ma h+aa ka la'i phung byed dug gi spu grir can /
NK038(nyi)003:4302: rno la myur ba'i las la /
NK038(nyi)003:4303: gzhan la med pa'i gsang yig go //
NK038(nyi)003:4304: ma h+aa ka la'i rten gsum gzug ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4305: phyi'i rten ni g.yag rog po'am /
NK038(nyi)003:4306: lug nag po'i skye ru srog gi snying po gser gyi bris pa la rab gnas bya ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4307: btags la bsngo zhing bstab bo //
NK038(nyi)003:4308: nang gi rten ni bya rog gi nang du rgyal
NK038(nyi)003:4309: mtshan la gser gyis bris pa'i srog snying nang du
NK038(nyi)003:4311: gsang ba'i rten ni skyes pa dar ma shi ba'i
NK038(nyi)003:4312: snying gi nang du srog snying gser yig tu bris
NK038(nyi)003:4313: pa bcug la / snying de'i mthar rin po che sna tshogs dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4314: sman bzang po du mas bskor ba dar nag tu gtum la mis mi mthong bar lus la btag /
NK038(nyi)003:4315: gzhan yang mchod rdzas gtor ma dang bdud rtsi rak+ta yang bsham /
NK038(nyi)003:4316: sha mar dang chang la sogs pa spyan gzigs mang
NK038(nyi)003:4317: na yang bkra shis la mi nor rab tu 'phel
NK038(nyi)003:4318: lo // ye shes lha'i bsnyen pa sngon du rdzogs par bya ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4319: dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka'i bzlas bsgom mo //
NK038(nyi)003:4320: de nas yang ma h+aa k+aa la'i mchod gzhung snyag pa ni yid bzhin nor bu'i las ltar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4321: de nyid kyi bsnyen pa ni bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba 'dis rtags rdzogs par bzlas so //
NK038(nyi)003:4322: b+hur kur i tsi kyi phyi u tsut+ma kro ta h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4323: de nas las la sbyar ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4324: 'brub khung nag por thod ngan gyi nang du /
NK038(nyi)003:4325: dgra bo'i ling ga bzhag ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4326: sa bzhag dang bag phyes mgo bsdus la kho'i dri ma gang rnyed la bya /
NK038(nyi)003:4327: ming rus bris la rlan la dgug bstim byas ste spyir mthun /
NK038(nyi)003:4328: yang na nag po nyid kyis byas na legs so //
NK038(nyi)003:4329: thun rdzas ni dug dang khrag gis ngar blud pa'i
NK038(nyi)003:4330: yungs kar dang yungs nag la bya ste sngags cing
NK038(nyi)003:4331: nyin gung dang mtshan gung la brab bo //
NK038(nyi)003:4332: phur pa lcags sam shing nag po la byas la /
NK038(nyi)003:4333: mgon por mnga' gsol la gru gsum gcig la gzugs so //
NK038(nyi)003:4334: de nas las kyi bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4335: thog mar bzhi snying dril ba la ming rus dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4337: b+hu kur i tsi kyi phyi u tsut+ma kro ta che ge mo m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4338: zhes pa la dgra bo'i srog gi rtags rnyed tsam du bzlas so //
NK038(nyi)003:4340: phung byed nag po rbad pa'i 'dzab 'di ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4342: bdag nyid kyi las kyi mgon po nag po sngo
NK038(nyi)003:4343: skya ba g.yas gri gug g.yon thod khrag can zhabs
NK038(nyi)003:4344: brkyangs bskum bgrad cing rngam pa 'khor bdud dang srin
NK038(nyi)003:4345: po khros shing rngam pa grangs med la las bkye
NK038(nyi)003:4346: bar bsgom zhing / shin tu ma rungs pa khros
NK038(nyi)003:4347: pa'i sems kyi drag po'i ngar phyung la bzlas so
NK038(nyi)003:4348: bar bsgom zhing / // b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la rak+sha kro ta /
NK038(nyi)003:4349: che ge mo'i srog la phrig phrig /
NK038(nyi)003:4352: hu ru hu ru nag po snying rtsa la breng breng /
NK038(nyi)003:4354: ni sha ku ru r+n+ri dza /
NK038(nyi)003:4355: che ge mo thum ril ma ra ya rbad /
NK038(nyi)003:4356: 'dis dgra bo'i bla rtags phal cher sod sod tsam bya'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4358: skabs su khrag dang yungs kar la sngags te zor tu'am /
NK038(nyi)003:4359: thod par bstim la 'phang du'ang rung ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:4360: de nas las sbyor bsad pa dngos la 'jug pa ni /
NK038(nyi)003:4361: lcags sam mkhar ba nag po btsugs te /
NK038(nyi)003:4362: rang nyid lang la gos nag po gyon /
NK038(nyi)003:4364: khros shing rngam pa gdug cing rtsub pa'i sems kyis
NK038(nyi)003:4365: gang la bya ba dus gcig tu brlag par byed
NK038(nyi)003:4366: cing / sha rus dang snying la sogs pa la
NK038(nyi)003:4367: phar spyang sha la rngam pa ltar du bdud srin
NK038(nyi)003:4368: po'i tshogs kyis bstod cing rub nas za bar bsgom
NK038(nyi)003:4369: cing / / sngags pa gnyis sam gsum gyi bar ma chad par bsad par bya ste /
NK038(nyi)003:4370: gang ma thun res ma bab pa des tshogs dang gtor ma btang pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4371: phyi nang gsang ba'i bskul pa'am /
NK038(nyi)003:4372: pho nya ring thung gang spro bas bskul du rung ngo //
NK038(nyi)003:4373: mi spro na ma byas kyang chog /
NK038(nyi)003:4374: ngan sngags kyi ma dor ba dug gi spu gri nag po 'di ru /
NK038(nyi)003:4375: shin tu sgra dag pa zur phyin pa /
NK038(nyi)003:4376: rngam pa'i nga ro dang bcas pas bzlas pa 'di kho na 'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4377: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la e he shwa mo
NK038(nyi)003:4378: kro ta che ge mo'i srog thug thug m+aa ra
NK038(nyi)003:4379: ya dza / che ge mo'i srog rbud rbud ma ra ya dza /
NK038(nyi)003:4380: che ge mo'i tshe la dum rbud /
NK038(nyi)003:4382: che ge mo'i snying khrag ljib ljib /
NK038(nyi)003:4386: ma ma trag ru tra dgra bo ma ra ya phata /
NK038(nyi)003:4388: zhag grangs nges pa med do //
NK038(nyi)003:4389: rmi rtags la gsod nges pa'i rtags byung ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4393: dug shing la me sbar la bsreg go //
NK038(nyi)003:4398: mnan pa bya mi dgos so //
NK038(nyi)003:4399: bsad pa dug gi spu gri nag po'i 'chang ngo /
NK038(nyi)003:4401: sh+r+ai ma h+aa k+aa la na mo /
NK038(nyi)003:4402: mgon po tshogs bdag gi mdos la /
NK038(nyi)003:4403: ri rab la sogs pa gzhung dang mthun par bshams te /
NK038(nyi)003:4404: ri rab kyi dbus su ma h+aa ka la mthing nag ber dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK038(nyi)003:4405: rgyan dang na bza' gzhung dang mthun pa zhig dgod do //
NK038(nyi)003:4406: de bzhin du mdun du kro ti shwa ri cha lugs yab dang mthun pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4407: g.yas su las kyi bdud pho bya rog gdong can nag po gri gug bsnams pa zhabs rdebs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4408: rgyab tu las kyi bdud mo nag mo lcags kyu dang thod khrag can no //
NK038(nyi)003:4409: g.yon du las kyi srin po smug nag ral gri
NK038(nyi)003:4410: dang snying thogs pa kha phyir bltas pa'i shar du
NK038(nyi)003:4411: sa la ljang sngon lag pa gnyis ka phur pa
NK038(nyi)003:4412: la 'jus te mdun du btsugs pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4413: lho ru gnod sbyin zangs thogs dmar po bse khrab can bse mdung bsnams /
NK038(nyi)003:4414: yum bse gdong zangs gri dang bcas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4415: nub tu srin po r+aa hu la smug po dbu
NK038(nyi)003:4416: gsum dgu pa phyag na lcags kyu dang sbrul zhags
NK038(nyi)003:4417: bsnams / sku smad sbrul dkar ljang du yod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4418: byang du za byed ma dkar mo shel phreng ma /
NK038(nyi)003:4419: phyag na gser gyi gri zhags bsnams /
NK038(nyi)003:4420: sku stod dar dkar sku smad stag sham seng ge zhon pa sman g.yu chung rol ba'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4421: de las gzhan yang rab tu byung pa'i cha lugs /
NK038(nyi)003:4423: chos gos nag po phyin ci log tu gyon pa /
NK038(nyi)003:4428: khyung dkar po mchu gshog sngon po /
NK038(nyi)003:4429: sbrul sngo dmar za ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4430: bya smug po lag pa za ba dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4431: mthing nag gri gug thod khrag can dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4432: mthing ga gri gug thod khrag can stag la zhon pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4433: dmar po rdo rje dang snying bsnams pa /
NK038(nyi)003:4434: gos ser gyon cing rta smug po la zhon pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4435: ser po ber ka'i mgo bo la mi mgos mtshan pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4436: ne le'i rkyal ba can rta sngon po zhon pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4437: smug po khram shing dang thod khrag bsnams pas drel sngon po zhon pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4438: mthing ga ber ka'i mgo gzhug phyed rdor can dar sna btags pa bsnams pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4439: nag po 'jigs su rung ba bsgral bya mnan te /
NK038(nyi)003:4440: g.yon pas skra nas bzung te /
NK038(nyi)003:4441: g.yas gri gug gis snying 'don pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4442: dmar po kha gdengs kha dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4443: zhing gi rgyal mtshan bsnams pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4444: mthing ga gri gug dang snying thogs pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4445: smug po ra dung 'bud pa dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4448: 'phar ba sngo skya'am dmar skya dang /
NK038(nyi)003:4454: mchod rten nag po bang rim gsum pa bum pa dang bre dang bcas pa dgod do //
NK038(nyi)003:4455: de dag ni rus pa'i rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK038(nyi)003:4456: mi rengs rnams zhing gdan dang bcas pa'o //
NK038(nyi)003:4457: de yang pho seng g.yas la mo seng g.yon /
NK038(nyi)003:4458: ces pa la sogs pa ltar mdzes shing phyogs dang mthun par dgod do //
